iteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113417","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Overflow","native":"おーばーふろぉ","romaji":"Overflow","userPreferred":"Overflow"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/110347-LNK3w8GgV80a.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f18628","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx110347-yrizi77YpB89.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx110347-yrizi77YpB89.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx110347-yrizi77YpB89.jpg"},"description":"Based on the erotic game by Bishop.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nEven though Souichi Takazaki is just a normal student, he's forced to attend an elite school in accordance with his father's will. Worse still, because everyone feels superior to him, he can't blend in with the crowd and is always alone.\u003cbr\u003e\nHowever, in the midst of it all, there's still someone who treats him without discrimination, Ayana, and she becomes his moral support. But after an incident occurs, he misunderstands that she also disdains him like everyone else.\u003cbr\u003e\nAffection turns into resentment. And as a result, the protagonist discovers something interesting -- He has the ability to manipulate others, but only their body, not their mind.\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd thus, he decides to use this new-found power to satisfy his every desire.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site)","episodes":2,"format":"OVA","id":110347,"idMal":40048,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":65,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/110347","startDate":{"day":1,"month":11,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"屈辱","romaji":"Kutsujoku","userPreferred":"Kutsujoku"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113425-hcwuSZsuYMtt.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#2886e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx113425-tYGRUa5pgZje.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113425-tYGRUa5pgZje.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx113425-tYGRUa5pgZje.jpg"},"description":"In a dark world of monsters, adventurers and mages, some of the most gifted healers are subjugated to brute force even by the hands of their compatriots. But one mage, Keyaru, gains the ability to rewind time, turn the tables and right all wrongs.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: This anime was aired at three broadcast censorship levels: a TV version, a streaming-exclusive \"Redo\" version, and an uncensored \"Complete Healing\" version, also translated as \"Complete Recovery,\" shown on AT-X.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":113425,"idMal":40750,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":57,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113425","startDate":{"day":13,"month":1,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Redo of Healer","native":"回復術士のやり直し","romaji":"Kaifuku Jutsushi no Yarinaoshi","userPreferred":"Kaifuku Jutsushi no Yarinaoshi"},"trailer":{"id":"dLwpj-sjnho","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dLwpj-sjnho/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#e4865d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx104040-bx0g38avoWsz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx104040-bx0g38avoWsz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx104040-bx0g38avoWsz.jpg"},"description":"After obtaining the powers of hypnosis he does what any man would do. Takes over an entire school of women, students and teachers and creates a harem of his very own!\u00