br\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nKenta quickly learns that his uncle got transferred to another city so it's only the three of them in the house. Saki and Maki waste no time to approach him very aggressivly.\u003cbr\u003e","episodes":1,"format":"OVA","id":21527,"idMal":29085,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":65,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21527","startDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"聖ヤリマンシスターズ パコパコ日記 THE ANIMATION","romaji":"Sei Yariman Sisters Pakopako Nikki THE ANIMATION","userPreferred":"Sei Yariman Sisters Pakopako Nikki THE ANIMATION"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/109326-XMJ00kqfT5kr.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbf1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx109326-eZrJOPw7DCzB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx109326-eZrJOPw7DCzB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx109326-eZrJOPw7DCzB.jpg"},"description":"A guy by the name of Kuroda-sensei is given a job as the new coach/adviser of the girls lacrosse club in an all female school called Felinus Academy for Girls but... it turns out to be a bumpy ride as he encounters sex fiends among the squad, and his adventures begins as he attempts to gain their respect as adviser.\n","episodes":6,"format":"OVA","id":109326,"idMal":39800,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/109326","startDate":{"day":6,"month":9,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"じょしラク！","romaji":"Joshi Luck!","userPreferred":"Joshi Luck!"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/108113-IGgl60QmF3S4.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4865d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx108113-2Toq1jDKvnom.jpg","larg