 ni Yasashii Gal toka, Kyonyuu no Osananajimi toka."},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx179823-bRAv7uaS8mxl.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx179823-bRAv7uaS8mxl.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx179823-bRAv7uaS8mxl.png"},"description":"Hikari Kuroda, a classmate who often comes over to read manga to my house, the house of an inconspicuous \"otaku\" in class. The reason why Kuroda, who I thought I would never have anything to do with, started hanging out at an otaku's house three months ago was because she asked me if I had all the volumes of a very popular manga, and when I answered that I did... \u003ci\u003e\"I'm bored today, so I'll go read it.\"\u003c/i\u003e I don't find it annoying at all that she's started hanging out at my house. Because... She lets me use her pussy instead.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fanza, translated and edited)","format":"ONA","id":179823,"idMal":59407,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/179823","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"native":"入り浸りギャルにま〇こ使わせて貰う話 Animation","romaji":"Iribitari Gal ni Manko Tsukawasete Morau Hanashi Animation","userPreferred":"Iribitari Gal ni Manko Tsukawasete Morau Hanashi Animation"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/123760-KhoXSLHmJLpu.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg"},"description":"Some gyarus have decided to use Imaizumi's house as a gathering spot to play video games and eat snacks. When Reina gets bored with video games, she sets her sights on another toy in the house: Imaizumi himself...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku!)\u003cbr\u003e","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":123760,"idMal":124483,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123760","startDate":{"day":8,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Imaizumi's house is a place for gals to gather","이마이즈미네, 어느새 갸루 아지트가 되어버렸다"],"title":{"english":"Imaizumi Brings All The Gyarus To His House","native":"今泉ん家はどうやらギャルの溜まり場になってるらしい","romaji":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii","userPreferred":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/132203","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":187266,"name":{"full":"Gorou Nori"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":106200,"name":{"full":"Ken Raika"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":216547,"name":{"full":"Tokku03"}},"role":"Script"},{"node":{"id":153718,"name":{"full":"Megane Sagari"}},"role":"Storyboard"}]},"startDate":{"day":6,"month":8,"year":2021},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":405,"name":"T-REX"}]}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:04:14.439059+03:00"},"135584":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":78,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":517547,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Mignon is a young, up-and-rising cage fighter. He has been boxing for two and a half years. His coach is strict and controls a lot of his career. After each violent match, Mignon suffers severe injuries and needs medical treatment. The doctor tries convincing him to quit fighting. However, Mignon believes he has no other prospects for his future.","gender":"Male","id":353870,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b353870-ouwNpLAfLxkv.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mignon","native":"민용"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/353870"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":517548,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Yeong-Won is a doctor who works for the boxing club. He treats the injuries of Mignon and other cage fighters who get hurt. Young-One worries about the young boxer's well-being. He tries convincing him to quit this dangerous career. His boss, Master Woo, warns Yeong-Won not to get emotionally attached. Any relationship between Yeong-Won and Mignon comes with complications.","gender":"Male","id":353869,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b353869-oeRrS8ZQXatU.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Young-Won Oh"],"full":"Yeong-Won O","native":"오영원"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/353869"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"description":"After losing his parents at a young age, Mignon lives as a mechanic by day, and a cage fighter by night at an illegal arena. Living a life of exploitation and violence, the only person who gives him any attention is Oh Young-One, a doctor at the illegal arena.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e“I’ll do anything…! I… I can help you!”\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDespite knowing Young-One’s true identity, Mignon’s pure and blind love for him causes Young-One to start slowly opening his heart. But the hellish reality that surrounds Mignon starts to shake up even Young-One’s life!","duration":5,"endDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2023},"genres":["Drama","Romance","Sports","Supernatural"],"id":135584,"meanScore":78,"popularity":7699,"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/109412-w7u1XIePvzoF.jpg","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b109412-HEtoCbVxWOwb.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b109412-HEtoCbVxWOwb.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b109412-HEtoCbVxWOwb.png"},"description":"It's winter. Myung came to the highschool reunion party to see Sun-Ho, a guy he secretly had a crush on. Yet, it is hard for Myung to have fun with others because of his shy disposition. He sneaks out of the party for smoking. Then, Sun-Ho also gets up and follows after Myung.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Laftel)","episodes":6,"format":"ONA","id":109412,"idMal":40491,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/109412","startDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Hyperventilation","native":"과호흡","romaji":"Gwahoheup","userPreferred":"Gwahoheup"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/132821-ZxPlNDQhrjxC.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4351a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx132821-jiU4WyEoy7kh.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx132821-jiU4WyEoy7kh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx132821-jiU4WyEoy7kh.jpg"},"description":"Short ONA animating sweet moments from the novel and a new side story.","episodes":4,"format":"ONA","id":132821,"idMal":49202,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/132821","startDate":{"day":12,"month":3,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"시맨틱 에러 스페셜","romaji":"Semantic Error Special","userPreferred":"Semantic Error Special"},"trailer":{"id":"NWMudS0g4LU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NWMudS0g4LU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#bbe4f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx132816-ZEqk6c7YaB8v.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx132816-ZEqk6c7YaB8v.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx132816-ZEqk6c7YaB8v.jpg"},"description":"In the dream, a romance starts with a stranger.","episodes":10,"format":"ONA","id":132816,"idMal":49059,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/132816","startDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Unbelievable Space Love","native":"언빌리버블 스페이스 러브","romaji":"Unbelievable Space Love","userPreferred":"Unbelievable Space Love"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b183798-4OLL3fkVpHAk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b183798-4OLL3fkVpHAk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b183798-4OLL3fkVpHAk.jpg"},"description":"Eunkyum has been at his company for a year now. He's friendly, bright, and has a great relationship with his colleagues. But he's unlucky in love — most likely because he's a sucker for looks. That's why he was thrilled when his hot new boss joined the company... before he made Eunkyum's life hell.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Manta Comics)","episodes":10,"format":"ONA","id":183798,"idMal":58783,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":65,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/183798","startDate":{"day":29,"month":12,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"연애제한구역","romaji":"Yeonae Jehan Guyeok","userPreferred":"Yeonae Jehan Guyeok"},"trailer":{"id":"s3h_i9jw4so","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/s3h_i9jw4so/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/109171-EhGBzwDvN3ZT.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5daef1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx109171-gJ51P8kLDxgt.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx109171-gJ51P8kLDxgt.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx109171-gJ51P8kLDxgt.png"},"description":"Yakuza bosses are supposed to be tough, ruthless, and treat their men like cogs in a callous criminal machine. When former cop and ex-con Chikara Doumeki accepts his latest bodyguard assignment, however, he realizes that there’s something different about his new boss, Yashiro. Because while Yashiro may seem as emotionally distant as his counterparts, he’s also a closet masochist who enjoys receiving pain as much as his job involves bringing it. \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nYashiro’s feelings for a least a few of his men also extends far beyond what’s normally extended to other members of the same crime family… a group that now includes Chikara. Of course, Chikara’s got his own issues, and nobody can beat an ex-cop when it comes to putting the lockdown on a relationship.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)","episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","id":109171,"idMal":39761,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/109171","startDate":{"day":15,"month":2,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Twittering Birds Never Fly: The Clouds Gather","native":"囀る鳥は羽ばたかない The clouds gather","romaji":"Saezuru Tori wa Habatakanai: The clouds gather","userPreferred":"Saezuru Tori wa Habatakanai: The clouds gather"},"trailer":{"id":"4YVi4TnZTVY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4YVi4TnZTVY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b184290-xTkOhwcT3GT2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b184290-xTkOhwcT3GT2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b184290-xTkOhwcT3GT2.jpg"},"description":"Wanna fake-date for four weeks?\nDojun's life at college is off to a perfect start! Until he meets his roommate, Jaehee, a high school friend whom he may have ghosted. Jaehee claims he's over their unresolved past, but after an accident resulting in a fractured wrist, he makes Dojun a proposition...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Manta)","episodes":10,"format":"ONA","id":184290,"idMal":55725,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":66,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184290","startDate":{"day":4,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"4 Week Lovers","native":"4주 애인","romaji":"4-ju Aein","userPreferred":"4-ju Aein"},"trailer":{"id":"Vd-HFj5yzTE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Vd-HFj5yzTE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/206974-PpNBE8alLWMI.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx206974-7SVXzDTvaqcd.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx206974-7SVXzDTvaqcd.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx206974-7SVXzDTvaqcd.png"},"description":"\u003ci\u003eIn Jung-gu, Seoul, tucked away in a secluded industrial alley behind the glittering skyscrapers, a vampire lives.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Mignon, orphaned at a young age, works as a car mechanic by day and fights as a mixed martial artist in illegal underground arenas by night. Amidst his daily grind stained by exploitation and violence, Yeong-Won, the arena's doctor, is the only one who shows him genuine care and concern. One day, Mignon witnesses Yeong-Won's dangerous secret.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003e “I'll do whatever you tell me...! I can help you!”\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e Even knowing his true identity, Yeong-Won slowly opens his heart to Mingnon's blind devotion. But the hellish reality that binds Mignon begins to shake Yeong-Won's own life to its core...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Ridibooks, translated)","endDate":{"day":31,"month":1,"year":2026},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Sports","Supernatural"],"id":206974,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/206974","startDate":{"day":28,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["민용(MIGNON)"],"title":{"native":"민용","romaji":"MIGNON","userPreferred":"MIGNON"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"ADAPTATION"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/135584","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":138973,"name":{"full":"Lewin"}},"role":"Original Creator"}]},"startDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2023},"studios":{},"trailer":{"id":"kcupE5zz3AY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kcupE5zz3AY/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:04:13.992172+03:00"},"142116":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":72,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":400894,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":291965,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b291965-cOjMFEGVNNZL.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Sayuri Takamine","native":"高嶺小百合"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/291965"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":400895,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":291966,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b291966-K34X7WcXXrdh.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ayame Takamine","native":"高嶺あやめ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/291966"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":400896,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":291967,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b291967-GjjSDFloFPJv.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kasumi Takamine","native":"高嶺香澄"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/291967"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"duration":30,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":2,"year":2022},"genres":["Hentai"],"id":142116,"meanScore":74,"popularity":3801,"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"ban