r\u003e\nAnd so, a forbidden bathing experience began. Me, my sister, and childhood friend—one man and two women—are sharing one bath. After involuntarily \"overflowing,\" the sister's secret love come out?!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThis is a young romantic comedy that won't let you say, \"it's over!\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, translated)","episodes":8,"format":"ONA","id":113417,"idMal":40746,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":68,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113417","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Overflow","native":"おーばーふろぉ","romaji":"Overflow","userPreferred":"Overflow"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n98769-80A4M02KDsJX.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#1a50e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/98769-cgwAYgZgaTJV.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/98769-cgwAYgZgaTJV.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/98769-cgwAYgZgaTJV.png"},"description":"Come to the biggest sexual entertainment park in the world, Mizuryuu Kei Land! A place where you can enjoy safe sex with everyone as much. This is where the dream can be grasped.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Nekopoi and Has Been Translated and Edited)","episodes":2,"format":"OVA","id":98769,"idMal":35581,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":69,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/98769","startDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"おいでよ! 水龍敬ランド","romaji":"Oide yo! Mizuryuu Kei Land","userPreferred":"Oide yo! Mizuryuu Kei Land"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101033-mKf4OdKAFFQh.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx101033-FH0AL46i3WWt.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx101033-FH0AL46i3WWt.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx101033-FH0AL46i3WWt.jpg"},"description":"Based on the CG collection by TORYA!/Otona teikoku (TORYA!/オトナテイコク).\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nMy dad got re-married to a Russian woman with massive breasts, and she has two daughters who are half-Russian and also have a super sexy body!\nI have all kinds of sex with my Russian mother in law and stepsisters!\n\nThe Russian girls had suppressed their desires in their day to day lives until now,\nbut as the main character desires them, their initial resistance gives way and their bodies become honest...!\n\nIn the house, at school, even outdoors! Anywhere! Sex all the way!!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: DLsite English)","episodes":2,"format":"OVA","id":101033,"idMal":37233,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":70,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101033","startDate":{"day":1,"month":6,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"むっつりドスケベロシア義母姉妹の本質見抜いてセックス三昧","romaji":"Muttsuri Dosukebe Russia Gibo Shimai no Honshitsu Minuite Sex Zanmai","userPreferred":"Muttsuri Dosukebe Russia Gibo Shimai no Honshitsu Minuite Sex Zanmai"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx194353-DYQodQxpFuXD.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx194353-DYQodQxpFuXD.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx194353-DYQodQxpFuXD.png"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eEpisode 1\u003c/b\u003e - \u003ci\u003eDekapai Gimai, Shuurai\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHis stepsister's overwhelming breasts cause him to lose all sense of reason! Takashi's parents remarried and he ended up living with his stepsister. He thought it would be awkward to live with a girl, even though she was his stepsister, but he was surprised when he saw her. Her name was Alice, a beautiful girl from Northern Europe. While Takashi was happy to have a beautiful stepsister, her overly large breasts made him feel uneasy. However, seeing Alice trying to fit in with the family, Takashi suppressed his wicked feelings and treated her as his stepbrother. However, one day, when he saw Alice naked, Takashi's wall of reason collapsed.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eEpisode 2\u003c/b\u003e - \u003ci\u003e7days\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nBig breasts dancing in the hands of a cheeky younger man. One day, Kotomi returns home to find a strange boy there. When she asks her mother about the situation, she learns that a relative and her husband are going on a trip and she's going to take care of him for a week. His name is Ren, a boy younger than Kotomi. Kotomi is put off by Ren's cheeky manner, who calls her by her first name in a familiar manner. However, things turn out to be different, and Ren ends up staying in Kotomi's room. Remembering a scary TV show she saw at dinner, Ren becomes afraid to sleep alone. Kotomi reluctantly lets Ren into her bed. Once in bed, Ren clings to her. Kotomi senses something akin to Ren, but his hand movements gradually become more erotic. Kotomi tries to reject him, but he massages her big breasts with practiced hands, and before she knows it, she's pleased.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Getchu, translated)","format":"OVA","id":194353,"idMal":62316,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":69,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/194353","startDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"native":"ちょろ・めす・でいず","romaji":"Choro Mesu Days","userPreferred":"Choro Mesu Days"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21668-sxBklMF3OoGF.png","coverImage":{"color":"#35d6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21668-i2tD558TqCo6.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21668-i2tD558TqCo6.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/21668-i2tD558TqCo6.png"},"description":"Take a school trip to Nude Beach where this beach has rules for all visitors to be naked without dressing, and also men are forbidden to be aroused. However, if someone is aroused then someone will be given the opportunity to release his desire by doing pervert things in the tent.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Nekopoi and Has Been Translated and Edited)","episodes":2,"format":"OVA","id":21668,"idMal":32833,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":66,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21668","startDate":{"day":27,"month":5,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"In school trip to the nudist beach!!","native":"ヌーディストビーチに修学旅行で!! THE ANIMATION","romaji":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugakuryokou de!! THE ANIMATION","userPreferred":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugakuryokou de!! THE ANIMATION"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg"},"description":"1. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Seed~; Comic ExE 9\u003cbr\u003e\n2. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Bloom~; Comic ExE 10\u003cbr\u003e\n3. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Lily~; Comic ExE 13\u003cbr\u003e\n4. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Iris~; Comic ExE 25\u003cbr\u003e\n5. Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou ~Gypsophila~; Comic ExE 27\u003cbr\u003e\n6. Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~Fruits~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜Fruits〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~Fruits~)\u003cbr\u003e\n7. Shoka no Makuai de; COMIC Anthurium 2017-07\u003cbr\u003e\n8. Kaiten Eigyouchuu ~Afternoon Tea~; COMIC X-EROS #21\u003cbr\u003e\n9. Tousian e Youkoso!; COMIC X-EROS #17\u003cBR\u003e\n10. Last Summer; COMIC ExE 16\u003cBR\u003e\n10.5 Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~ampoule \"0\"~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜ampoule 『0』〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~ampoule “0”~)","endDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":132725,"idMal":142890,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132725","startDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Takamine-ke no Nirinka","Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou","Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou","Shoka no Makuai de","Kaiten Eigyouchuu","Tousian e Youkoso!","The Three Flowers of The Takamine House","The Anemone of the Takamine House","Between the Bookshelves ","Welcome to Tousian!"],"title":{"native":"Garden","romaji":"Garden","userPreferred":"Garden"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142116","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":114023,"name":{"full":"Kuro no Miki"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":290117,"name":{"full":"Ao Ishii"}},"role":"Director"}]},"startDate":{"day":25,"month":2,"year":2022},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":541,"name":"Seven"}]}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:01:56.49194+03:00"},"166613":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":80,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":435029,"node":{"age":"15-16","dateOfBirth":{"day":8,"month":1},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Fire\n__Occupation:__ Shinobi\n__Affiliation:__ Iwagakure (Formerly)\n\nGabimaru is an elite shinobi assassin formerly from Iwagakure. He is the husband of [Yui](https://anilist.co/character/151771/Yui) and the son-in-law to the chief of Iwagakure.\n\nGabimaru is calm, level-headed and rarely shows any emotions. He is calm to the point where he is unfazed by any sort of crisis, such as being executed or when he is confronted and attacked by a strong enemy. As noted by Sagiri, once Gabimaru calms down he tends to complain. He prefers to stick with his main objective at hand and not get tangled with anything else that doesn't involve his goals. Although he is viewed as being obnoxious (mainly by Sagiri), he can also be respectful and polite at times.\n\n~!During his time in Iwagakure, Gabimaru was known and admired by his peers for his cruelty and ruthless killings of his victims, but after being married to Yui, Gabimaru underwent a major change. Even though he was influenced by his leader's words of ridding himself of his emotions to become strong, Gabimaru was also influenced by Yui's kind and caring nature into believing that having emotions made him truly strong and would turn him into a true warrior. This overwrote his cruel nature as a ninja and made him want to avoid unnecessary killing.!~\n\nHe served as Iwagakure's most infamous shinobi until he was betrayed by his village for wanting to abandon his role as a murderer and live a peaceful life with his wife, resulting in him being handed over to the authorities to be executed. However, after the shogun calls for convict criminals to acquire the Elixir of Life from the dangerous island known as Kotaku, in exchange for a pardon for their past crimes, Gabimaru accepts the invitation to be a part of the competition mission in order to reunite with Yui and live the life he so desired. Upon taking the mission, [Yamada Asaemon Sagiri](https://anilist.co/character/137263/Sagiri) was chosen as his assigned monitor.\n\n~!Shortly after, Gabimaru becomes a part of a united front formed from the remaining surviving criminals and executioners to defeat Lord Tensen, work together in capturing the elixir, and have everyone escape the island.!~","gender":"Male","id":137260,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137260-xmSis8FmwhEE.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Garan no Gabimaru (がらんの画眉丸)","Gabimaru the Hollow"],"full":"Gabimaru","native":"画眉丸"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137260"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":435030,"node":{"age":"16-17","dateOfBirth":{"day":16,"month":12},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Wood\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n__Rank:__ 12th\n\nYamada Asaemon Sagiri is the 12th rank Asaemon in the Yamada Clan. After the shogun sent criminals to Kotaku to find the Elixir of Life, she was tasked with being [Gabimaru's](https://anilist.co/character/137260/Gabimaru) executioner.\n\nSagiri generally displays a calm demeanor when taking on her role as an executioner. However, after landing on Kotaku, she allowed herself to act casual around others as long as she continued to do her job. She is very polite and caring towards her fellow Asaemon members, despite the fact that she is aware that some view her as being unworthy of becoming a samurai. However, she is not afraid to speak her mind and to stand up for herself. Though she takes matters seriously, Sagiri does possess a sense of humor, often laughing at Shion's jokes. \n\n~!After her experience with working successfully with criminals and witnessing the deaths of her fellow clansmen, Sagiri resolved to abandon her role as an executioner on the mission and viewed everyone that came not as a criminal or an executioner but as allies so they can work together to return home safely.!~\n\nWhen she was young, Sagiri watched as her father skillfully decapitated a condemned performer with a single swing of his sword. From that day she became inspired to walk the path of an executioner and achieve the same level of skill as her father. As she began her training on how to wield a sword, Sagiri was looked down on by her fellow Yamada members, as well as her father, for being a female following the path of a samurai. Sagiri was also shunned by other children because of the clan's bad reputation. Despite the harsh treatment she faced, Sagiri managed to earn her name as a Yamada Asaemon.","gender":"Female","id":137263,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137263-I2krXFEFOHjL.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yamada Asaemon Sagiri (山田浅ェ門佐切"],"full":"Sagiri","native":"佐切"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137263"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":435037,"node":{"age":"19-20","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Metal\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n__Rank:__ 9th\n\nYamada Asaemon Fuchi is the 9th rank Asaemon in the Yamada Clan and was chosen to be [Tamiya Gantetsusai's](https://anilist.co/character/137264/Gantetsusai-Tamiya) assigned monitor. \n\nFuchi is a rational thinker that has a good sense of judgement in situations and carries a no-nonsense view when it comes to matters that he deems are unscientific, pointless, and illogical. He has great pride as a Yamada Asaemon and does not tolerate anybody speaking disgracefully about the Yamada clan. He is very close with his Asaemon comrades and gives them nicknames instead of using honourifics. Even though the Yamada clan mainly deal with testing new swords and executions, Fuchi preferrs, and has a deep passion, for studying the human anatomy to improve medical science that came with the trade. He whole-heartedly believes that anatomical research would save lives and despises those who thought so little of this study.\n\n~! Although he was an executioner, after his experience working together with the surviving convicts, Fuchi found that both \"crime\" and \"evil\" were entirely different from one another, with Tamiya Gantetsusai as an example. From a scientific view point, Fuchi found that samurai and criminals were not so different since they are structured the same and had a will to live, which was reason enough for the survivors to band together in trying to return home. !~\n\n~! With both him and Gantetsusai badly injured Fuchi musters up the rest of his strength to administer first aid to Gantetsusai instead of himself resulting in him dying. In his last thoughts, Fuchi warns Shugen not to underestimate the survivors since they are not willing to die easily and wishes the best of luck to both his allies and enemies. !~","gender":"Male","id":137268,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137268-veVGOk95qa87.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yamada Asaemon Fuchi (山田浅ェ門付知)","Yamada Asaemon Tsukechi"],"full":"Fuchi","native":"付知"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137268"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559507,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":9},"description":"__Race:__ Tensen\n__Tao Attribute:__ Fire\n__Occupation:__ Partial Ruler of Kotaku\n__Affiliation:__ Lord Tensen, Xu Fu\n\nJu Fa is a member of Lord Tensen, as well as one of the rulers of Kotaku.\n\nJu Fa is very short tempered and has aggressive tendencies towards anything that irritated him at the slightest, which also applied to his fellow Lord Tensen members. While its true that all members of Lord Tensen have a negative view on humans, Ju Fa is the one that truly despises them with a passion and believes that they are nothing more than \"livestock\". \n\nHe is very protective of [Tao Fa](https://anilist.co/character/151778/Tao-Fa) since they had been by each others side from the moment they were born, because of that Rien stated that the two were special in that they are in fact two of a whole. Despite their ability to heal themselves, Ju Fa hated when Tao Fa got hurt and was told that he cared greatly for Tao Fa as his partner.\n\nJu Fa found the male gender to be well-suited for him because of his moods and how he is able to easily handle situations.","gender":"Male/Female (Prefer the Male gender)","id":151772,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151772-6Q3z1oDIrqxT.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["ジュファ","Ashuku Taitei (ア閦大帝)","Great Emperor Akshobhya","Dadi Aksho"],"full":"Ju Fa","native":"菊花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151772"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559521,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":388252,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Dokuro Doushi","native":"ドクロ道士"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388252"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560943,"node":{"age":"48","dateOfBirth":{"day":30,"month":1},"description":"11th Shogun of Japan.","gender":"Male","id":301606,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b301606-08sCkI5L3d11.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tokugawa Nariyoshi","native":"徳川斉慶"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/301606"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435038,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n\nYamada Asaemon Senta is the 5th rank Asaemon in the Yamada Clan. After the shogun sent criminals to Kotaku to find the Elixir of Life, he was tasked with being [Yuzuriha's](https://anilist.co/character/137270/Yuzuriha) executioner.\n\nSenta is very nervous around others and tends to frequently sweat. He usually remains in the background and goes along with whatever is happening around him but will speak up when he feels that whatever he has to say would be helpful. Senta is capable of assessing the situation and makes good judgements as to how to approach them. He dislikes his role of killing people but feels that he has no choice in the matter and chooses to abandon his dream of becoming an artist. After observing Yuzuriha, he becomes envious and enchanted by her innate freedom. Despite his nervous demeanor, Senta is fearless and stands his ground no matter who he is up against.","gender":"Male","id":137266,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137266-5BQ0RQI2SXjs.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yamada Asaemon Senta (山田浅ェ門仙汰)"],"full":"Senta","native":"仙汰"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137266"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559508,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":9},"description":"__Race:__ Tensen\n__Tao Attribute:__ Water\n__Occupation:__ Partial Ruler of Kotaku\n__Affiliation:__ Lord Tensen, Xu Fu\n\nZhu Jin is one of the rulers of Kotaku and one of the seven Lord Tensen.\n\nZhu Jin carries themselves with a calm and relaxed demeanor even when handling threats. Like their fellow Tensen, Zhu Jin has no sympathy for humans when it comes to killing them. Zhu Jin is also very perceptive of their opponents skills and can quickly adjust to them, causing them to become unfazed by whatever move they make. Zhu Jin can become easily irritated with troubling matters. Despite usually keeping a straight face at all times, when faced with an unbelievable crisis, Zhu Jin can break into a state of panic and fear and will take matters seriously. \n\nZhu Jin follows [Gui Fa's](https://anilist.co/character/170488/Gui-Fa) example of taking the Middle Way in terms of the two sexes. Therefore, unlike the other Tensens, Zhu Jin does not carry a preference to either being male or female and allows themselves to switch in and out of the two chi's over time.","gender":"Male/Female (Switches constantly)","id":151775,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151775-1f264MokbLYd.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["ヂュジン","Nyoi Genkun (如イ元君)","Tathaataa Yuanjun"],"full":"Zhu Jin","native":"朱槿"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151775"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560944,"node":{"age":"30","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":11},"description":"__Height:__ 175 cm\n\nOne of the shogun's retainers.","gender":"Male","id":302050,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b302050-IX99PePUve0D.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Aoki","native":"青木"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/302050"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435031,"node":{"age":"19-20","dateOfBirth":{"day":4,"month":8},"description":"__Race:__ Human (Formerly), ~! Semi-Immortal Human !~\n__Tao Attribute:__ Metal\n__Occupation:__ Bandit\n\nAza Chobe also known as the Bandit King, is a well-known bandit leader in Iyo that is responsible for multiple crimes committed.\n\nChobe is an extremely barbaric individual who attacks anyone or anything that poses as a threat to him. He prefers to do things of his own accord and would rather resort to violence than talk things through. Chobe is also very sadistic whenever he engages in fights with his enemies, Chobe always stuck to taking on the role of the villain, and holds grudges to those that have bested him. Although he tends to act like a brute, Chobe is a rationale thinker that knows what is the best course of action in a serious situation.\n\n~! Chobe and Toma were born as sons to a retainer under the service of the daimyō of Akō Domain, Asano Takunori. However, after Asano Takunori attacked the court official Kira Yoshinaka at Edo Castle, he was sentenced to commit seppuku. As a result, their father and the rest of the retainers had their status removed and were left as ronin, leaving their family in poverty. They were eventually taken by bandits who planned on selling them but later came to live amongst them after Chobe managed to become their leader. !~","gender":"Male","id":137269,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137269-8sLwiijk0bti.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Bandit King (賊王 Zoku-ou)","Aza Chobei","Aza Chobe"],"full":"Choubei Aza","native":"亜左弔兵衛"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137269"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435039,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Age:__ Unknown\n__Tao Attribute:__ Fire\n\nTamiya Gantetsusai formerly known as Tetsunosuke is a renown master swordsman known throughout as the Blade Dragon and Eight Provinces Unparalleled.\n\nHe considers fighting to be fun and lives to seek out and battle strong opponents that can make him feel a thrill whenever he has to draw his blade. Even when critically injured, Gantetsusai's carries a satisfied smile from the adrenaline he gets from fighting and feels as though as he is becoming stronger with each injury. However, he is not very disciplined, preferring to recklessly fight his opponents head on without thinking of a clear strategy, or listen to his allies, and hates it when others try to interfere in his enjoyment. Gantetsusai also has a perverted side as he took note and commented on Yuzuriha's physique during the selection process. Despite his perverted behavior, Gantetsusai has morals as he felt disgusted of the thought of the Dōshi using Mei for sexual intercourse to complete their Tao training.\n\n~!Gantetsusai has a massive ego and wishes to go down in history as a legendary figure. He believes that by performing extraordinary feats and people remembering his name throughout generations is the true form of immortality rather than gaining the Elixir of Life.!~\n\nAt a young age, Tetsunosuke was trained in the art of swordsmanship. After being defeated by his master, Tetsunosuke asked how he was able to despite his old age. He explains to Tetsunosuke that he has become greedy with wanting to become stronger and says that he must throw away his strength in order to see everything in what he has left. Despite this lesson, Tetsunosuke was unable to understand what his master was telling him. As he grew up, Tetsunosuke renamed himself to Tamiya Gantetsusai and went around searching for strong opponents, eventually making a name for himself as a fame swordsman.","gender":"Male","id":137264,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137264-qmjsYXb6YkX7.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Blade Dragon","剣龍","Kenryū","Eight Provinces Unparalleled","八州無双","Hasshū Musō"],"full":"Gantetsusai Tamiya","native":"民谷巌鉄斎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137264"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559509,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":9},"description":"A member of Lord Tensen and a partial ruler of Kotaku. Gui Fa maintains a complete deadpan demeanor and is known to be extremely shy around others, as they prefer to cover their face with a book at all times to avoid making eye contact. ","gender":"Male/Female","id":170488,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170488-3YyeY3FGm7Sn.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Monju Koukou (文殊公々)","Decorous Monju Koukou","Gonggong Manjusri"],"full":"Gui Fa","native":"桂花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170488"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435032,"node":{"age":"15-16","dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":9},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Earth\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon (Unofficial)\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n\nToma is a relatively new member of the Yamada clan trying to rise in their ranks and is the assigned monitor of [Chobe Aza](https://anilist.co/character/137269/Chobe-Aza).\n\n~! He turns out to be the younger brother of Chobe Aza and had a mission of infiltrating the Yamada clan to rescue him from prison. !~\n\nToma believes that the key to surviving in life is adapting to ones environment. Toma tends to act rather unfriendly when someone tries to communicate with him on friendly terms. He also displays a cocky attitude.\n\n~! He is very caring and loyal to Chobe since he has been his protector since they were children and stresses out whenever harm comes to him. Because of how his father died fighting for his allies, Toma is reluctant to cooperate with anyone except for his brother. In his own eye, Toma views himself as an extension of his brother instead of an ally and stated that the bandits that followed the two were merely pawns for them to use. However, Toma soon realizes that his reliance on his brother to protect him interferes with his growth rate to look after himself. !~\n\n~! Toma and Chobe were born as sons to a retainer under the service of the daimyō of Akō Domain, Asano Takunori. However, after Asano Takunori attacked the court official Kira Yoshinaka at Edo Castle, he was sentenced to commit seppuku. As a result, their father and the rest of the retainers had their status removed and were left as ronin, leaving their family in poverty. Their mother eventually died of an illness and their father was executed for being a part of the Akō Incident, leaving the two siblings left alone to defend for themselves. They were eventually taken by bandits who planned on selling them but later came to live amongst them after Chobe managed to become their leader. !~","gender":"Male","id":137261,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137261-lWhxTwLOYLpO.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yamada Asaemon Touma (山田浅ェ門桐馬)","Toma"],"full":"Touma","native":"桐馬"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137261"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":462748,"node":{"age":"19-20","dateOfBirth":{"day":26,"month":7},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Water\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon, Assistant Instructor\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n__Rank:__ 2nd\n\nShugen is the 2nd ranked Asaemon, as well as an Assistant Instructor, in the Yamada clan. Shugen is the leader of the second team sent to Kotaku after the shogun became impatient waiting for the first team to comeback. \n\nShugen is very dignified and diligent in his duties as an Asaemon. Shugen cares greatly for his Yamada clansmen, having spent his years with them and being taught what they know. He greatly expressed his concern for their safety on the island and vowed to bring them back home no matter what the means were. Furthermore, Shugen has a tendency to become emotional whenever he thinks about his comrades. He's one of the only Yamada clan members who doesn't look down on women in the clan and vouches for their qualifications as executioners. He greatly despises all criminals and truly believes that they are evil no matter who they are. At a young age, Shugen could not understand the Yamada clan's way of thinking when executing criminals and believed that they should all deserve a painful death.\n\nShugen believes in order of all things in the world; the order in which those who abide by the law are to be protected while those who break them should be punish without mercy.","gender":"Male","id":148752,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b148752-WkhrTfWC7kC8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["山田浅ェ門殊現","Yamada Asaemon Shugen"],"full":"Shugen","native":"殊現"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/148752"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559511,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A subordinate of Lord Tensen who was ordered to check to see if Aza Chōbei and Tōma were still in the pit becoming Tan.","id":307701,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b307701-vmr1ov2ZJNaq.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Tentacle Doushi","ナメクジ道士"],"full":"Shokushu Doushi","native":"道士"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/307701"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559594,"node":{"age":"16-17","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Occupation:__ House Wife\n__Affiliations:__ Iwagakure\n\nYui is the daughter of the Iwagakure chief and the wife of Gabimaru.\n\nYui is very kind, caring and gentle. She truly loves Gabimaru and believes that he is not completely emotionless as people make him out to be. She accepts the fact that he kills people and is not terrified being around him. Yui is also shown to be wise as she gave Gabimaru words of wisdom on why he should relax his body while giving him a bath. She is very civilized as she taught Gabimaru basic manners when they became a couple.\n\nYui was born as the daughter of the Iwagakure chief. Being born a female, Yui was not trained in the ways of the shinobi and instead lived a semi-normal life within the village. \n\n~! At some point, during her time with her father, the chief burned her face to make sure that she gave up on her dreams of ever living a normal, peaceful life as a woman. After Gabimaru proved his worth to the chief, Yui was forced by her father to marry him. The two then came to love each other as their days went by. Wanting to give his wife a peaceful life, Gabimaru came to the village chief requesting to abandon his duties as a shinobi, resulting in him being betrayed by the village and handed over to the authorities to be executed. After hearing news of her husband's captured, Yui went into a state of depression and refused to speak to anyone or eat as she waits in hopes for Gabimaru's return. !~","gender":"Female","id":151771,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151771-obZQxZPwjiud.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["画眉丸の妻"],"full":"Yui","native":"結"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151771"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435033,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human \n__Tao Attribute:__ Wood\n\nShion is the 4th rank Asaemon of the Yamada clan and is the one chosen to be Akaginu's monitor. \n\nShion is a strict but kind man. He is well aware of the brutal nature of his work as an executioner, opting to spend the rest of his time helping others. Like the other Asaemon, he possesses a strong loyalty to the Yamada clan. Shion also has a witty sense of humor, often making puns and jokes regarding his eyesight, which has become a major part of his character to the people around him. Shion is shown to be fearless, showing no fear or hesitation when facing extremely strong enemies. \n","gender":"Male","id":137267,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137267-D3mKSNS6H4o8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yamada Asaemon Shion (山田浅ェ門士遠)"],"full":"Shion","native":"士遠"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137267"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":544428,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Age:__ Unknown\n__Tao Attribute:__ Metal\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n\nKiyomaru is an unranked Asaemon in the Yamada Clan. After the shogun became impatient of the first team acquiring the Elixir of Life, Kiyomaru and [Isuzu](https://anilist.co/character/151770/Isuzu) were chosen to join [Shugen](https://anilist.co/character/148752/Shugen) and [Jikka](https://anilist.co/character/148756/Jikka) to be a part of the second team sent to acquire the elixir.\n\nDue to his young age, Kiyomaru is very immature. While departing to Kotaku, Kiyomaru spoke rudely to one of his superiors and childishly did as he pleased, such as cutting one of the ninjas mask to prove his strength and ordered one ninja to kill themselves to prove their loyalty. Kiyomaru is also very arrogant, as he declared that he was far superior to everyone that came along on the mission and hates it when people look down on him for not having a ranking.\n\n~! Despite being loyal to Shugen, because of the dire situation escalating in Hōrai, Kiyomaru and a few others decide to cooperate with the Vanguard Party. After discussing the plan to destroy the Banko's tandens scattered around Hōrai, Kiyomaru is paired with Isuzu to strengthen her Water Tao with his Metal Tao and goes after the tandens.  !~","gender":"Male","id":151776,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151776-cSAXW38xkM5B.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["山田浅ェ門清丸","Yamada Asaemon Kiyomaru"],"full":"Kiyomaru","native":"清丸"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151776"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559512,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":9},"description":"__Race:__ Tensen\n__Tao Attribute:__ Wood\n__Occupation:__ Partial Ruler of Kotaku\n__Affiliation:__ Lord Tensen, Xu Fu\n\nTao Fa is a member of Lord Tensen, as well as one of the rulers of Kotaku.\n\nTao Fa is very cheerful and always seems to be in a good mood. Unlike the other members of Lord Tensen, Tao Fa is rather friendly towards humans, or at least ones that are willing to cooperate with Lord Tensen's plans. However, she still carries the same view of using them as tools and shows no signs of sympathy towards them. Because she specializes in Bōchū Jutsu, Tao Fa is quite vulgar and often likes to flirt with others.\n\nTao Fa is always being protected by [Ju Fa](https://anilist.co/character/151772/Ju-Fa) since they had been by each others side from the moment they were born, because of that Rien stated that the two were special in that they are in fact two of a whole.\n\nTao Fa had stated that they preferred the female gender because of their liking to their appearance. As such, they also acted feminine on top of their appearance.\n","gender":"Female/Male (Prefers the Female gender)","id":151778,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151778-eaLrGLvveKGL.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["タオファ","Ratna Taisei (ラトナ大聖)","Great Sage Ratna","Sagacious Dasheng Ratna"],"full":"Tao Fa","native":"桃花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151778"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559608,"node":{"age":"500+","dateOfBirth":{"day":6,"month":2},"description":"__Race:__ Houko\n__Tao Attribute:__ Metal\n","gender":"Male","id":305440,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b305440-nNgZoPz0B2NE.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Mu Ren"],"full":"Houko","native":"木人"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/305440"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435034,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":11,"month":10},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Earth\n__Occupation:__ Kunoichi\n\nYuzuriha also known as Yuzuriha of the Keishu, is a kunoichi and one of the few criminals recruited to acquire the Elixir of Life.\n\nYuzuriha is friendly and cheerful around others with a typical teenage girl personality. She is shown to be carefree and prefers to do things at her own pace. Because of her reputation as a criminal, Yuzuriha has no problems when it comes to killing or who she has to sacrifice to achieve a goal. Underneath her friendly attitude, Yuzuriha's true nature is that of a complete narcissist, only focusing on her own well-being and shows little concern for others. This attitude stemmed from her past vow to her little sister to live only for the both of them. As a kunoichi, Yuzuriha uses her charms to get what she wants, but despite that she is shown to be a terrible liar after trying to make up her backstory.\n\n~! Though selfish, Yuzuriha can show compassion to others. As Senta was dying, she consoled him and had him die in peace by making him forget about his duties as an Asaemon and gave him the last bit of freedom he had to think about what he wanted to imagine as his last memory. !~\n\n~! Despite her beautiful appearence, with her mucus abilities she actually hides a body full of scars. !~\n\nYuzuriha grew up in a shinobi village living with her little sister, Saya, who was suffering from an incurable disease and eventually died. From then on, Yuzuriha swore to live her life for the both of them and started her career as a kunoichi. Sometime ago, Yuzuriha raided the Sagiwa Castle and defeated the retainers defending it.","gender":"Female","id":137270,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137270-PTFen9fxyo4H.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yuzuriha of the Seishu","傾主の杠","Seishu no Yuzuriha","Fox (狐 Kitsune)"],"full":"Yuzuriha","native":"杠"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137270"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":544429,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Age:__ Unknown\n__Tao Attribute:__ Earth\n__Occupation:__ Asaemon\n__Affiliation:__ Yamada Clan\n__Rank:__ 3rd\n\nJikka is the 3rd ranked Asaemon in the Yamada clan. After the shogun sent criminals to Kotaku to find the Elixir of Life, he was tasked with being Hōrubō's executioner.\n\nJikka is a laid-back individual who compared to his fellow clan members, especially Shugen, is less dedicated to his work as an Asaemon. He is rather dishonest and goes as far as to lie to shogun's officials. Jikka is also rude and disrespectful to others around him regardless of who they are, even towards his fellow Asaemon. Also, unlike his clan members who each show concern for one another, Jikka is the only member shown to have little to no concern over the safety of the other Asaemon. \n\nJikka stated that he is an individual that prefers to enjoy life to the fullest rather than focus on status and rank. This way of thinking greatly shows in his life as an executioner as he has been reported to attend his execution assignments while intoxicated and even sold his own sword as a way to collect money for his vulgar exploits. As a result, Jikka has received a bad reputation amongst his peers in the Yamada clan. Despite being so lazy and laid-back he is a very analytical individual and is incapable of being fooled through deception.\n\n~! He is one of the most mysterious people of the Yamada clan and also one of the strongest despite the attitude towards his duties, he is in fact so strong that he's the only person known who has come back from Kotatsu island alive and in perfect condition. Having sold his sword he now carries a simple takemitsu (bamboo sword), but even then he still manages to cut off criminal heads and kill monsters with ease. !~\n\nJikka believes that he and Gabimaru are similar in that they value life more than anything.","gender":"Male","id":148756,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b148756-BRSo9v4Rzds2.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["山田浅ェ門 十禾","Yamada Asaemon Jikka"],"full":"Jikka","native":"十禾"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/148756"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559516,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":9},"description":"__Race:__ Tensen\n__Tao Attribute:__ Water\n__Occupation:__ Partial ruler of Kotaku\n__Affiliation:__ Lord Tensen, Xu Fu\n\nRan is a member of Lord Tensen and part ruler of Kotaku.\n\nRan is very loyal to [Rien](https://anilist.co/character/148754/Rien) and carries the same view of seeing the Tensens as family. Like all the members of Lord Tensen, Ran has no sympathy for humans and uses them as they see fit. He believes that it is a futile effort for the trespassers to invade the palace and try their hand at opposing the Tensens, showing signs that he views them inferior compared to his family. However, he is not above praising or admiring them if they show impressive skills. Due to specializing in Dō'in, Ran is extremely passionate about the physical work of the body and fighting styles that can only be obtained through diligent training.\n\n~! Upon transforming into his Kishikai form, Ran expressed his physicality while attacking [Gabimaru](https://anilist.co/character/137260/Gabimaru) and [Yuzuriha](https://anilist.co/character/137270/Yuzuriha). He was also up to the challenge of facing the two in their use of ninjutsu in order to strengthen his Dō'in training. !~\n\n~! He is bested in a fight against Gabimaru and Yuzuriha and is killed. Ran slowly dies with his last thoughts about Rien. !~","gender":"Male/Female (Prefers the Male gender)","id":151773,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b151773-THqI74IGmHsS.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Juntei Teikun (准胝帝君)","Imperial Juntei Teikun","Deified Dijun Cundi"],"full":"Ran","native":"蘭"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/151773"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560928,"node":{"age":"17","dateOfBirth":{"day":16,"month":10},"description":"__Height:__ 180 cm\n\nKumokiri is a jounin-class shinobi of Iwagakure.","gender":"Male","id":306843,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b306843-tk8Z4a3qTCXi.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kumokiri","native":"雲霧"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/306843"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":435035,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Race:__ Human\n__Tao Attribute:__ Water\n\nNurugai is the last remaining member of the Sanka and a wrongly convicted death-row criminal. Her assigned monitor is Tenza\n\nNurugai looks down on samurai, viewing them as stupid. Her disdain for them stems from the fact that they were partially responsible for killing her people. Because of this incident, Nurugai feels a strong guilt for leading her village's extermination, even believed that the reason why she is on a dangerous mission is because she was receiving divine punishment for her actions and accepted death. \n\nNurugai was raised with the Sanka Mountain People in a village where she had lived with her grandfather. Nurugai and her grandfather were in a friendly, familial relationship where she would learn off her grandfather's wisdom. Her village however were considered rebels against the current shogunate, refusing to submit to Tokugawa. Because of this, samurai were sent to locate the hillside tribes they defined as Emishis. One day, Nurugai crossed paths with a party of lost men, encouraging Nurugai to offer her help by seeking rest in the security of her village. Nurugai recognized her mistake when she realised that these men were samurai under the order of Tokugawa, who began a mass killing of her village that would leave her as the sole survivor.","gender":"Female","id":137262,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137262-frEjtAk5zYRV.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Nurugai","native":"ヌルガイ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137262"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJigokuraku\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166613,"meanScore":81,"popularity":114187,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":273,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"TV","rank":484,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":8,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":3,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":8,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":3,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n101347-tHurKfTlhtFl.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#d6bb6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101347-TGaDwEYqLfm1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101347-TGaDwEYqLfm1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101347-TGaDwEYqLfm1.jpg"},"description":"Dororo, a young orphan thief, meets Hyakkimaru, a powerful ronin. Hyakkimaru's father, a greedy feudal lord, had made a pact with 12 demons, offering his yet-unborn son's body parts in exchange for great power. Thus, Hyakkimaru - who was born without arms, legs, eyes, ears, a nose or a mouth - was abandoned in a river as a baby. Rescued and raised by Dr. Honma, who equips him with artificial limbs and teaches him sword-fighting techniques, Hyakkimaru discovers that each time he slays a demon, a piece of his body is restored. Now, he roams the war-torn countryside in search of demons.","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":101347,"idMal":37520,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101347","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Dororo","native":"どろろ","romaji":"Dororo","userPreferred":"Dororo"},"trailer":{"id":"CPG64L4bSkI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CPG64L4bSkI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101922-33MtJGsUSxga.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg"},"description":"It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself. Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a “demon slayer” so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":26,"format":"TV","id":101922,"idMal":38000,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101922","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba","native":"鬼滅の刃","romaji":"Kimetsu no Yaiba","userPreferred":"Kimetsu no Yaiba"},"trailer":{"id":"6vMuWuWlW4I","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6vMuWuWlW4I/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178025-WvcXi1J2SGRa.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178025-cWJKEsZynkil.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178025-cWJKEsZynkil.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178025-cWJKEsZynkil.jpg"},"description":"A boy lives in a floating town, where the poor scrape by and the rich live a sumptuous life, simply casting their garbage off the side, into the abyss. When he’s falsely accused of murder, though, his wrongful conviction leads to an unimaginable punishment—exile off the edge, with the rest of the trash. Down on the surface, the cast-off waste of humanity has bred vicious monsters, and to travel the path to vengeance against those who cast him into Hell, a boy will have to become a warrior…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":178025,"idMal":59062,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178025","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Gachiakuta","native":"ガチアクタ","romaji":"Gachiakuta","userPreferred":"Gachiakuta"},"trailer":{"id":"yeRvDchyo44","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/yeRvDchyo44/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113415-jQBSkxWAAk83.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg"},"description":"A boy fights... for \"the right death.\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nHardship, regret, shame: the negative feelings that humans feel become Curses that lurk in our everyday lives. The Curses run rampant throughout the world, capable of leading people to terrible misfortune and even death. What's more, the Curses can only be exorcised by another Curse.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nItadori Yuji is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a friend who has been attacked by Curses, he eats the finger of the Double-Faced Specter, taking the Curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with the Double-Faced Specter. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Gojou Satoru, Itadori is admitted to the Tokyo Metropolitan Technical High School of Sorcery, an organization that fights the Curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a Curse to exorcise a Curse, a life from which he could never turn back.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode received an early web premiere on September 19th, 2020. The regular TV broadcast started on October 3rd, 2020.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":113415,"idMal":40748,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113415","startDate":{"day":3,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN","native":"呪術廻戦","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen"},"trailer":{"id":"pkKu9hLT-t8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pkKu9hLT-t8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101348-pivKKffCAwAY.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101348-2fhDFPCuMNiz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101348-2fhDFPCuMNiz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101348-2fhDFPCuMNiz.jpg"},"description":"Thorfinn is son to one of the Vikings' greatest warriors, but when his father is killed in battle by the mercenary leader Askeladd, he swears to have his revenge. Thorfinn joins Askeladd's band in order to challenge him to a duel, and ends up caught in the middle of a war for the crown of England.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":101348,"idMal":37521,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101348","startDate":{"day":8,"month":7,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Vinland Saga","native":"ヴィンランド・サガ","romaji":"VINLAND SAGA","userPreferred":"VINLAND SAGA"},"trailer":{"id":"5xqEp7R9SYM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5xqEp7R9SYM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127230-o8IRwCGVr9KW.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#6b1a1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx127230-DdP4vAdssLoz.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx127230-DdP4vAdssLoz.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx127230-DdP4vAdssLoz.png"},"description":"Denji is a teenage boy living with a Chainsaw Devil named Pochita. Due to the debt his father left behind, he has been living a rock-bottom life while repaying his debt by harvesting devil corpses with Pochita.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOne day, Denji is betrayed and killed. As his consciousness fades, he makes a contract with Pochita and gets revived as \"Chainsaw Man\" — a man with a devil's heart.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":127230,"idMal":44511,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/127230","startDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Chainsaw Man","native":"チェンソーマン","romaji":"Chainsaw Man","userPreferred":"Chainsaw Man"},"trailer":{"id":"v4yLeNt-kCU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/v4yLeNt-kCU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/11061-8WkkTZ6duKpq.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png"},"description":"A new adaption of the manga of the same name by Togashi Yoshihiro.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA Hunter is one who travels the world doing all sorts of dangerous tasks. From capturing criminals to searching deep within uncharted lands for any lost treasures. Gon is a young boy whose father disappeared long ago, being a Hunter. He believes if he could also follow his father's path, he could one day reunite with him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter becoming 12, Gon leaves his home and takes on the task of entering the Hunter exam, notorious for its low success rate and high probability of death to become an official Hunter. He befriends the revenge-driven Kurapika, the doctor-to-be Leorio and the rebellious ex-assassin Killua in the exam, with their friendship prevailing throughout the many trials and threats they come upon taking on the dangerous career of a Hunter.","episodes":148,"format":"TV","id":11061,"idMal":11061,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":89,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/11061","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Hunter x Hunter (2011)","native":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)","romaji":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)","userPreferred":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)"},"trailer":{"id":"d6kBeJjTGnY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/d6kBeJjTGnY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/167152-6QxZG8Dmf1EL.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg"},"description":"In a world where heroism is a punishment, Xylo Forbartz, a condemned goddess killer, battles endless hordes of monstrous abominations as part of Penal Hero Unit 9004. Death is no escape, only a cycle of resurrection and relentless combat. But when Xylo encounters a mysterious new goddess, their unlikely alliance sparks a rebellion that could shatter the chains of eternal punishment.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode aired with a runtime of ~58 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Initially scheduled to air in October, 2025 \u003c/i\u003e","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":167152,"idMal":56009,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/167152","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero","native":"勇者刑に処す　懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"trailer":{"id":"GcRs1JC7xeg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GcRs1JC7xeg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/100994-mEIqjSzFKysR.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png"},"description":"Gabimaru the Hollow is one of the most vicious assassins ever to come out of the ninja village of Iwagakure. He’s ruthlessly efficient, but a betrayal results in him being handed a death sentence. He has only one hope—in order to earn his freedom, he must travel to a long-hidden island and recover an elixir that will make the shogun immortal. Failure is not an option. On this island, heaven and hell are just a hair’s breadth away.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":100994,"idMal":112318,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/100994","startDate":{"day":23,"month":1,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Hell's Paradise","Paradition","Heavenhell","Jigoku Raku","Piekielny Raj","지옥락","สุขาวดีอเวจี"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku","native":"地獄楽","romaji":"Jigokuraku","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku"},"trailer":{"id":"C7iGt19x_F4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/C7iGt19x_F4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128893-pAA7PjY8l7dy.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg"},"description":"The Edo period is nearing its end. Gabimaru, a shinobi formerly known as the strongest in Iwagakure who is now a death row convict, is told that he will be acquitted and set free if he can bring back the Elixir of Life from an island that is rumored to be the Buddhist pure land Sukhavati. In hopes of reuniting with his beloved wife, Gabimaru heads to the island along with the executioner Yamada Asaemon Sagiri. Upon arriving there, they encounter other death row convicts in search of the Elixir of Life... as well as a host of unknown creatures, eerie manmade statues, and the hermits who rule the island. Can Gabimaru find the Elixir of Life on this mysterious island and make it back home alive?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":7,"year":2023},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":128893,"idMal":46569,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/128893","startDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku","สุขาวดีอเวจี","Адский рай"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise","native":"地獄楽","romaji":"Jigokuraku","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku"},"trailer":{"id":"8BIaDDN-r3o","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8BIaDDN-r3o/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166613","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":119118,"name":{"full":"Yuuji Kaku"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":146805,"name":{"full":"Kaori Makita"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":144651,"name":{"full":"Akira Kindaichi"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":105543,"name":{"full":"Kouji Hisaki"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":119687,"name":{"full":"Junichi Higashi"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":158729,"name":{"full":"Ayako Suenaga"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":245503,"name":{"full":"Haruka Juuta"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":118969,"name":{"full":"Yoshiaki Dewa"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":181681,"name":{"full":"Wataru Kawagoe"}},"role":"Animation Producer"},{"node":{"id":161639,"name":{"full":"Tatsuya Kitani"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":373272,"name":{"full":"BABYMETAL"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":161639,"name":{"full":"Tatsuya Kitani"}},"role":"Theme Song Composition (OP)"},{"node":{"id":161639,"name":{"full":"Tatsuya Kitani"}},"role":"Theme Song Lyrics (OP)"},{"node":{"id":161639,"name":{"full":"Tatsuya Kitani"}},"role":"Theme Song Arrangement (OP)"},{"node":{"id":124946,"name":{"full":"Avu-chan"}},"role":"Theme Song Lyrics (ED)"},{"node":{"id":124946,"name":{"full":"Avu-chan"}},"role":"Theme Song Composition (ED)"},{"node":{"id":135580,"name":{"full":"Ziyoou-vachi"}},"role":"Theme Song Arrangement (ED)"},{"node":{"id":159933,"name":{"full":"Kouji Tsukada"}},"role":"Theme Song Arrangement (ED)"},{"node":{"id":135580,"name":{"full":"Ziyoou-vachi"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED)"},{"node":{"id":144651,"name":{"full":"Akira Kindaichi"}},"role":"Script (eps 1-3)"},{"node":{"id":145258,"name":{"full":"Rie Nishimura"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director (ep 1)"},{"node":{"id":146805,"name":{"full":"Kaori Makita"}},"role":"Storyboard (ED, eps 1, 2)"},{"node":{"id":214309,"name":{"full":"Iho Ishikawa"}},"role":"Episode Director (ED)"},{"node":{"id":142258,"name":{"full":"Hajime Ootani"}},"role":"Storyboard (OP)"},{"node":{"id":151952,"name":{"full":"Daisuke Niitsuma"}},"role":"Creature Animation Director (eps 1, 2)"}]},"startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":569,"name":"MAPPA"}]},"trailer":{"id":"JLe_NUnAZVs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JLe_NUnAZVs/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-02T03:43:20.64197+03:00"},"166617":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":83,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":435158,"node":{"id":54223,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","age":"16-20","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["アヤカ・サジョウ","Person A","A氏","A-shi"],"full":"Ayaka Sajyou","native":"沙条綾香"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b54223-CEs1n0hKjakd.png"},"description":"Ayaka Sajyou is a magus living in Fuyuki City attending school at Homurahara Academy. She is also a former student of the El-Melloi Classroom, having attended classes for about a month.\n\n__In Fate/Prototype:__\n\n~!She’s the Master of [Saber](https://anilist.co/character/497) in the Second Tokyo Holy Grail War.!~\n\n__In Fate/strange Fake:__\n\n~!She's the \"True\" Master of [Saber](https://anilist.co/character/127453) in the True and False Holy Grail Wars. Ayaka is recognized by [Thia Escardos](https://anilist.co/character/270568) as a non-human being.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/54223"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":435169,"name":"Saber","node":{"id":127453,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Lionheart","True Saber","Coeur de Lion","Richard the Lionheart","Oc e No"],"full":"Richard I","native":"リチャード一世"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b127453-5hx20va8HGzd.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 178 cm\n\nSaber-class Servant summoned in the \"True and False Holy Grail Wars\" of Fate/strange Fake. His true name is Richard I, also known as Richard the Lionheart.\n\n~!\nHe is the \"True\" Saber-class Servant summoned by [Ayaka Sajyou](https://anilist.co/character/54223/), after usurping the contract from [Cashura](https://anilist.co/character/239478), in the True and False Holy Grail Wars of Fate/strange Fake. He is the Saber of the True Holy Grail War, but there is no \"False Saber\" due to the abnormal nature of the False Holy Grail War.\n!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/127453"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":503499,"node":{"id":87313,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Orlando Reeve","native":"オーランド・リーヴ"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b87313-eqVc91PCWGQu.jpg"},"description":"Orlando Reeve is the police chief of Snowfield and the Master of Caster. He is a magus who has gone to great lengths to prepare for the Holy Grail War. He has known of the ritual, and he is disappointed in the government for their decision to advertise it to outsiders.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/87313"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503507,"name":"Assassin","node":{"id":76520,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Beautiful Assassin","美しき暗殺者","No Name Assassin","Zealot","False Assassin"],"full":"Assassin","native":"アサシン"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b76520-0qLVeJrHS77v.jpg"},"description":"Summoned by Jester Karture as an Assassin in the fake Holy Grail War in Snowfield. She is a former candidate for the position of Hassan-i Sabbah, the pseudonym shared by the leaders of the League of Assassins, the Hashshashin. She was known a particularly faithful girl in a certain country whose existence is referred to as \"merely a story.\" She underwent intense training to earn herself a name, and she was pious to the point in attempting to prove her faith that she was labelled as a \"zealot\" with despise by even those who worshiped the same God. While their group could be called a company of fanatics, her convictions were so beyond the norm that they earned her that title. She did not hate those who disparaged her because she believed the reason she was despised was because of her own immaturity and that her conviction was not firm.\n\nShe wished to become the sect’s leader, which required that she acquire power that could be called Divine Miracles. These Miracles had some unique specifications in that they must all quickly and reliably snuff out the lives of heretics and infidels. The leaders in the past obtained their titles by achieving numerous miracles worthy of bearing the name of the Fallen Angel in the form of Zabaniya, so she continued her mad pursuit of self-improvement incessantly, seeking the miracles that were achieved by her predecessors. She recreated them one by one, but the World seemed to only shout “Still not enough” at her without pause. The other members were shocked by her achievements to the point where they could not believe what had happened. While she had achieved the miracles of all eighteen leaders in the past, no one in the sect acknowledged her right to inherit the leadership. It was her proof, soaked in blood and sweat, and she knew better than everyone what it really took to reach that point.\n\nThe faithfuls began to shun her, telling her that “What you achieved is no different from making copies of old tomes. You have not achieved your own Miracle, because there is still immaturity within you.” While she did lack the ability to innovate, their denial was only half of the reason. They feared her, she who learned all of those techniques in the span of a few years. Their final reasoning was that “You are still too young. We cannot have someone like you bearing the title of our leader.”, and although it was filled with nothing but excuses, she obeyed without question. She simply questioned her own faith, and believed herself to be juvenile in having defiled the secret techniques of their past leaders. She did not blame anyone, but still continued the quest for her own secret technique.\n\n“The Hundred-Faced One,” a man capable of resolving every single situation masterfully, eventually became the nineteenth leader, and upon recognizing his ability, Zabaniya: Delusional Illusion, was one she did not have, she was ashamed of her own immaturity rather than filled with envy. She did not fulfill anything in the end, nor did she receive any acknowledgement. She merely lived as a zealot, and she was not even allowed to be martyred for her faith. She spent her life meaninglessly until the end, but still bore the World no hatred. Still ashamed of her immaturity, she again dove into the whirlpool of faith because she has no emotions to allow her to bear a grudge. The only things she despised were the false idols of infidels, making her a zealot that no normal man could redeem. That is her whole story which merely disappeared into the abyss of history as that of another zealot, and while it should have ended there, it was reborn the instant when the zealot become the False Grail’s chosen.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/76520"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":511872,"node":{"id":221839,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Fillia"],"full":"Philia","native":"フィリア"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b221839-YmaWjSbdft8d.jpg"},"description":"Philia is an Einzbern homunculus involved in the False Holy Grail War of Fate/strange fake. \n\n~!As of the summoning of True Berserker, her body has been possessed by the goddess Ishtar.!~\n\n(Source: TYPE-MOON wiki)","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/221839"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514863,"node":{"id":220379,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","age":"3","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Little Red Riding Hood","*# XX"],"full":"Akazukin","native":"赤ずきん"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b220379-qvgxvNjNGuQy.png"},"description":"She's a resident of Fuyuki City who died in a family suicide in Semina Apartments, whose death has become a ghost story involving \"Mr. A\".\n\n~!In truth, the \"Little Red Riding Hood\" is a Supreme Mystic Code modified as a Magical Energy Reactor. In Fate/Zero, Kayneth El-Melloi Archibald chose to bring \"her\" with him to the Hyatt Hotel. Eventuelly the Little Red Riding Hood and Mr. A fused together becoming the individual known as Ayaka Sajyou.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/220379"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551381,"name":"True Archer","node":{"id":504,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Berserker","バーサーカー","Hercules","Alcides","True Archer","Megalos"],"full":"Heracles","native":"ヘラクレス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b504-2k7LldrHYSAP.png"},"description":"\nIn Fate/Stay Night\n~!The Servant of Illya, he is a swarthy giant with adamantine skin and gross brawn. He wields a colossal stone Axe-Sword, and is capable of causing massive destruction with the mere backlash of his swings. As a Berserker, he was stripped of his sanity and reason, acting feral and animalistic in combat. Berserkers are praised as members of the \"Strongest\" class, though they are difficult to control. Illya, however, appears to have little trouble managing Berserker.!~   ","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/504"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562589,"node":{"id":270573,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Orion","native":"オリオン"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b270573-15doGXFZNEds.png"},"description":"Orion comments that if Watcher's Master happened to have been an attractive woman, he would have \"materialized and made a go of it as a Heroic Spirit.\" He is described as being carefree even while Sigma is in battle with No Name Assassin.\n\n As one of Watcher's Shadows rather than a Heroic Spirit, Orion's appearance does not necessarily correlate to his Heroic Spirit self.\n","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/270573"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562597,"node":{"id":225096,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Halri Vorzak"],"full":"Haruri Borzak","native":"ハルリボルザーク"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b225096-7h59AvL839Fd.jpg"},"description":"Haruri was born into the Magus Borzak clan, where her grandfather Odd Borzak was a noted Magus who eventually became a Dead Apostle while pursuing his research which then eventually lead him to destroy and kill scores of people and even an entire town to create an army of Ghouls, leading him to be hunted by both the Church and the Association for his destructive actions. This eventually lead him to surgically alter his face and change his name in order to hide his identity and constantly change locations to avoid detection. Eventually he was killed by two Freelancers while in a plane, which then left his surviving family to be viciously attacked and ransacked for his research, leaving only Haruri, his granddaughter, as the only survivor.\n\nLeft as the only survivor of the Borzak family, Haruri was taken in by an Unnamed Magus from the Clock Tower who possessed the physical body of a young girl, but had a mind far older. Despite teaching her Magecraft, her teacher did not take her in as her official apprentice and was simply her legal guardian, and therefore, when Haruri made her intention to join the True and False Holy Grail Wars for the sake of her vendetta against the Mage's Association and the World of Magecraft, she could do nothing to stop her and only try to convince her not to get involved with Francesca Prelati due to not being able to forcibly compel her as she was not her apprentice.\n\nHaruri encountered Francesca Prelati while attempting a mystical approach to the United States in pursuit of her goal. She accepted Francesca's deal for a chance to destroy the magical world she hates","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/225096"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503500,"node":{"id":76522,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Tsubaki Kuruoka","native":"繰丘椿"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b76522-hJXdbSEazxji.png"},"description":"Rider's master in the fake Holy Grail War in Snowfield","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/76522"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503508,"name":"Archer","node":{"id":2514,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Archer","King of Heroes","King of Kings","Golden King","King of Babylon","Oldest King","AUO","Gil-kun","Wedge of Heaven"],"full":"Gilgamesh","native":"ギルガメッシュ"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b2514-hnE6LEdqm7Su.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 182 cm\n\nGilgamesh is the King of Uruk, said to have reigned during the Sumer Dynasty in Mesopotamia 5000 years ago. He's the namesake Hero described in the Epic of Gilgamesh, making him the most ancient Hero on which all the others legends were modeled. This grants him the title of King of Heroes and, within his Gates of Babylon, the prototypes of all the Noble Phantasms of the Heroes yet to come. \n\nBorn from the human Lugalbanda, the King of Uruk, and the goddess Rimat-Ninsun, he was a being so perfect and transcendent to the point that he was two-thirds deity and one-third human. He was the chosen one that would guide humanity on the earth that was slowly abandoning the Age of Gods, but instead he grew up to be a selfish and arrogant despot.\n\nHis only friend and being he considered his equal was Enkidu.\n\n__In Fate/Zero:__\n~!\nInitially summoned as the Archer-class Servant of [Tokiomi Toosaka](https://anilist.co/character/16017/Tokiomi-Toosaka) in the 4th Holy Grail War, using the fossil of the first skin ever shed by a snake as a catalyst, he soon becomes bored with his Master and takes interest in Kirei Kotomine. Together they plot to kill Tokiomi and forge a new pact, with Gilgamesh pushing Kotomine to accept his true desires. He also takes interest in Iskandar as a worthy opponent to kill, and in Artoria, a tragic figure to take as his bride. \n\nIn the end, invested by the pollution of the Holy Grail, he is gifted a mortal body and is reincarnated in the world. !~\n\n__In Fate/strange Fake:__\n~!\nWithin the World of Fate/strange Fake, Servant Archer Gilgamesh was previously summoned in the Fourth Fuyuki Holy Grail War and participated in the Fifth Fuyuki Holy Grail War. But the Servant summoned in the False Holy Grail War is a new Servant without any memories of the Fuyuki Holy Grail Wars. \n\nHe is the first Servant summoned in the True and False Holy Grail War as the \"False\" Archer-class Servant of [Thine Chelc](https://anilist.co/character/87307/).\n!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/2514"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":511873,"node":{"id":239479,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Aludra","native":"アルドラ"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b239479-S3SNhBUzkFpC.png"},"description":"Aludra is a subordinate of Faldeus Dioland in the organization managing the True and False Holy Grail Wars of Fate/strange Fake.\n","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/239479"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551382,"node":{"id":158552,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Rocco Belfeban","native":"ロッコ・ベルフェバン"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158552-zvT02LWmCNoN.jpg"},"description":"Head of the Department of Summoning in the Clock Tower.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/158552"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562590,"node":{"id":189144,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["God of Medicine","Hepius","Caster"],"full":"Asclepius","native":"アスクレピオス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b189144-qGIh509xQ9Ce.png"},"description":"He's a hero of Greek myth who studied under [Chiron](https://anilist.co/character/129564) and he was a member of the Argonauts led by [Jason](https://anilist.co/character/203312). Being a child of [Apollo](https://anilist.co/character/222241), he eventually gained the power to resurrect the dead.\n\n__In Fate/Grand Order:__ \n\n~!Asclepius  serves as a Lokapala of [God Arjuna](https://anilist.co/character/175330).!~\n\n__In Fate/strange fake:__ \n\n~!Asclepius is one of seven individuals manifested as [Watcher's](https://anilist.co/character/138622) Shadows. He has the appearance of a young boy in his early teens.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/189144"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562598,"node":{"id":270569,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Captain","native":"船長"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b270569-Y6oDbpqMIFua.png"},"description":"The Captain's True Name is unknown. He is the Shadow of a figure who qualifies as a Heroic Spirit.\n","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/270569"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":443762,"node":{"id":138621,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Hansa Cervantes","native":"ハンザ・セルバンテス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138621-uoe5RNf2XHV4.png"},"description":"He is a member of the Assembly of the Eighth Sacrament. He was sent to Snowfield by the Holy Church as a moderator for the False Holy Grail War.\n\nHansa is a man of Spanish ethnicity and appears in his mid-thirties. Hansa is an unusual looking man with shoulder length, wavy hair and a distinctive eyepatch over his right eye.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/138621"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503501,"name":"Lancer","node":{"id":60059,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Lancer","Chains of Heavens","False Lancer"],"full":"Enkidu","native":"エルキドゥ"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b60059-ErZDIiDz7tKq.png"},"description":"Enkidu is known to be Gilgamesh's only true friend and much like him, they regard their friendship highly. \n\nWhile they may have the appearance of a human they're nothing more than a doll made of mud, shaped and given life by the Gods. Before assuming their current form and acquiring intellect and knowledge, they spent a long time roaming the forests and thus has a deep connection with nature.\n\nThe task given to them was to reprimand Gilgamesh tyrannical behavior and bring him back into the service of the Gods but the might of the two was equal and they developed a tight bond fighting together. \n\n__In Fate/Grand Order - Absolute Demonic Front: Babylonia__\n~!\nEnkidu's corpse, which was buried in the graveyard of the underworld, was taken. Kingu is a chimera created from Enkidu's corpse, although the puppet itself does not find out until later on.\n!~\n\n__In Fate/strange Fake:__\n~!\nClass name, False Lancer, is the \"False\" Lancer-class Servant summoned by the [Wolf](https://anilist.co/character/138619/) in the True and False Holy Grail Wars of Fate/strange Fake.\n!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/60059"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503516,"node":{"id":87321,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Jack the Ripper","False Berserker"],"full":"Berserker","native":"バーサーカー"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/87321-pGFnMVgo41zF.jpg"},"description":"He is the Servant of Flatt Escardos in the Holy Grail War in Snowfield.\n\nHe is the embodiment of the mystery behind the legend of Jack the Ripper. Thus he has no true form, and is capable of shapeshifting into any form he desires.\n\nThe legend is full of madness, which the Berserker class gives to the Servants in its class. So in an odd twist of fate, this Berserker managed to keep his sanity just because had been summoned as a Berserker and not under another class.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/87321"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":511874,"node":{"id":239478,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Cashura","native":"カーシュラ"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b239478-CYzvEopPUFBV.png"},"description":"Cashura is the Master of Saber in the True and False Holy Grail Wars of Fate/strange Fake. He is killed during the summoning process, and Ayaka Sajyou's special Command Spells allow her to usurp the summoning.\n","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/239478"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551383,"node":{"id":220377,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"John Wingard","native":"ジョン・ウィンガード"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b220377-d8xzQZ1RLCzq.png"},"description":"A member of the Clan Calatin, a group of magi policemen in Snowfield, participating in the True and False Holy Grail Wars of Fate/strange Fake.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/220377"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562599,"node":{"id":270567,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Icarus","native":"イーカロス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b270567-XaiRgOer6gH3.png"},"description":"The boy's True Name is unknown. He describes himself as \"an escaped prisoner.\"","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/270567"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":443763,"node":{"id":138590,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["シグマ"],"full":"Sigma"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b138590-pT2mqjfz9GN4.jpg"},"description":"Sigma is the \"true\" Master of Watcher in the False Holy Grail War of Fate/strange Fake.\n\n~!Sigma is the product of rape between [Maiya Hisau](https://anilist.co/character/16020/) and an unknown soldier. He wasn't given a name and was taken away from Maiya when he was a baby.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/138590"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503502,"node":{"id":87319,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Flat Escardos","Idiot Genius"],"full":"Flatt  Escardos","native":"フラット・エスカルドス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b87319-t3o6viRp1ci4.jpg"},"description":"He is the Master of Berserker in the Holy Grail War in Snowfield. \n\nA student at the Clock Tower, the greatest school backed by the Magic Association, he is overcome by a great desire to go see the Holy Grail in Snowfield. While he is talented, he lacks the proper disposition to be a Magus. His teacher is Lord El-Melloi II.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/87319"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":503517,"node":{"id":87299,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Langal"],"full":"Rohngall","native":"ランガル"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/87299-xVRW65pZV8JC.jpg"},"description":"An agent for the Magic Association sent to investigate the rumor of a Holy Grail War beginning to take place in the city of Snowfield, California.\n\n~!At some point in the past, Rohngall took Faldeus Dioland as his student, unaware that the younger man was a spy for the American organization.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/87299"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":511875,"node":{"id":220369,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Quartet Nun #4"],"full":"Katya Kambanellis","native":"カティア・カンバネリス"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b220369-P9rjyHY6iPfC.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/220369"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166617,"meanScore":83,"popularity":59061,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":141,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":5,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":7,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":5,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":7,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/10087-32MFY9VnJQ7I.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx10087-M4Hd9qrHGrXk.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx10087-M4Hd9qrHGrXk.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx10087-M4Hd9qrHGrXk.png"},"description":"With the promise of granting any wish, the omnipotent Holy Grail triggered three wars in the past, each too cruel and fierce to leave a victor. In spite of that, the wealthy Einzbern family is confident that the Fourth Holy Grail War will be different; namely, with a vessel of the Holy Grail now in their grasp. Solely for this reason, the much hated \"Magus Killer\" Kiritsugu Emiya is hired by the Einzberns, with marriage to their only daughter Irisviel as binding contract.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nKiritsugu now stands at the center of a cutthroat game of survival, facing off against six other participants, each armed with an ancient familiar, and fueled by unique desires and ideals. Accompanied by his own familiar, Saber, the notorious mercenary soon finds his greatest opponent in Kirei Kotomine, a priest who seeks salvation from the emptiness within himself in pursuit of Kiritsugu.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nBased on the light novel written by Gen Urobuchi, \u003ci\u003eFate/Zero\u003c/i\u003e depicts the events of the Fourth Holy Grail War—10 years prior to \u003ci\u003eFate/stay night\u003c/i\u003e. Witness a battle royale in which no one is guaranteed to survive.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~48 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":10087,"idMal":10087,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/10087","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Fate/Zero","native":"Fate/Zero","romaji":"Fate/Zero","userPreferred":"Fate/Zero"},"trailer":{"id":"n-7PFiut1HI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n-7PFiut1HI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/106918-rfoPP8HknWAM.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx106918-4T0AdnCg8d64.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx106918-4T0AdnCg8d64.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx106918-4T0AdnCg8d64.jpg"},"description":"Ten years after facing defeat in the Fourth Holy Grail War, Waver Velvet, now Lord El Melloi II, teaches classes at the Clock Tower—the center of education for mages. However, his new status as \"Lord\" comes with a caveat: obey the orders of Reines, the younger sister of the deceased Kayneth El Melloi, until she is old enough to rule the House of El Melloi.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nWaver, along with his mysterious apprentice Gray, takes on a series of cases assigned by Reines and the Mages Association. With each case proving to be more complex than the last, could there be more to the Clock Tower than meets the eye, and what secrets does Reines hide?\n","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":106918,"idMal":38959,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/106918","startDate":{"day":7,"month":7,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Lord El-Melloi II's Case Files {Rail Zeppelin} Grace note","native":"ロード・エルメロイⅡ世の事件簿 {魔眼蒐集列車} Grace note","romaji":"Lord El-Melloi II-sei no Jikenbo: \"Rail Zeppelin\" Grace note","userPreferred":"Lord El-Melloi II-sei no Jikenbo: \"Rail Zeppelin\" Grace note"},"trailer":{"id":"E3w2accrWoU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/E3w2accrWoU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/19603.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a135","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx19603-ycT0pyEgDVQu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx19603-ycT0pyEgDVQu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx19603-ycT0pyEgDVQu.jpg"},"description":"Fuyuki City - a city surrounded by the sea and mountains becomes the setting for an ancient ritual. Seven masters are given control of heroic spirits in order to realize the mythical Holy Grail, which is said to grant its owner any wish. These heroic spirits or servants represent legendary heroes of various classes: \"Saber,\" \"Lancer,\" \"Archer,\" \"Rider,\" \"Caster,\" \"Assassin,\" and \"Berserker.\" Each master will enter into a contract with their chosen servant and battle the others to the death until only one pair remains... This is the \"Holy Grail War.\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe young and capable mage, Rin Tohsaka, prepares for her long-awaited Fifth Holy Grail War to begin... With her servant Archer, Rin enters the Holy Grail War as the sole heir to the prestigious Tohsaka family after her father's death. But when Shirou Emiya, a boy from Rin's school, unwittingly becomes a Master and is fatally wounded in battle, she has no choice but to save him. With Shirou and his servant Saber, Rin sets out to strike down the conspiracies surrounding the Holy Grail War. Will the Holy Grail bless Rin and Shirou's path toward victory or will they be cursed with defeat?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex of America)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes Prologue.\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first, second and last episodes aired with a runtime of ~48 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\n\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":19603,"idMal":22297,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/19603","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Fate/stay night: Unlimited Blade Works","native":"Fate/stay night [Unlimited Blade Works]","romaji":"Fate/stay night: Unlimited Blade Works","userPreferred":"Fate/stay night: Unlimited Blade Works"},"trailer":{"id":"61RuoLIlCUM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/61RuoLIlCUM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2251-FVSbYyJhQPj2.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2251-tTQoWxVy4472.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2251-tTQoWxVy4472.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx2251-tTQoWxVy4472.jpg"},"description":"During the early 1930s in Chicago, the transcontinental train, Flying Pussyfoot, is starting its legendary journey that will leave a trail of blood all over the country. At the same time in New York, the ambitious scientist Szilard and his unwilling aide Ennis, are looking for missing bottles of the immortality elixir. In addition, a war between the mafia groups is getting worse. On board the Advena Avis, in 1711, alchemists are about to learn the price of immortality.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nBased on the award winning light novels of the same name, this anime adaptation follows several events that initially seem unrelated, both in time and place, but are part of a much bigger story\u0026mdash;one of alchemy, survival and immortality. Merging these events together are the kindhearted would-be thieves, Isaac and Miria, connecting various people, all of them with their own hidden ambitions and agendas, and creating lifelong bonds and consequences for everyone involved.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":2251,"idMal":2251,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2251","startDate":{"day":27,"month":7,"year":2007},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Baccano!","native":"バッカーノ！","romaji":"Baccano!","userPreferred":"Baccano!"},"trailer":{"id":"MtuNdtfMlJ0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MtuNdtfMlJ0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2593-4TD2W9Zk693v.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e44343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2593-FsRHa8PIl2OJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2593-FsRHa8PIl2OJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx2593-FsRHa8PIl2OJ.jpg"},"description":"September, 1998: In the city where Shiki lives, something triggers a spate of mysterious schoolgirl suicides. The connection between the girls who've leapt to their deaths is unclear, although all of them have jumped from the Fujou Building, a skyscraper scheduled to be demolished.\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n(Source: Aniplex USA)","episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","id":2593,"idMal":2593,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2593","startDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2007},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"the Garden of sinners Chapter 1: Thanatos. (Overlooking View)","native":"空の境界 俯瞰風景","romaji":"Kara no Kyoukai: Fukan Fuukei","userPreferred":"Kara no Kyoukai: Fukan Fuukei"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/6746-84oNA7P9pboV.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d6ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx6746-3LTwM95Uqeoa.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx6746-3LTwM95Uqeoa.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx6746-3LTwM95Uqeoa.png"},"description":"In Tokyo's downtown district of Ikebukuro, amidst many strange rumors and warnings of anonymous gangs and dangerous occupants, one urban legend stands out above the rest—the existence of a headless \"Black Rider\" who is said to be seen driving a jet-black motorcycle through the city streets.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nRyuugamine Mikado has always longed for the excitement of the city life, and an invitation from a childhood friend convinces him to move to Tokyo. Witnessing the Black Rider on his first day in the city, his wishes already seem to have been granted. But as supernatural events begin to occur, ordinary citizens like himself, along with Ikebukuro's most colorful inhabitants, are mixed up in the commotion breaking out in their city.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":6746,"idMal":6746,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/6746","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2010},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Durarara!!","native":"デュラララ!!","romaji":"Durarara!!","userPreferred":"Durarara!!"},"trailer":{"id":"q5qlX4lWst0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/q5qlX4lWst0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/103275-9vSzr7YzbXQb.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5d78e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx103275-SN0wwshS3tWA.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx103275-SN0wwshS3tWA.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx103275-SN0wwshS3tWA.jpg"},"description":"A seventh Singularity has been discovered in ancient Mesopotamia in the year 2655 B.C.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe land of Uruk, governed by the wise King Gilgamesh after he returned from his quest for immortality, was grand and prosperous until three goddesses and countless Demonic Beasts appeared. These enemies have brought Uruk to the brink of destruction. With a Rayshift—a method of traveling across both time and space—Fujimaru and Mash journey to the land of Uruk, where they encounter the fortress city of Uruk and the Absolute Demonic Front, where a terrible battle against the fearsome onslaught of the Demonic Beasts rages. There, the citizens of Uruk, who live their lives to the fullest despite facing an existential threat, continue to fight for their future. Deities and Demonic Beasts attack with terrifying force, and mankind pushes back with all its might... This is the era where humans and gods are destined to part ways.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nFujimaru and Mash, the pair who have fought through all six previous Singularities, embark on their final battle.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex of America)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Based on the Babylonia Singularity of Fate/Grand Order, the Japanese smartphone role-playing game created by Delight Works based on the Fate series by Type-Moon.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":21,"format":"TV","id":103275,"idMal":38084,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/103275","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Fate/Grand Order Absolute Demonic Front: Babylonia","native":"Fate/Grand Order -絶対魔獣戦線バビロニア-","romaji":"Fate/Grand Order: Zettai Majuu Sensen Babylonia","userPreferred":"Fate/Grand Order: Zettai Majuu Sensen Babylonia"},"trailer":{"id":"ZE34_tkqFwU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZE34_tkqFwU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98035-hbrEf8ulDnAe.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#784328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx98035-rdkjeqUUsG2j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx98035-rdkjeqUUsG2j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx98035-rdkjeqUUsG2j.jpg"},"description":"There was once a Holy Grail War waged by Mages and Heroic Spirits in a town of Fuyuki. However, one Mage took advantage of the chaos of World War II to steal a Holy Grail. Several decades have passed, and the Yggdmillennia family, who took upon the Holy Grail as its symbol, defected from the Mages' Association. Furious, the Association sent forces to deal with the Yggdmillennia, but were defeated. With the Holy Grail system changed, war at an unprecedented scale breaks out.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":98035,"idMal":34662,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/98035","startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Fate/Apocrypha","native":"Fate/Apocrypha","romaji":"Fate/Apocrypha","userPreferred":"Fate/Apocrypha"},"trailer":{"id":"c2r3sF9vAGs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/c2r3sF9vAGs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":86753,"idMal":83923,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86753","status":"RELEASING","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/86753-J0xAuASfT348.jpg","synonyms":["フェイト/ストレンジフェイク","페이트 스트레인지 페이크"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":81,"description":"The plot centers around a Grail War faultily copied from the Third Holy Grail War in Fuyuki. After the end of the third Grail War, an organization from the United States that has magi separate from the London based Mage Association as members took data from Fuyuki's Grail War and planned their own ritual. After seventy years, they used the city Snowfield as the Sacred Land for their own Grail War. They were unable to successfully copy every aspect of the ritual, which lead to it acting only as an imitation that has lost the Saber class and allowed for the summoning of strange Servants due to the definition of a \"hero\" being blurred.","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy","Supernatural"],"title":{"native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2015},"endDate":{}},"relationType":"ALTERNATIVE"},{"node":{"id":50006,"idMal":83903,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/50006","status":"RELEASING","type":"MANGA","format":"NOVEL","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/50006-9feJaDhW14aS.jpg","synonyms":["フェイト/ストレンジフェイク","Fake/states night","페이트 스트레인지 페이크"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":86,"description":"The stage: the city of Snowfield in the western U.S., far from Fuyuki. There, a \"false Holy Grail War\", quite unlike the original Holy Grail War, unfolds. There were those who had been keeping an eye on the auguries of the Holy Grail in Snowfield. According to an investigation by the Mage's Association, the Holy Grail War system in Snowfield was an imitation of the one in Fuyuki. What's more, the system was incomplete, leading to the exclusion of one of the seven classes and the selection of beings as Servants who ordinarily could not be summoned. It was, verily, a strange fake. As an organ of the U.S. government executes its various plots, the Servants are summoned one after another...","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"title":{"native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e44350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2015},"endDate":{}},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"id":154966,"idMal":53127,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/154966","status":"FINISHED","season":"SUMMER","type":"ANIME","format":"SPECIAL","seasonYear":2023,"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/154966-xIvcAtzwOZk6.jpg","episodes":1,"synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка. Шёпот рассвета"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":81,"description":"Years after the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan, strange reports surface of one appearing in America. Attracting new Mages and Servants, the question is raised about the relic’s authenticity. As the city of Snowfield is turned into a bloody battleground, specific details seem wrong. Is it possible someone is manipulating this twisted little play, and if so, does this mean the true Holy Grail exists?\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Special premiere occurred in Los Angeles at Anime Expo before the Japanese television premiere on July 2, 2023.\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"duration":55,"trailer":{"id":"dQOtt9tW0F4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dQOtt9tW0F4/hqdefault.jpg"},"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake -Whispers of Dawn-","native":"Fate/strange Fake -Whispers of Dawn-","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake: Whispers of Dawn","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake: Whispers of Dawn"},"coverImage":{"color":"#50c9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png"},"startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2023},"endDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2023}},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":97582,"name":{"full":"Type-Moon"}},"role":"Original Story"},{"node":{"id":97948,"name":{"full":"Ryougo Narita"}},"role":"Original Story"},{"node":{"id":109963,"name":{"full":"Shizuki Morii"}},"role":"Original Character Design"},{"node":{"id":119966,"name":{"full":"Mineji Sakamoto"}},"role":"Original Character Design Assistance"},{"node":{"id":128243,"name":{"full":"Shun Enokido"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":131945,"name":{"full":"Takahito Sakazume"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":189703,"name":{"full":"Daisuke Oohigashi"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":121788,"name":{"full":"Yuukei Yamada"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":122078,"name":{"full":"Masaaki Takiyama"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":208083,"name":{"full":"Kou Aine"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":131207,"name":{"full":"Yurie Hama"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":117599,"name":{"full":"Oka Okazaki"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":131197,"name":{"full":"Kazuma Tanaka"}},"role":"Prop Design"},{"node":{"id":254629,"name":{"full":"Yuuto Kajino"}},"role":"Monster Design"},{"node":{"id":131510,"name":{"full":"Shinpei Wada"}},"role":"Monster Design"},{"node":{"id":148253,"name":{"full":"Keigo Arihara"}},"role":"Visual Board"},{"node":{"id":129578,"name":{"full":"Hakuyu Go"}},"role":"Noble Phantasms Design"},{"node":{"id":118616,"name":{"full":"Ayu Kawamoto"}},"role":"Art Director (eps 1-6)"},{"node":{"id":148363,"name":{"full":"Yuuki Hatakeyama"}},"role":"Art Director (eps 1-6)"},{"node":{"id":118445,"name":{"full":"Kazuo Ogura"}},"role":"Art Board"},{"node":{"id":118449,"name":{"full":"Hideyasu Narita"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":186144,"name":{"full":"Sayaka Itabashi"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":160967,"name":{"full":"Ayumi Sugimoto"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":145990,"name":{"full":"Masayuki Niizuma"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":230135,"name":{"full":"Mikiya Hiragi"}},"role":"Art Design"}]},"startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":561,"name":"A-1 Pictures"}]},"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T05:59:22.391066+03:00"},"167152":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":79,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":520740,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The former captain of the Federated Kingdom's Fifth Order of the Holy Knights and the now de facto leader of Penal Hero Unit 9004. He was sentenced to be a hero for the crime of killing the goddess [Senerva](https://anilist.co/character/387992/Senerva). He would later meet and reluctantly make a contract with [Teoritta](https://anilist.co/character/355726), the \"Goddess of Swords\".","gender":"Male","id":355722,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b355722-WiobumP5f1Qx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Xylo Forbartz","native":"ザイロ・フォルバーツ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/355722"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":520744,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The Sword Goddess who made a contract with [Xylo](https://anilist.co/character/355722/Xylo-Forbartz). She summons numerous swords, including holy swords and demon swords. While possessing a high sense of self-worth and a fondness for being praised, she also exhibits a characteristic goddess-like trait of engaging in self-sacrificing actions.","gender":"Female","id":355726,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b355726-PzgGZOHK5X8v.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Teoritta","native":"テオリッタ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/355726"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":551654,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"An eccentric who volunteered to become a Hero, he possesses a talent for artillery. He has a polite demeanor and speaks like a saint, but he always wears a suspicious smile. His bizarre armor encases his entire body, engraved with holy symbols, and his enormous right arm functions as a cannon barrel.","gender":"Male","id":382390,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382390-WdFXyLCx6ASe.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rhyno","native":"ライノー"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382390"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565496,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":392248,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b392248-ARjfEcfBVjq3.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Iri","native":"イリ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/392248"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":566137,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":392867,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Higedzura","native":"髭面"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/392867"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":520741,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The commander of the Punisher Heroes Squad 9004. He is a rare conman who attempted to sell off the royal palace to a circus. His eloquence and deception skills make him appear competent at first glance, but in reality he's a weakling with no guts. He always delivers \"bad news\" in a hurry.","gender":"Male","id":355723,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b355723-N6dEyV3gwMet.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Venetim Leopool","native":"ベネティム・レオプール"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/355723"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551655,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The daughter of the Mastibolt family, the leader of the Southern Night Demons. Formerly engaged to [Xylo](https://anilist.co/character/355722/Xylo-Forbartz), their engagement was annulled when he became a Hero, but she refuses to acknowledge that she broke off her engagement with him. Her expression remains unchanged as she utters harsh words.","gender":"Female","id":382391,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382391-MqWJ4Ek9qZGM.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Renzari"],"full":"Frenci Mastibolt","native":"フレンシィ・マスティボルト"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382391"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559082,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387976,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387976-ASIG2xTsxwi4.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Koufuchou","native":"坑夫長"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387976"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":520742,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Captain of the 13th Holy Knights. She was originally supposed to make a pact with the Goddess [Teoritta](https://anilist.co/character/355726/Teoritta). She is a serious and righteous holy knight, but can also be strict and harsh in her words. She is willing to sacrifice her own life and the life of the hero for the Goddess.","gender":"Female","id":355724,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b355724-aVkx1o6ClJpx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Patausche Kivia","native":"パトーシェ・キヴィア"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/355724"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557111,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A terrorist who believed himself to be the true king of the United Kingdom and carried out a large-scale terrorist act against the royal family. Nicknamed \"His Majesty.\" Although he displays an arrogant attitude, his concern for his people is genuine. He possesses exceptional talent in the art of Sacred Seal Tuning, which engraves sacred symbols.","gender":"Male","id":360742,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360742-7hfqRRLdq4Zx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["His Majesty"],"full":"Norgalle Senridge","native":"ノルガユ・センリッジ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360742"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559075,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387967,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387967-DOZoVayr9gj8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Simreed Colmadino","native":"シムリード・コルマディノ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387967"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":564058,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":391272,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b391272-bYJcFSeQ2o4p.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Boojum","native":"ブージャム"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/391272"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":520743,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"An unparalleled petty thief, responsible for over a thousand thefts. He impulsively attempts to steal anything, from the Goddess's coffin to completely meaningless objects, and possesses the skill to actually steal anything. He has excellent low-light vision and is sensitive to presences, but is extremely timid.","gender":"Male","id":355725,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b355725-2vLrWMLNXytR.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Dotta Luzulas","native":"ドッタ・ルズラス"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/355725"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557112,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A berserker who has been a member of the Hero Squad longer than anyone else. Because he has been resurrected as a hero so many times, he has lost his sense of self and the ability to think, and is unable to speak. His true identity and everything else about him are shrouded in mystery. His close combat abilities are monstrous, and he wields a giant battle axe as easily as a kitchen knife.","gender":"Male","id":360741,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360741-br5UdxTcXq1f.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tatsuya","native":"タツヤ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360741"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":564059,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":391273,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b391273-jPh0sAA81K3A.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shiji Bau","native":"シジ・バウ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/391273"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559058,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387953,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387953-suMCn8bvdgeo.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rajit Heathrow","native":"ラジート・ヒスロー"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387953"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":538874,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A former elite assassin raised by an assassination cult. He possesses supernatural-level sniping abilities, but during his time as an assassin, he would develop empathy for his targets, preventing him from killing them, and would instead turn innocent people into \"mincemeat\" to cover up his losses. He's easygoing and talkative, and loves gambling.","gender":"Male","id":370733,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b370733-hIA6qSW42SlT.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tsav","native":"ツァーヴ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/370733"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559059,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387954,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387954-dsmVs5Sj9zhH.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Zofflec Ostbiche","native":"ゾフレク・オストビシュ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387954"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":561948,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":389680,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389680-uUJRoT2FQIei.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Hord Clivios","native":"ホード・クリヴィオス"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389680"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":543266,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A female dragon who races alongside [Jayce](https://anilist.co/character/375408/Jayce-Patiract) on the battlefield. She possesses vibrant blue scales and can unleash powerful flames from her mouth. Because Jayce is loved by the dragon, she can sometimes become jealous and upset. According to Jayce, her dark eyes and strong will are her charms.","gender":"Female","id":375407,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b375407-1ROaWvWjtluz.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Neely","native":"ニーリィ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/375407"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559060,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":387955,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387955-ikvgHnqJJVli.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Siena","native":"シエナ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387955"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560331,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Captain of the 12th Order of the Holy Knights.","gender":"Male","id":388812,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388812-IrRtxafmu0xS.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kafzen Dakrom","native":"カフゼン・ダクローム"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388812"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":561949,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is known as the Goddess of Poisons.","gender":"Female","id":389681,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389681-sC6aNC1gA1n2.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Pelmerry","native":"ぺルメリィ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389681"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565494,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A High Priest and [Patausche's](https://anilist.co/character/355724) uncle.","gender":"Male","id":392244,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b392244-sglaWULkt4pF.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Marlen Kivia","native":"マーレン・キヴィア"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/392244"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":543267,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A dragoon who rides a dragon and soars through the skies as the unit's aerial force. He is also skilled in spearmanship. Not only can he communicate with dragons, but he also has an abnormally endearing disposition. He himself is only interested in dragons and is unfriendly towards humans.","gender":"Male","id":375408,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b375408-lOwWlfpHXgG3.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Jayce Patiract","native":"ジェイス・パーチラクト"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/375408"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"In a world where heroism is a punishment, Xylo Forbartz, a condemned goddess killer, battles endless hordes of monstrous abominations as part of Penal Hero Unit 9004. Death is no escape, only a cycle of resurrection and relentless combat. But when Xylo encounters a mysterious new goddess, their unlikely alliance sparks a rebellion that could shatter the chains of eternal punishment.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode aired with a runtime of ~58 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Initially scheduled to air in October, 2025 \u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":167152,"meanScore":80,"popularity":99822,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":342,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":11,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":4,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":11,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":4,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178869-ZFn0hKphaLtk.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e43528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178869-qiEz0gQD8H5N.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178869-qiEz0gQD8H5N.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178869-qiEz0gQD8H5N.png"},"description":"The story centers on the titular Clevatess, the lord of Dark Beasts, who wields both uncanny intellect and destructive power. Frustrated by the 13 heroes tasked to destroy him, he has decided to be rid of humanity once and for all. However, he has been charged with one nuisance: he revived a hero he personally slayed and adopts an orphaned humanoid baby—the last hope to save a dying world. The world stands upon the brink of Armageddon, with the obligation of raising one child holding it all back. Now bound together, what fate awaits this unlikely trio?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network, Crunchyroll, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~46 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":178869,"idMal":59205,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178869","startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Clevatess","native":"クレバテス-魔獣の王と赤子と屍の勇者","romaji":"Clevatess: Majuu no Ou to Akago to Kabane no Yuusha","userPreferred":"Clevatess: Majuu no Ou to Akago to Kabane no Yuusha"},"trailer":{"id":"sX4o5OODMqQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sX4o5OODMqQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116589-SqwYWzaZCdD5.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#bbd6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx116589-qT34qzsZtk9V.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx116589-qT34qzsZtk9V.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx116589-qT34qzsZtk9V.jpg"},"description":"Called “Juggernaut,” these are the unmanned combat drones developed by the Republic of San Magnolia in answer to the attacks by the autonomous unmanned drones of the neighboring Empire of Giad, the “Legion”. But they’re only unmanned in name. In reality, they are piloted by the Eighty-sixers—those considered to be less than human and treated as mere tools.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nDetermined to achieve his own mysterious ends, Shin, the captain of Spearhead Squadron, which is comprised of Eighty-sixers, continues to fight a hopeless war on a battlefield where only death awaits him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":11,"format":"TV","id":116589,"idMal":41457,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/116589","startDate":{"day":11,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"86 EIGHTY-SIX","native":"86－エイティシックス－","romaji":"86: Eighty Six","userPreferred":"86: Eighty Six"},"trailer":{"id":"VSdS29SDvn4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VSdS29SDvn4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128893-pAA7PjY8l7dy.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg"},"description":"The Edo period is nearing its end. Gabimaru, a shinobi formerly known as the strongest in Iwagakure who is now a death row convict, is told that he will be acquitted and set free if he can bring back the Elixir of Life from an island that is rumored to be the Buddhist pure land Sukhavati. In hopes of reuniting with his beloved wife, Gabimaru heads to the island along with the executioner Yamada Asaemon Sagiri. Upon arriving there, they encounter other death row convicts in search of the Elixir of Life... as well as a host of unknown creatures, eerie manmade statues, and the hermits who rule the island. Can Gabimaru find the Elixir of Life on this mysterious island and make it back home alive?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":128893,"idMal":46569,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/128893","startDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise","native":"地獄楽","romaji":"Jigokuraku","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku"},"trailer":{"id":"8BIaDDN-r3o","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8BIaDDN-r3o/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/108465-RgsRpTMhP9Sv.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#35a1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx108465-1ANspF1EWyFx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx108465-1ANspF1EWyFx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx108465-1ANspF1EWyFx.jpg"},"description":"When a 34-year-old underachiever gets run over by a bus, his story doesn’t end there. Reincarnated in a new world as an infant, Rudeus will seize every opportunity to live the life he’s always wanted. Armed with new friends, some freshly acquired magical abilities, and the courage to do the things he’s always dreamed of, he’s embarking on an epic adventure—with all of his past experience intact!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The anime pre-screened its 1st and 2nd episode starting on the 27th of December on the Nico Nico Live Broadcasting and D Anime Store services\u003ci/\u003e","episodes":11,"format":"TV","id":108465,"idMal":39535,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/108465","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation","native":"無職転生 ～異世界行ったら本気だす～","romaji":"Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu","userPreferred":"Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu"},"trailer":{"id":"JoS7Z8MCD6E","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JoS7Z8MCD6E/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99263-IwkmdCTsDY1t.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx99263-LcazQwdlWzMy.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx99263-LcazQwdlWzMy.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx99263-LcazQwdlWzMy.jpg"},"description":"Naofumi Iwatani, an uncharismatic Otaku who spends his days on games and manga, suddenly finds himself summoned to a parallel universe! He discovers he is one of four heroes equipped with legendary weapons and tasked with saving the world from its prophesied destruction. As the Shield Hero, the weakest of the heroes, all is not as it seems. Naofumi is soon alone, penniless, and betrayed. With no one to turn to, and nowhere to run, he is left with only his shield. Now, Naofumi must rise to become the legendary Shield Hero and save the world!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote:\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode was pre-aired on December 27th, 2018. Regular broadcast began on January 9th, 2019.\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode aired with a runtime of ~47 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":99263,"idMal":35790,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/99263","startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Rising of the Shield Hero","native":"盾の勇者の成り上がり","romaji":"Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari","userPreferred":"Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari"},"trailer":{"id":"VKYmpq-V3Rs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VKYmpq-V3Rs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/33-g7HwYRVm0ZkN.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e49350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx33-PSwfE5B0gejI.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx33-PSwfE5B0gejI.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx33-PSwfE5B0gejI.jpg"},"description":"Set during a time that very much resembles Europe during the Middle Ages, \u003ci\u003eBerserk\u003c/i\u003e is a story of revenge set in the castle town of Midland. Recently, the town has seen the rise of a wicked king, who uses demonic minions to control and victimise his subjects.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nHowever, when a lone soldier enters the town calling himself the Black Swordsman and armed to the teeth, many sense that the king's days of unchecked oppression are over. Soon, the Black Swordsman is plying his trade by hunting down the king's evil servants, giving no quarter, and preparing to exact his vengeance on the king.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MVM Entertainment)","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":33,"idMal":33,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/33","startDate":{"day":7,"month":10,"year":1997},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Berserk","native":"剣風伝奇ベルセルク","romaji":"Kenpuu Denki Berserk","userPreferred":"Kenpuu Denki Berserk"},"trailer":{"id":"odIwkGztmcc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/odIwkGztmcc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21613-FGAqKSTvfxuA.png","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21613-qT3NiwYP5dYc.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21613-qT3NiwYP5dYc.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21613-qT3NiwYP5dYc.png"},"description":"The novel series centers on a young girl who fights on the frontlines in war. She has blonde hair, blue eyes, and nearly transparent white skin, and she flies through the air and mercilessly strikes down her opponents. Her name is Tanya Degurechaff, and she speaks with a young girl's lisp and commands the army. Tanya used to be one of Japan's elite office workers, but because of a wrathful god, was reborn as a little girl. Tanya prioritizes optimization and career advancement above all, and she will become the most dangerous entity among the Imperial Army's sorcerers.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":21613,"idMal":32615,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21613","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Saga of Tanya the Evil","native":"幼女戦記","romaji":"Youjo Senki","userPreferred":"Youjo Senki"},"trailer":{"id":"JwaruTPKq9I","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JwaruTPKq9I/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/16498-8jpFCOcDmneX.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a143","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx16498-buvcRTBx4NSm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx16498-buvcRTBx4NSm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx16498-buvcRTBx4NSm.jpg"},"description":"Several hundred years ago, humans were nearly exterminated by titans. Titans are typically several stories tall, seem to have no intelligence, devour human beings and, worst of all, seem to do it for the pleasure rather than as a food source. A small percentage of humanity survived by walling themselves in a city protected by extremely high walls, even taller than the biggest of titans.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nFlash forward to the present and the city has not seen a titan in over 100 years. Teenage boy Eren and his foster sister Mikasa witness something horrific as the city walls are destroyed by a colossal titan that appears out of thin air. As the smaller titans flood the city, the two kids watch in horror as their mother is eaten alive. Eren vows that he will murder every single titan and take revenge for all of mankind.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n(Source: MangaHelpers) ","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":16498,"idMal":16498,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/16498","startDate":{"day":7,"month":4,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Attack on Titan","native":"進撃の巨人","romaji":"Shingeki no Kyojin","userPreferred":"Shingeki no Kyojin"},"trailer":{"id":"LHtdKWJdif4\t","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LHtdKWJdif4\t/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f16b35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg"},"description":"Heroism—a punishment for only the worst criminals. Those sentenced to the fate of a hero are forced to fight at the front lines against the demon king’s army—and if they die, all they can expect is to be revived and continue the battle. But when their leader, convicted of killing a goddess, meets another goddess himself, the contract they forge may be enough to change the world…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{},"format":"NOVEL","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":142687,"idMal":156106,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/142687","startDate":{"day":17,"month":9,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sentenced to Brave Punishment"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero","native":"勇者刑に処す　懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"trailer":{"id":"nKYGfmykWCE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/nKYGfmykWCE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#863528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg"},"description":"Sinned heroes will save this world...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nBeing sentenced to Heroship was the most severe punishment one could be given. Heroes would be sent to the frontline of a never-ending battle against the demon lords. Not even death could relieve them on their duty.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThere was no end to prison sentence. Even if they fought for a hundred years, they would still not be released. Only by killing every last demon lord would they be pardoned for their crimes. And...that was no more than a pipe dream. However, things might be different for XYRO, Penal Hero Unit 9004. He accidentally meets a goddess...and she asks him to be her knight!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: KADOKAWA Global)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":164543,"idMal":151361,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/164543","startDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sentenced to Brave Punishment","Punishment for Brave Hero: 9004 Corps Prison Record","Sentenced to Hero Punishment: The Service Records of the 9004th Penitent Hero Corps"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero: The Prison Records of Penal Hero Unit 9004","native":"勇者刑に処す 懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"ALTERNATIVE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/167152","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":185310,"name":{"full":"Rocket  Shoukai"}},"role":"Original Story"},{"node":{"id":161193,"name":{"full":"Hitomi Shizuki"}},"role":"Original Illustration"},{"node":{"id":152776,"name":{"full":"Hiroyuki Takashima"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":148064,"name":{"full":"Yoshiki Nakakouji"}},"role":"Assistant Director"},{"node":{"id":121054,"name":{"full":"Kenta Ihara"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":157393,"name":{"full":"Takeru Noda"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":131205,"name":{"full":"Kouta Sugawa"}},"role":"Prop Design"},{"node":{"id":148064,"name":{"full":"Yoshiki Nakakouji"}},"role":"Creature Design"},{"node":{"id":131205,"name":{"full":"Kouta Sugawa"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":146742,"name":{"full":"Hayato Kurosaki"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":154923,"name":{"full":"Kouki Shikiji"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":239541,"name":{"full":"Ryuuken Toida"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":258856,"name":{"full":"Wataru Hirabayashi"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":120020,"name":{"full":"Nobutaka Ike"}},"role":"World Design"},{"node":{"id":123422,"name":{"full":"Shunsuke Takizawa"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":107707,"name":{"full":"SPYAIR"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance"},{"node":{"id":121054,"name":{"full":"Kenta Ihara"}},"role":"Script (eps 1-3)"},{"node":{"id":151477,"name":{"full":"Eiri Yasukawa"}},"role":"Episode Director (ep 1)"},{"node":{"id":152776,"name":{"full":"Hiroyuki Takashima"}},"role":"Episode Director (ep 1)"},{"node":{"id":153390,"name":{"full":"Taisuke Tsukuda"}},"role":"Episode Director (ep 1)"},{"node":{"id":152776,"name":{"full":"Hiroyuki Takashima"}},"role":"Storyboard (OP, eps 1-3)"},{"node":{"id":147919,"name":{"full":"Masaru Obata"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director (eps 1-3)"},{"node":{"id":157393,"name":{"full":"Takeru Noda"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director (ep 1)"},{"node":{"id":164481,"name":{"full":"Yasutaka Kimura"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director (eps 1, 2)"},{"node":{"id":256856,"name":{"full":"Pinchiao Tseng"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director (ep 1)"}]},"startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":6312,"name":"Studio KAI"}]},"trailer":{"id":"GcRs1JC7xeg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GcRs1JC7xeg/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-06T05:09:30.865368+03:00"},"172463":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":84,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":464565,"node":{"age":"15","dateOfBirth":{"day":20,"month":3,"year":2003},"description":"**Species:** Human\n**Height:** 173 cm (5'8\")\n**Occupation:** Sorcerer, Student, Vessel\n**Affiliation:** Jujutsu High\n\nYuuji is a fair person who cares greatly for not only his comrades but anyone he views as people with their own wills, despite how deep or shallow his connection to them is. He cares greatly for the \"value of a life\" and to this end, he will ensure that others receive a \"proper death.\" He is easy to anger in the face of pure cruelty and unfair judgment of other people.\nHe doesn't have the born talent required to use cursed techniques, but he has incredible athletic abilities and he is considered very strong for his age, as shown by when he easily beat a coach in Steel Ball Throw.","gender":"Male","id":127212,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b127212-FVm2tD0erQ5B.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Sukuna's Vessel","The Tiger of West Junior High"],"full":"Yuuji Itadori","native":"虎杖悠仁"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/127212"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":464566,"node":{"age":"16-17","dateOfBirth":{"day":7,"month":3,"year":2001},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Occupation:__ Sorcerer, Student\n__Affiliation:__ Jujutsu High\n__Grade:__ Special Grade Sorcerer\n\nThe main protagonist of Jujutsu Kaisen prequel series [Tokyo Metropolitan Curse Technical School](https://anilist.co/manga/105469/Tokyo-Toritsu-Jujutsu-Kodo-Senmon-Gakko). He was initially a Special Grade Cursed Victim haunted by his late childhood friend, Rika Orimoto. [Satoru Gojou](https://anilist.co/character/127691/Satoru-Gojou) mentored Yuuta and enrolled him at Tokyo Jujutsu High.","gender":"Male","id":129571,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b129571-GHJk7gviHOOw.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yuta Okkotsu"],"full":"Yuuta Okkotsu","native":"乙骨憂太"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/129571"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":464580,"node":{"age":"15","dateOfBirth":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2002},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 175 cm (5'9\")\n__Occupation:__ Sorcerer, Student\n__Affiliation:__ Jujutsu High\n__Grade:__ Grade 2 Sorcerer\n__Cursed Technique:__ 10 Shadows\n\nMegumi is the deuteragonist of the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He is a first-year student at Jujutsu High and also a descendant of the Zenin Family.\n\nWhile outwardly stoic and calculating, Megumi wishes to help protect people he sees as good or kind. He believes that the world is unfair and that a Sorcerer is a tool to ensure kind people are given more chances to live. Claiming it to be his selfish and irrational desire, he does not see himself as a hero for doing this.","gender":"Male","id":126635,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b126635-L0y3I92JSUkN.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Sea Urchin Head"],"full":"Megumi Fushiguro","native":"伏黒恵"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/126635"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":542906,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":20,"month":1},"description":"__Height:__ 170 cm (5'7\")\n\nMai Zenin is the younger twin sister of [Maki Zenin](https://anilist.co/character/134167/Maki-Zenin). Mai is a grade 3 sorcerer and a second-year at Kyoto Jujutsu Technical High School. As a child, Mai always relied on Maki since she was afraid of Cursed Spirits. \n\n~!Because Mai and Maki are monozygotic twins, their strength is considerably limited to one another. Monozygotic twins are considered as a single individual in the Jujutsu world and are a sign of bad omen.!~\n\n~!In chapter 149, Mai decides to sacrifice herself in order to make Maki stronger.!~","gender":"Female","id":134168,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b134168-FdWz5w2LqpeF.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mai Zenin","native":"禪院真依"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/134168"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553024,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Hana is a young girl with as light colored eyes and short light hair with bangs that curve inward. She wears a large turtleneck sweater, dark pants and heeled ankle boots. She appears to have a halo and a pair of wings. ","gender":"Female","id":220724,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b220724-PiTAVLDqbWQn.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Angel"],"full":"Hana Kurusu","native":"来栖華"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/220724"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558719,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is a member of the Zenin Family and its elite unit of jujutsu sorcerers, the Hei.","gender":"Male","id":229953,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b229953-wzhSuoKTdCnu.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Chōjurō"],"full":"Choujurou Zenin","native":"禪院長寿郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/229953"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":561869,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Shikigami that act as the interface of the Culling Game, serving as the liaison between the player and the game.\n\nEach Culling Game player receives a Kogane that services them as their main point of contact with the Culling Game. It goes over the rules with each player and tells them every time they've scored points. Any non-players who decide to declare participation will need to confirm with Kogane upon entering a barrier colony. Kogane also allows the players to contact the game master in order to negotiate new rules. Kogane will announce newly added rules to their players in a different voice than when acting as a liaison for a player.","id":389616,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389616-0bs7Dwj671HU.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kogane","native":"コガネ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389616"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563077,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Rin Amai is a minor character in the Jujutsu Kaisen series. ~!He was a citizen of Sendai City until he was involuntarily turned into a sorcerer by [Kenjaku](https://anilist.co/character/289584/Kenjaku) and forced to participate in the Culling Game.!~","gender":"Male","id":306187,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b306187-D2R4Z0Htjply.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rin Amai","native":"甘井凛"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/306187"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":548882,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Tengen, often referred to as Master Tengen is a supporting character in Jujutsu Kaisen. They are an immortal jujutsu sorcerer that remains within their chamber; the Tombs of the Star Corridor at all times in order to reinforce the barriers that protect both Jujutsu High locations.\n\nMaster Tengen is also known as the \"Star\". They were responsible for preaching the foundation of jujutsu sorcerers and spawning religious groups that worship the Star as their deity.","id":217291,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b217291-zKcyXtXLZZJy.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Star","Master Tengen"],"full":"Tengen","native":"天元"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/217291"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":555829,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Rika Orimoto is the childhood friend of Yuta Okkotsu who tragically died when she was hit by a car. Her spirit was cursed, transforming her into a powerful Special Grade Vengeful Cursed Spirit worthy of the moniker \"Queen of Curses\".","gender":"Female","id":208533,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b208533-EXiA1hR5l585.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rika Orimoto","native":"祈本里香"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/208533"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557064,"node":{"age":"28-","dateOfBirth":{"day":7,"month":11},"description":"__Height:__ 168 cm\n__Ability:__ Reverse Healing Cursed Technique\n\nAlumnus of Tokyo Jujutsu High, having been classmates with [Satoru Gojo](https://anilist.co/character/127691) and [Suguru Geto](https://anilist.co/character/133699). After graduating into a full-fledged jujutsu sorcerer, Shoko became the school's primary doctor. \n\n","gender":"Female","id":158154,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b158154-UCqbiULli62P.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shouko Ieiri","native":"家入硝子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/158154"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558720,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is a member of the Zenin Family and its elite unit of jujutsu sorcerers, the Hei.\n\n~!He is later killed by Maki after confronting her with Jinichi.!~","gender":"Male","id":229951,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b229951-JcBkO8gnEult.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ranta Zenin","native":"禪院蘭太"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/229951"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563078,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She was a normal human turned jujutsu sorcerer by [Kenjaku](https://anilist.co/character/289584/Kenjaku) for the Culling Game. ~!Remi aligned herself with [Reggie Star](https://anilist.co/character/306194/Reggie-Star)'s group who all serve as antagonists for the Culling Game Arc.!~","gender":"Female","id":306240,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b306240-FwSl5KEs9hsi.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Remi","native":"麗美"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/306240"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":464567,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 183 cm\n__Occupation:__ Curse User\n__Cursed Technique:__ Cursed Spirit Manipulation\n\nKenjaku is one of the primary antagonists of the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He is an ancient sorcerer who pursues the goal of \"evolving\" humanity via cursed energy, thereby ushering in a new golden age of jujutsu sorcery paralleling the Heian Era.\n\n~!Using his cursed technique that allows him to transplant his brain into different bodies to possess them, he has inhabited different people throughout the centuries, assuming different identities.!~\n\n","gender":"Male","id":289584,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b289584-KndGudJZm5Ik.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kenjaku","native":"羂索"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/289584"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":552280,"node":{"age":"28","dateOfBirth":{"day":7,"month":12,"year":1989},"description":"__Height:__ 190 cm (6'3\")\n__Occupation:__ Jujutsu Sorcerer, Teacher\n__Affiliation:__ Tokyo Metropolitan Curse Technical College, Gojou Family\n__Grade:__ Special Grade Sorcerer\n__Cursed Technique:__ Six Eyes, Limitless\n\nSatoru Gojou is one of the main protagonists of the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He is a special-grade jujutsu sorcerer and is widely recognized as the strongest in the world. Satoru is the pride of the Gojou Family, the first person to inherit both the Limitless and the Six Eyes in four hundred years. He works as a teacher at the Tokyo Jujutsu High and uses his influence to protect and train strong young allies\n","gender":"Male","id":127691,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b127691-9zqh1xpIubn7.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Satoru Gojo"],"full":"Satoru Gojou","native":"五条悟"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/127691"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":555844,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Furudate is a minor character in the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He is the executor of [Naobito Zenin](https://anilist.co/character/188432/Naobito-Zenin)'s will.","gender":"Male","id":306278,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b306278-Pn2TbaqDM10h.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Furudate","native":"フルダテ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/306278"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557066,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He was initially one of Suguru Geto's commanders who wished to see him become king. Following the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons, Miguel was forcefully recruited by Satoru Gojo. He returned to his homeland of Africa and the community of sorcerers there to train Yuta Okkotsu.","gender":"Male","id":272175,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b272175-wBjreG7iB9n2.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Miguel","native":"ミゲル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/272175"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558721,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is a member of the Zenin Family and captain of its Kukuru Unit, which is a unit specialized in martial arts for clan members that aren't sorcerers. \n\n~!He is later stabbed in the throat by Maki after confronting her in her rampage.!~","gender":"Male","id":229954,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b229954-s7hYTlueHFIj.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Nobuaki Zenin","native":"禪院信朗"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/229954"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560174,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":388744,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388744-dyiuhdgQxZvJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"John☆Bobby","native":"ジョン☆ボビ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388744"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563079,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Sasaki is a second-year student at Sugisawa Third High School and a member of school's Occult Research Club alongside her friends [Yuuji Itadori](https://anilist.co/character/127212/Yuuji-Itadori) and [Takeshi Iguchi](https://anilist.co/character/200767/Takeshi-Iguchi).","gender":"Female","id":200765,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b200765-xQLkNIRUGuQw.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Setsuko Sasaki","native":"佐々木せつこ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/200765"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":464568,"node":{"age":"150+","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Chousou is half human and half cursed spirit and the first of the Death Painting Wombs with a Special Grade rank. He and his two brothers, Kechizu and Eso are Cursed Womb: Death Paintings who have sided with Mahito's group.\n\nChousou bears strong attachments to his brothers and is very overprotective of them. ~!However, after receiving a vision during his battle with Itadori, Chousou was eventually convinced that Sukuna's vessel was actually one of his younger brothers. He then became furious at Mahito and the other cursed spirits for manipulating him into harming Itadori.!~\n\n~!Chousou is one of nine death painting wombs that came from a woman capable of giving birth to cursed spirit children. At some point, Chousou and his brothers were stored at the Jujutsu High, along with some of Sukuna's fingers.\n\nAs stated by Chousou himself, Noritoshi Kamo, the man who experimented on his mother is in fact his third \"parent\" due to him having mixed in his own blood into Chousou when his mother was pregnant with him. Although seemingly not remembering much about his own past, it is evident that Chousou himself remembers Noritoshi and holds a grudge against him for toying with his mother and siblings' lives.!~","gender":"Male","id":157116,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b157116-2jYQf3y8NeTZ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Choso"],"full":"Chousou","native":"脹相"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/157116"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553003,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Kinji Hakari is a character in the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He is a third-year student at Tokyo Jujutsu High who is currently suspended for clashing with authority. While away from the school, Kinji is running a fight club between sorcerers for money.","gender":"Male","id":197584,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b197584-fK7Jc6DLfx7e.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["はかり"],"full":"Kinji Hakari","native":"秤金次"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/197584"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556116,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":5,"month":3},"description":"__Species:__ Cursed Corpse (varies among 3 personalities)\n__Occupation:__ Jujutsu Sorcerer, Student\n__Affiliation:__ Jujutsu High\n__Grade:__ 2\n\nHe is a second-year at Tokyo Prefectural Jujutsu High. As a Metamorphosed Cursed Corpse, he is the best creation of Principal [Masamichi Yaga](https://anilist.co/character/189237/Masamichi-Yaga). He is sentient and has three cores inside the doll body: the youngest brother \"Panda\", the eldest brother \"Gorilla\" and a sister. ","gender":"Male","id":137974,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b137974-9qnK3DPrvLKh.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Panda","native":"パンダ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/137974"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557067,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":386892,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386892-8Dn15ydijrt3.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ken-san","native":"ケンさん"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386892"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565877,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Keita Oue is a minor character in the Jujutsu Kaisen series. He was the defendant in a murder case where he was represented by [Hiromi Higuruma](https://anilist.co/character/248818/Hiromi-Higuruma) and unjustly found guilty.","gender":"Male","id":306273,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b306273-jJGb5SbYVIs1.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Keita Oue","native":"大江圭太"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/306273"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter the Shibuya Incident, a deadly jujutsu battle known as the Culling Game orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo erupts across ten colonies in Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHaunted by guilt over the mass killings in Shibuya and wary of Sukuna’s interest in Fushiguro, Itadori chooses not to return to Jujutsu High. Instead, he teams up with Choso to exorcise the countless cursed spirits unleashed by Noritoshi Kamo.\nAmid this chaos, the Jujutsu Headquarters revokes Yuji Itadori’s suspended death sentence and appoints special-grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu as his executioner. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNewly awakened modern sorcerers and resurrected ancient ones,  now fighting as players in the Culling Game, collide with conflicting motives, driving the world once more toward an age ruled by jujutsu.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOHO Animation)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":172463,"meanScore":84,"popularity":164772,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":94,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"TV","rank":296,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":3,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":1,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":3,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":1,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/171627-7esVHhgw69rn.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e43550","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png"},"description":"Theatrical follow-up to \u003ci\u003eChainsaw Man\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDenji became “Chainsaw Man”, a boy with a devil’s heart, and is now part of Special Division 4’s devil hunters. After a date with Makima, the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain. There he meets Reze, a girl who works in a café.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: MAPPA CHANNEL)\n\n","episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","id":171627,"idMal":57555,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":90,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/171627","startDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc","native":"チェンソーマン レゼ篇","romaji":"Chainsaw Man: Reze-hen","userPreferred":"Chainsaw Man: Reze-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"pv8A7eubPQQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pv8A7eubPQQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/269-08ar2HJOUAuL.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png"},"description":"Ichigo Kurosaki is a rather normal high school student apart from the fact he has the ability to see ghosts. This ability never impacted his life in a major way until the day he encounters the Shinigami Kuchiki Rukia, who saves him and his family's lives from a Hollow, a corrupt spirit that devours human souls. \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWounded during the fight against the Hollow, Rukia chooses the only option available to defeat the monster and passes her Shinigami powers to Ichigo. Now forced to act as a substitute until Rukia recovers, Ichigo hunts down the Hollows that plague his town. \n\n\n","episodes":366,"format":"TV","id":269,"idMal":269,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/269","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2004},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Bleach","native":"BLEACH","romaji":"BLEACH","userPreferred":"BLEACH"},"trailer":{"id":"0c4IoCA5fY0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0c4IoCA5fY0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/11061-8WkkTZ6duKpq.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx11061-y5gsT1hoHuHw.png"},"description":"A new adaption of the manga of the same name by Togashi Yoshihiro.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA Hunter is one who travels the world doing all sorts of dangerous tasks. From capturing criminals to searching deep within uncharted lands for any lost treasures. Gon is a young boy whose father disappeared long ago, being a Hunter. He believes if he could also follow his father's path, he could one day reunite with him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter becoming 12, Gon leaves his home and takes on the task of entering the Hunter exam, notorious for its low success rate and high probability of death to become an official Hunter. He befriends the revenge-driven Kurapika, the doctor-to-be Leorio and the rebellious ex-assassin Killua in the exam, with their friendship prevailing throughout the many trials and threats they come upon taking on the dangerous career of a Hunter.","episodes":148,"format":"TV","id":11061,"idMal":11061,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":89,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/11061","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Hunter x Hunter (2011)","native":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)","romaji":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)","userPreferred":"HUNTER×HUNTER (2011)"},"trailer":{"id":"d6kBeJjTGnY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/d6kBeJjTGnY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116674-l2YlIyJzvGSV.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45043","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx116674-p3zK4PUX2Aag.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx116674-p3zK4PUX2Aag.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx116674-p3zK4PUX2Aag.jpg"},"description":"Was it all just a coincidence, or was it inevitable?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIchigo Kurosaki gained the powers of a Soul Reaper through a chance encounter. As a Substitute\nSoul Reaper, Ichigo became caught in the turmoil of the Soul Society, a place where deceased\nsouls gather. But with help from his friends, Ichigo overcame every challenge to become even\nstronger.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWhen new Soul Reapers and a new enemy appear in his hometown of Karakura, Ichigo jumps\nback into the battlefield with his Zanpakuto to help those in need. Meanwhile, the Soul Society\nis observing a sudden surge in the number of Hollows being destroyed in the World of the Living.\nThey also receive separate reports of residents in the Rukon District having gone missing. Finally,\nthe Seireitei, home of the Soul Reapers, comes under attack by a group calling themselves the\nWandenreich.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nLed by Yhwach, the father of all Quincies, the Wandenreich declare war against the Soul Reapers\nwith the following message: \u003ci\u003e\"Five days from now, the Soul Society will be annihilated by the\nWandenreich.\"\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe history and truth kept hidden by the Soul Reapers for a thousand long years is finally brought\nto light.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAll things must come to an end as Ichigo Kurosaki's final battle begins!","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":116674,"idMal":41467,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/116674","startDate":{"day":11,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War","native":"BLEACH 千年血戦篇","romaji":"BLEACH: Sennen Kessen-hen","userPreferred":"BLEACH: Sennen Kessen-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"fzR82oXbjnY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/fzR82oXbjnY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/392-nbB6cBnhHOFb.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e49343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx392-z90299zIvYmx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx392-z90299zIvYmx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx392-z90299zIvYmx.png"},"description":"Urameshi Yusuke, 14 years of age, is about as troublesome and violent as teenagers come. He is constantly ditching school, causing trouble, and getting into numerous fights everyday. One day however, he does the unexpected, sacrificing himself to save a young child. Such an action, was never ever expected, especially coming from someone as troublesome as Urameshi Yusuke. The afterlife is not prepared for Yusuke, as they never thought he would make such a sacrifice. Nowhere to go, and dead, Yusuke becomes a ghost and must earn his way back into existence.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYusuke is \"employed\" by Koenma, who is in charge while his father and ruler of the afterlife, King Enma, is away. Under Koenma's command, Yusuke helps to stop menacing demons that threaten the lives of people everywhere; whether by stealing priceless and invaluable items and destructive weapons, or by wreaking havoc on humans everywhere.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThroughout Yusuke's journey, he is usually joined by; his arch-rival, and local bully, Kuwabara Kazuma. He is also joined by two demons named Hiei and Kurama, whom are ex-convicts of the afterlife that managed to escape from Koenma.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThis group of unlikely allies goes on to participate and struggle in battles that have outcomes that determine the fate of humanity!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: AniDB) ","episodes":112,"format":"TV","id":392,"idMal":392,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/392","startDate":{"day":10,"month":10,"year":1992},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Yu Yu Hakusho: Ghostfiles","native":"幽☆遊☆白書","romaji":"Yuu☆Yuu☆Hakusho","userPreferred":"Yuu☆Yuu☆Hakusho"},"trailer":{"id":"UuRNnGmwVc4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UuRNnGmwVc4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/136-uHALFo2vGOGd.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx136-gj0bbCpDNrKG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx136-gj0bbCpDNrKG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx136-gj0bbCpDNrKG.jpg"},"description":"A Hunter is one who travels the world doing all sorts of dangerous tasks. From capturing criminals to searching deep within uncharted lands for any lost treasures. Gon is a young boy whose father disappeared long ago, being a Hunter. He believes if he could also follow his father's path, he could one day reunite with him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter becoming 12, Gon leaves his home and takes on the task of entering the Hunter exam, notorious for its low success rate and high probability of death to become an official Hunter. He befriends the revenge-driven Kurapika, the doctor-to-be Leorio and the rebellious ex-assassin Killua in the exam, with their friendship prevailing throughout the many trials and threats they come upon taking on the dangerous career of a Hunter. Based on the manga by Togashi Yoshihiro. ","episodes":62,"format":"TV","id":136,"idMal":136,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/136","startDate":{"day":16,"month":10,"year":1999},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Hunter x Hunter","native":"HUNTER×HUNTER","romaji":"HUNTER×HUNTER","userPreferred":"HUNTER×HUNTER"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101922-33MtJGsUSxga.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101922-WBsBl0ClmgYL.jpg"},"description":"It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself. Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a “demon slayer” so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":26,"format":"TV","id":101922,"idMal":38000,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101922","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba","native":"鬼滅の刃","romaji":"Kimetsu no Yaiba","userPreferred":"Kimetsu no Yaiba"},"trailer":{"id":"6vMuWuWlW4I","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6vMuWuWlW4I/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166613-drS86exJlIjG.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e49328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJigokuraku\u003c/i\u003e.","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":166613,"idMal":55825,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166613","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise Season 2","native":"地獄楽 第二期","romaji":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JLe_NUnAZVs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JLe_NUnAZVs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/101517-FrJtb3Th3HtF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg"},"description":"Although Yuji Itadori looks like your average teenager, his immense physical strength is something to behold! Every sports club wants him to join, but Itadori would rather hang out with the school outcasts in the Occult Research Club. One day, the club manages to get their hands on a sealed cursed object. Little do they know the terror they’ll unleash when they break the seal…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Ranked 1st in Japan's Bookstore Employees Top Manga of 2018.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize in 2021.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 65th Shogakukan Manga Award in the Shounen Category in 2019.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":101517,"idMal":113138,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101517","startDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Sorcery Fight","주술회전","咒术回战","Guerra de Hechiceros","Batalha de Feiticeiros","JJK","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร","Chú thuật hồi chiến","Магическая битва","La guerra màgica","Prokleté války","咒術迴戰","Contiendas de Brujería","Lanet Savaşları"],"title":{"english":"Jujutsu Kaisen","native":"呪術廻戦","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen"},"trailer":{"id":"R60IExw7v8A","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/R60IExw7v8A/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/145064-esDtAY2He7sk.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a178d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe past comes to light when second-year students Satoru Gojou and Suguru Getou are tasked with escorting young Riko Amanai to Master Tengen. But when a non-sorcerer user tries to kill them, their mission to protect the Star Plasma Vessel threatens to turn them into bitter enemies and cement their destinies—one as the world’s strongest sorcerer, and the other its most twisted curse user!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":12,"year":2023},"episodes":23,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":145064,"idMal":51009,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/145064","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["呪術廻戦 懐玉・玉折／渋谷事変 ","Jujutsu Kaisen: Kaigyoku Gyokusetsu / Shibuya Jihen","Jujutsu Kaisen: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death","JJK2","咒術迴戰  第二季","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร ภาค 2 ","咒术回战 2","2جوجوتسو كايسن ","Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Incident"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 2","native":"呪術廻戦 第2期","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"O6qVieflwqs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O6qVieflwqs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg"},"description":"Movie compilation of the Shibuya Incident Arc from the second season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e and the first two episodes of the third season's Culling Game Arc.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: GKIDS)","duration":88,"endDate":{"day":7,"month":11,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":204066,"idMal":62392,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204066","startDate":{"day":7,"month":11,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["JJK Movie","JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution -Shibuya Incident x The Culling Game Begins-","native":"呪術廻戦『渋谷事変 特別編集版』×『死滅回游 先行上映』","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Jihen Tokubetsu Henshuu-ban x Shimetsu Kaiyuu Senkou Jouei","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Jihen Tokubetsu Henshuu-ban x Shimetsu Kaiyuu Senkou Jouei"},"trailer":{"id":"VEjVqXiiUNY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VEjVqXiiUNY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/172463","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":125415,"name":{"full":"Gege Akutami"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":131334,"name":{"full":"Shouta Goshozono"}},"role":"Director "},{"node":{"id":154010,"name":{"full":"Yousuke Takata"}},"role":"Assistant Director"},{"node":{"id":104503,"name":{"full":"Takeru Satou"}},"role":"Assistant Director"},{"node":{"id":99012,"name":{"full":"Hiroshi Seko"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":132677,"name":{"full":"Hiromi Niwa"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":207061,"name":{"full":"Yousuke Yajima"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":203427,"name":{"full":"Tatsuo Ishino"}},"role":"Title Logo Design"},{"node":{"id":119687,"name":{"full":"Junichi Higashi"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":181823,"name":{"full":"Eiko Matsushima"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":187695,"name":{"full":"Teppei Itou"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":121967,"name":{"full":"Keisuke Yanagi"}},"role":"Editing"},{"node":{"id":172647,"name":{"full":"Yuusuke Tannawa"}},"role":"CG Producer"},{"node":{"id":121305,"name":{"full":"Kentarou Shiga"}},"role":"CG Director"},{"node":{"id":103110,"name":{"full":"Yasunori Ebina"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":142411,"name":{"full":"Katsuhiro Nakano"}},"role":"Sound Effects"},{"node":{"id":161984,"name":{"full":"Yoshimasa Terui"}},"role":"Music "},{"node":{"id":150013,"name":{"full":"Yoshiki Kobayashi"}},"role":"Music Producer"},{"node":{"id":190880,"name":{"full":"Keisuke Seshimo"}},"role":"Animation Producer"},{"node":{"id":244924,"name":{"full":"Riku Nihonyanagi"}},"role":"Animation Producer"},{"node":{"id":294169,"name":{"full":"Yuki Sanjo"}},"role":"Production Desk"},{"node":{"id":385856,"name":{"full":"Shin Takahashi"}},"role":"CG Production Assistant"},{"node":{"id":168653,"name":{"full":"Sukeyuki Honda"}},"role":"Planning Assistance"},{"node":{"id":168654,"name":{"full":"Kouhei Oonishi"}},"role":"Planning Assistance"},{"node":{"id":220441,"name":{"full":"Yuu Saitou"}},"role":"Planning Assistance"}]},"startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":569,"name":"MAPPA"}]},"trailer":{"id":"ruX3rIj3--w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ruX3rIj3--w/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:42:00.654978+03:00"},"176276":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":72,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":478914,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":12,"month":3},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 173 cm (5'8\")\n__Occupation:__ Caretaker\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (7th Unit)\n__Family:__ [Aoba Wakura](https://anilist.co/character/170333/Aoba-Wakura) (sister)\n\nCaretaker of the Anti-Demon Corps 7th Unit. He attended Kaminoge High School as a third-year student but after getting caught up in a Mato Disaster, he was rescued by Kyouka Uzen and became her Slave, granting him the power to fight alongside her.\n\nDue to being a male, he could not become an official member of the Demon Corps since men can't receive special powers after consuming Peaches and has instead became the caretaker of the 7th unit, lending his support to his comrades both in and out of combat.","gender":"Male","id":170329,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170329-nLoZpvOU26Md.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Slave-kun"],"full":"Yuuki Wakura","native":"和倉優希"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170329"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":478913,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":11,"month":2},"description":"**Species:** Human\n**Height:** 162 cm (5'4\")\n**Peach Ability:** \"Vairocana\"\n**Affiliation:** Anti-Demon Corps (Anti-Demon Unit Commander \u0026 10th Unit Chief)\n\nRen Yamashiro is the Anti-Demon Unit Commander and 10th Unit Chief. She had an upbringing where she succeeded in anything and everything that she did, whether it was mock exams, sports competitions, or leading the student council. Having eaten a Peach from Mato and receiving powerful abilities, she has been described by the previous president as \"life's apex.\"","gender":"Female","id":192783,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192783-yqW1z23efg07.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ren Yamashiro","native":"山城恋"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192783"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514255,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Species:__ Unknown\n__Affiliation:__ Eight Gods Of Thunder","gender":"Female","id":192911,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192911-E1YLO21jjVQP.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shikoku","native":"紫黒"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192911"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":550601,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":16,"month":5},"description":"Yakumo Ezo is the Anti-Demon Corps' 5th Unit Chief.","gender":"Female","id":192781,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192781-hvQoHZiBnm7b.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yakumo Ezo","native":"蝦夷夜雲"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192781"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514256,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":14,"month":2},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 155 cm (5'1\")\n__Peach Ability:__ Eastern Time, \u003ci\u003e\"Golden Hour\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (6th Unit Vice-Chief)\n\nOlder sister of Himari Azuma","gender":"Female","id":170337,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170337-OiE2Qk0D8CTv.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yachiho Azuma","native":"東八千穂"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170337"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553026,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":3,"month":6},"description":"__Height:__ 164cm\n\nMaia Azuma is a member of the Azuma Family. She is a member of the Anti-Demon Corps' 9th Unit earning the position of Vice-Chief.","gender":"Female","id":266758,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b266758-GlrxJgIwaIxd.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Maia Azuma","native":"東麻衣亜"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/266758"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514245,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":13,"month":11},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 165 cm (5'5\")\n__Peach Ability:__ Imperial Liberation, \u003ci\u003e\"Paradigm Shift\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (7th Unit)","gender":"Female","id":170330,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170330-HgLYmja2EIll.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shushu Suruga","native":"駿河朱々"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170330"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514257,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Species:__ Humanoid Shuuki\n__Peach Ability:__ I am the Older Sister, \u003ci\u003e\"Invincible\"\u003c/I\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Hidden Village\n\nAoba Wakura is the older sister of [Yuuki Wakura](https://anilist.co/character/170329/Yuuki-Wakura) who'd taught him about being a proper young man, but later went missing at least six years prior in a Mato Disaster","gender":"Female","id":170333,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170333-tX4fYxtmO7Hd.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Aoba Wakura","native":"和倉青羽"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170333"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553027,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":19,"month":9},"description":"__Height:__ 158 cm\n\nHomare Azuma is a member of the Azuma Branch Family. She is a member of the Anti-Demon Corps' 9th Unit.","gender":"Female","id":266760,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b266760-wcLtKAaYi0OW.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Homare Azuma","native":"東誉"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/266760"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514246,"node":{"age":"11","dateOfBirth":{"day":5,"month":5},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 145 cm (4'9\")\n__Peach Ability:__ Sure To Find, \u003ci\u003e\"Promise\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Occupation:__ Scout\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (7th Unit)","gender":"Female","id":170336,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170336-MCONDHALGZbU.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Nei Ookawamura","native":"大川村寧"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170336"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542196,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":8},"description":"__Height:__ 170cm","gender":"Female","id":192785,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192785-MNEeXEtdmfRq.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mira Kamiunten","native":"上運天美羅"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192785"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553028,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":11},"description":"__Height:__ 155cm","gender":"Female","id":266761,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b266761-xAyRPFrqCo63.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tobera Azuma","native":"東海桐花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/266761"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514247,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":4,"month":9},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 167 cm (5'6\")\n__Peach Ability:__ Chains of Eternity, \u003ci\u003e\"Slave\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (7th Unit Chief)\n\nKyouka is the chief of the 7th Unit of the Anti-demon Corps, an elite group of women who have received power from the Peaches. She is Yuuki Wakura's savior and becomes his master after she decided to make him her slave. She is a fierce militaristic, calm, and serious woman befitting the 7th Unit Chief. She often fights against the Shuuki more seriously than other chiefs. She cares for the people around her to the point where she will do anything to protect them. ","gender":"Female","id":162524,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b162524-r8daVAJ32H4j.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kyouka Uzen","native":"羽前京香"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/162524"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542197,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":4,"month":12},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 155 cm\n__Peach Ability:__ Golden Xing Yi Quan, \u003ci\u003e\"Beast Power\"\u003c/I\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (1st Unit Chief)\n\nKonomi Tatara is the Anti-Demon Corps' 1st Unit new Chief after the previous Chief, Riu Myouga stepped down from her position.\n","gender":"Female","id":192778,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192778-2OVPAVYmj44F.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Konomi Tatara","native":"多々良木乃実"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192778"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559843,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Saki Tokoyama is a member of the Anti-Demon Corps' 5th Unit.","gender":"Female","id":266766,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b266766-NScbDXGO7YBy.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Saki Tokoyama","native":"所山サキ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/266766"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514252,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":28,"month":8},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 159 cm (5'3\")\n__Peach Ability:__ Noble Aspirations, \u003ci\u003e\"Learning\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (7th Unit Vice-Chief)\n__Family:__ [Tobera Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266761/Tobera-Azuma) (grandmother),  [Fubuki Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/192784/Fubuki-Azuma) (mother), [Yachiho Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/170337/Yachiho-Azuma) (sister), [Maia Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266758/Maia-Azuma) (sister), [Homare Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266760/Homare-Azuma) (sister-in-law), [Yumina Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266763/Yumina-Azuma) (sister-in-law)","gender":"Female","id":170335,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170335-THTEXHKfMQwW.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Himari Azuma","native":"東日万凛"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170335"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542198,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":30,"month":3},"gender":"Female","id":192782,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192782-a2lxwQ3tb7Sr.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Bell Tsukiyono","native":"月夜野ベル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192782"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559844,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":1},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 156 cm (5'1\")\n__Peach Ability:__ \u003ci\u003e\"Crazy Sheep\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (6th Unit)","gender":"Female","id":170331,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170331-MFTLouTYKKdI.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Sahara Wakasa","native":"若狭サハラ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170331"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514253,"node":{"age":"19-","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":10},"description":"__Species:__ Human\n__Height:__ 163 cm (5'4\")\n__Peach Ability:__ \u003ci\u003e\"Ame-No-Mitori\"\u003c/i\u003e\n__Affiliation:__ Anti-Demon Corps (6th Unit Chief)\n\nTenka is the 6th Anti-Demon Corps Chief. She is Kyouka's friend and rival.","gender":"Female","id":162432,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b162432-TYJ8eP6kKCO4.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tenka Izumo","native":"出雲天花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/162432"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542199,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Varvara Pilipenko is the Anti-Demon Corps' 8th Unit Chief.\n\n","gender":"Female","id":192780,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192780-oqZfEIDytKgK.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Barbara Pilipenko"],"full":"Varvara Pilipenko","native":"ワルワラ・ピリペンコ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192780"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":561929,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Kuusetsu is one of the Eight Thunder Gods, consisting of the so-called Gods who rule over the Shuuki.","gender":"Female","id":266759,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b266759-nazT2jt8E9kr.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kuusetsu","native":"空折"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/266759"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":514254,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":170338,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b170338-VecRBdIFzHF0.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Naon Yuno","native":"湯野波音"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/170338"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542200,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":16,"month":4},"description":"__Height:__ 171cm\n__Family:__ [Tobera Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266761/Tobera-Azuma) (mother), [Maia Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266758/Maia-Azuma) (daughter), [Yachiho Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/170337/Yachiho-Azuma) (daughter), [Himari Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/170335/Himari-Azuma) (daughter), [Homare Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266760/Homare-Azuma) (daughter-in-law), [Yumina Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266763/Yumina-Azuma) (daughter-in-law), [Sorako Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266771/Sorako-Azuma) (sister-in-law), [Takemi Azuma](https://anilist.co/character/266764/Takemi-Azuma) (sister-in-law)       \n\nFubuki Azuma is a member of the Anti-Demon Corps and is the 9th Unit's Chief. She is the mother of several daughters such as Yachiho and Himari Azuma.","gender":"Female","id":192784,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b192784-oB31s5ZqaRjJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Fubuki Azuma","native":"東風舞希"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/192784"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eMato Seihei no Slave.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":176276,"meanScore":73,"popularity":31488,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":17,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":17,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":16,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":10,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20745-dwEaM0N5STVq.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20745-HzWTPFv0P13I.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20745-HzWTPFv0P13I.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20745-HzWTPFv0P13I.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003eHigh School DxD\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe Red Dragon Emperor, Issei Hyoudou, and the Occult Research Club are back in action as summer break comes for the students of Kuoh Academy. After their fight with Issei’s sworn enemy, Vali and the Chaos Brigade, it is clear just how inexperienced Rias Gremory's team is. As a result, she and Azazel lead the club on an intense training regime in the Underworld to prepare them for the challenges that lie ahead.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nWhile they slowly mature as a team, Issei will once again find himself in intimate situations with the girls of the Occult Research Club. Meanwhile, their adversaries grow stronger and more numerous as they rally their forces. And with the sudden appearance of Loki, the Evil God of Norse Mythology, the stage is set for epic fights and wickedly powerful devils in High School DxD BorN!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":20745,"idMal":24703,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20745","startDate":{"day":4,"month":4,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"ハイスクールD×D BorN","romaji":"High School DxD BorN","userPreferred":"High School DxD BorN"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/15583.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx15583-Sxd2J4RJdRhj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx15583-Sxd2J4RJdRhj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx15583-Sxd2J4RJdRhj.jpg"},"description":"Thirty years before a strange phenomena called a \"spacequake\" devastated the center of Eurasia, claiming the lives of at least 150 million people. Since then, smaller spacequakes plague the world on an irregular basis. Shidou Itsuka, a seemingly ordinary high schooler comes across a mysterious girl at the ground zero of a spacequake and learns from his sister Kotori she is one of the \"Spirits\" who are the real cause of the spacequakes that occur when they manifest themselves in the world. He also learns that Kotori is the captain of the airship Ratatoskr and recruits him to make use of his mysterious ability to seal the Spirits' powers and stop them from being a threat to mankind. However, there is a catch: to seal a Spirit, he must make her fall in love with him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":15583,"idMal":15583,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/15583","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Date A Live","native":"デート・ア・ライブ","romaji":"Date A Live","userPreferred":"Date A Live"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100483-IRlokHgtKido.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f19350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx100483-fzseZYJnQTLI.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100483-fzseZYJnQTLI.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx100483-fzseZYJnQTLI.jpg"},"description":"Kogarashi Fuyuzora is a \"hands on\" psychic. Ever since the day he got possessed by an evil ghost, he has been burdened with debt. Needing a cheap room to rent, he winds up at a haunted hot springs inn, Yuragi Inn, where only incredibly beautiful girls reside. Amongst the residents is a ghost, Yuuna, who cannot move on to the spirit world. Despite the resistance from the current tenants that are all girls, Kogarashi manages to start his new life at Yuragi Inn.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":100483,"idMal":36726,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":66,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/100483","startDate":{"day":14,"month":7,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Yuuna and the Haunted Hot Springs","native":"ゆらぎ荘の幽奈さん","romaji":"Yuragi-sou no Yuuna-san","userPreferred":"Yuragi-sou no Yuuna-san"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20678-OJNSBFQsH20P.png","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20678-58D9Yhi4GcH2.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20678-58D9Yhi4GcH2.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20678-58D9Yhi4GcH2.png"},"description":"When a pair of sexy girls, Maria and Mio, come to live with high school student Basara Toujou, his life changes forever. The two girls have a secret that they don’t keep for long—Maria is a succubus, and Mio is a future Demon Lord. But Basara has a secret of his own—he’s the last descendant from a clan of demon-fighting heroes. To make things even more complicated, the girls force Basara into a master-servant contract, and Basara ends up becoming their master! What happens when you put a succubus, a demoness, and a demon-fighting hero under the same roof? They form a bond that will help them to take on anything!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":20678,"idMal":23233,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20678","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Testament of Sister New Devil","native":"新妹魔王の契約者","romaji":"Shinmai Maou no Testament","userPreferred":"Shinmai Maou no Testament"},"trailer":{"id":"kgIbAAb7TUQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kgIbAAb7TUQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21093-C8tuv3TH9I5c.jpg","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21093-fVFDznAnJZmL.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21093-fVFDznAnJZmL.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21093-fVFDznAnJZmL.png"},"description":"Monsters: they're real, and they want to date us!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThree years ago, the world learned that harpies, centaurs, catgirls, and all manners of fabulous creatures are not merely fiction; they are flesh and blood - not to mention scale, feather, horn, and fang. Thanks to the \"Cultural Exchange Between Species Act,\" these once-mythical creatures have assimilated into society, or at least, they're trying.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nWhen a hapless human teenager named Kurusu Kimihito is inducted as a \"volunteer\" into the government exchange program, his world is turned upside down. A snake-like lamia named Miia comes to live with him, and it is Kurusu's job to take care of her and make sure she integrates into his everyday life.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nUnfortunately for Kurusu, Miia is undeniably sexy, and the law against interspecies breeding is very strict. Even worse, when a ravishing centaur girl and a flirtatious harpy move in, what's a full-blooded teenage human with raging hormones to do?!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":21093,"idMal":30307,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21093","startDate":{"day":8,"month":7,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Monster Musume: Everyday Life With Monster Girls","native":"モンスター娘のいる日常","romaji":"Monster Musume no Iru Nichijou","userPreferred":"Monster Musume no Iru Nichijou"},"trailer":{"id":"G-IfYF_oesk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/G-IfYF_oesk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/148109-dVFhmQTxQ1IQ.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx148109-cwAINDGwAHB2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx148109-cwAINDGwAHB2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx148109-cwAINDGwAHB2.jpg"},"description":"In a world of monsters and magic, Sion, the local hero, is on his way to save the world from demons. Well, that was the plan until he fell into a pit dug by a sleazy villager, Touka, and died! After hiding the accident, Touka goes to bed as usual but wakes up feeling…different. Somehow he’s in Sion’s body! Now, the fate of the world is in his hands. What could go wrong?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":148109,"idMal":51706,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/148109","startDate":{"day":7,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Legendary Hero is Dead!","native":"勇者が死んだ！","romaji":"Yuusha ga Shinda!","userPreferred":"Yuusha ga Shinda!"},"trailer":{"id":"6VNZtBFNuCU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6VNZtBFNuCU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/160389-zQYpBIU4tnd8.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#4378e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx160389-2f6SosbyUpxX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx160389-2f6SosbyUpxX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx160389-2f6SosbyUpxX.jpg"},"description":"Satou is a high school boy in love with his best friend Hime, an unearthly beauty from another realm. So when she moves back to her home world to get married, Satou doesn’t think twice—he follows her and crashes the wedding. Then, after a kiss from Hime, he suddenly becomes the new groom! But here, Hime is a Ring Princess and her husband is destined to be the Ring King: a hero of immense power.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":160389,"idMal":54265,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":59,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/160389","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Tales of Wedding Rings","native":"結婚指輪物語","romaji":"Kekkon Yubiwa Monogatari","userPreferred":"Kekkon Yubiwa Monogatari"},"trailer":{"id":"S238Ng-DseE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/S238Ng-DseE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx179965-EwqzG3xSyxwc.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx179965-EwqzG3xSyxwc.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx179965-EwqzG3xSyxwc.jpg"},"description":"Takane Takamine is the goddess of her high school. With perfect grades, athletic prowess, and unrivaled beauty, this student council president is the apple of everyone's eye-including Koushi Shirota, a below-average student with no friends or social prospects whatsoever. But he'll soon find out the secret behind Takamine's unbelievable success-her underwear! When she strips, she can undo any of her past actions, and now that Koushi knows, Takamine won't let him off so easy...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Yen Press)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":179965,"idMal":59457,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/179965","startDate":{"day":2,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Please Put Them On, Takamine-san","native":"履いてください、鷹峰さん","romaji":"Haite Kudasai, Takamine-san","userPreferred":"Haite Kudasai, Takamine-san"},"trailer":{"id":"XQABbjkXMB4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XQABbjkXMB4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/141821-KIRWH28jXINm.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45035","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx141821-lkVTjKqL4BU2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx141821-lkVTjKqL4BU2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx141821-lkVTjKqL4BU2.jpg"},"description":"Yuuki Wakura watches as dueling supernatural forces ravage the Earth. Mato are portals to another dimension, avenues from which dangerous monsters escape. Peaches are resources given to women granting them abilities. Chief of the Seventh Unity of the Anti-Demon Corp, Kyouka Uzen arrives to save Yuuki from a monster. Surprisingly, Yuuki holds the power to increase the Peaches effectiveness. But to save the world, Yuuki must be willing to become Kyouka’s servant both on the battlefield and at home.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":21,"month":3,"year":2024},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":141821,"idMal":50392,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2024,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/141821","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Slave of the Magic Capital's Elite Troops","Demon Slave","Slave of the Hell Soldiers","ทาสสุดแกร่งแห่งหน่วยป้องกันอสูร","Mabotai","Demon Slave: The Chained Soldier"],"title":{"english":"Chained Soldier","native":"魔都精兵のスレイブ","romaji":"Mato Seihei no Slave","userPreferred":"Mato Seihei no Slave"},"trailer":{"id":"NdWFitNUsMw","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NdWFitNUsMw/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/106064-6DefHt0QW7jE.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4285d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx106064-WBMhTOo7UQ20.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx106064-WBMhTOo7UQ20.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx106064-WBMhTOo7UQ20.png"},"description":"Decades ago, gates to an otherworldly and dangerous dimension known as Mato—the “Demon City”—appeared across Japan. Those who partook in the “peaches” growing there gained unique abilities—but only if they’re girls. When down-in-the-dumps high school boy Yuuki Wakura finds himself caught up in a gate, he’s saved by Kyouka Uzen, the beautiful commander of the 7th squad of the Demon Defense Force, who…orders him to become her slave?!\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":106064,"idMal":116880,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/106064","startDate":{"day":5,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Slave of the Magic Capital's Elite Troops","Demon Slave","Slave of the Hell Soldiers","ทาสสุดแกร่งแห่งหน่วยป้องกันอสูร","Mabotai","마도정병의 슬레이브","魔都精兵的奴隸"],"title":{"english":"Chained Soldier","native":"魔都精兵のスレイブ","romaji":"Mato Seihei no Slave","userPreferred":"Mato Seihei no Slave"},"trailer":{"id":"3G3HBFr5FkY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3G3HBFr5FkY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/176276","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":106423,"name":{"full":"Takahiro"}},"role":"Original Story"},{"node":{"id":105153,"name":{"full":"Youhei Takemura"}},"role":"Original Character Design"},{"node":{"id":118607,"name":{"full":"Masafumi Tamura"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":100443,"name":{"full":"Yasuhiro Nakanishi"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":119953,"name":{"full":"Keiya Nakano"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":175062,"name":{"full":"Shino Ohara"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":149566,"name":{"full":"Sakie Suzuki"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":163956,"name":{"full":"Mai Kabatani"}},"role":"Color Design Assistance"},{"node":{"id":123934,"name":{"full":"Kouji Hayashi"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":146478,"name":{"full":"Ayako Tan"}},"role":"Editing"},{"node":{"id":359250,"name":{"full":"Takamasa Taba"}},"role":"CG Director"},{"node":{"id":120169,"name":{"full":"Chikako Yokota"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":121746,"name":{"full":"Kouta Yamamoto"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":100443,"name":{"full":"Yasuhiro Nakanishi"}},"role":"Script"},{"node":{"id":158254,"name":{"full":"Ohine Ezaki"}},"role":"Script"},{"node":{"id":194545,"name":{"full":"Keita Kanou"}},"role":"Script"},{"node":{"id":296474,"name":{"full":"Takahiro Nagase"}},"role":"Script"},{"node":{"id":95185,"name":{"full":"Kana Hanazawa"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED1)"},{"node":{"id":108639,"name":{"full":"Maaya Uchida"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED2)"},{"node":{"id":119722,"name":{"full":"Akari Kitou"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":146948,"name":{"full":"Junpei Takatsu"}},"role":"Photography Concept"},{"node":{"id":184375,"name":{"full":"Shizuku"}},"role":"Theme Song Composition (ED1)"},{"node":{"id":184375,"name":{"full":"Shizuku"}},"role":"Theme Song Lyrics (ED1)"},{"node":{"id":184376,"name":{"full":"Polkadot Stingray"}},"role":"Theme Song Arrangement (ED1)"}]},"startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":911,"name":"Passione"},{"id":7066,"name":"Hayabusa Film"}]},"trailer":{"id":"IDgkCjcNxtU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IDgkCjcNxtU/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T22:08:19.55951+03:00"},"182255":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":89,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":504747,"node":{"age":"1000+","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Frieren is the protagonist of _Sousou no Frieren_ and [Fern](https://anilist.co/character/183965)'s master. She was the Mage of the Hero Party and traveled alongside Hero [Himmel](https://anilist.co/character/184311/Himmel), Warrior [Eisen](https://anilist.co/character/184312/Eisen), and Priest [Heiter](https://anilist.co/character/184310/Heiter) in a 10-year journey to defeat the Demon King. \n\nShe was a magic prodigy at a young age, with an impressive quantity of mana, which caught the interest of [Flamme](https://anilist.co/character/219733/Flamme), a human wizard who taught her everything there is to know about magic and mana control until she passed away. Frieren persists in collecting magic knowledge no matter how trivial it may be.","gender":"Female","id":176754,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b176754-PCnpqIOkjhFk.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Frieren the Slayer"],"full":"Frieren","native":"フリーレン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/176754"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":504748,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Fern is the young mage apprentice of [Frieren](https://anilist.co/character/176754/Frieren) and accompanies her as a member of her party. She is an orphaned war refugee originally from the Southern Lands, later adopted by  [Heiter](https://anilist.co/character/184310/Heiter) and placed under Frieren's care.","gender":"Female","id":183965,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b183965-uGFohBjlFoTp.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Fern","native":"フェルン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/183965"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":504749,"node":{"age":"17-18","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Stark is a warrior who fights alongside [Frieren](https://anilist.co/character/176754/Frieren) and [Fern](https://anilist.co/character/183965/Fern). After his village was attacked by demons, he fled and became [Eisen](https://anilist.co/character/184312/Eisen)'s apprentice. At Eisen's instruction, he joined Frieren's party as their vanguard.","gender":"Male","id":184313,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184313-CQl6GSt4RSny.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Stark","native":"シュタルク"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/184313"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":557239,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Second-class mage in the Eighth Party, alongside Wirbel and Scharf, in the First Class Mage Exam. Fern feels that she is the strongest within both the Fourth and Eighth parties.","gender":"Female","id":321718,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b321718-MV9ZCxtNdOpJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ehre","native":"エーレ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/321718"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557240,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Scharf is a third-class mage and member of the eighth party along with Wirbel and Ehre for the First Class Mage Examination.","gender":"Male","id":327305,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b327305-DsvizGfxKnE8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Scharf","native":"シャルフ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/327305"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563182,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Revolte, also known as Divine Revolte, is a demon general. Revolte wields four swords made of magic.","gender":"Male","id":331269,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331269-PSE8DO36qCoW.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Divine Revolte","Kamiwaza no Revolte (神技のレヴォルテ)"],"full":"Revolte","native":"レヴォルテ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331269"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":536011,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Hero and Leader of the party that defeated the Demon King, and a self-proclaimed handsome narcissist. He cares about his friends and can't help but help those in need. He had a great influence on [Frieren](https://anilist.co/character/176754/Frieren), with whom he had adventures for 10 years.\n","gender":"Male","id":184311,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184311-wQFySqYXEqf1.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Himmel","native":"ヒンメル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/184311"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558984,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":331423,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331423-D1WkXFsj0Rdk.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Graf Dach"],"full":"Dach Hakushaku","native":"ダッハ伯爵"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331423"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563183,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"An Elf acquaintance of Frieren and the creator of the inscription that names Boshaft as the finest spirit in the world.","gender":"Female","id":331425,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331425-XgqTo4PKsdhH.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Milliarde","native":"ミリアルデ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331425"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":566378,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"An elven mage who is said to possess knowledge about nearly every magic that exists. She was Flamme's master. She founded the Continental Magic Association around 20 years before Himmel's death. First-class mages get the privilege of meeting her and can ask for any magic they desire.","gender":"Female","id":219734,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b219734-aS4UMAb16DGd.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Serie","native":"ゼーリエ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/219734"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":536012,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Dwarf warrior who was a part of the Hero's party, later became a mentor to [Stark](https://anilist.co/character/184313/Stark).","gender":"Male","id":184312,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184312-kxd5H6iOHIq4.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Eisen","native":"アイゼン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/184312"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563407,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":331439,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331439-meDK5YbPGLuQ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Fass","native":"ファス"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331439"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565584,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"First-class mage who was a proctor for the first examination. ","gender":"Male","id":246055,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b246055-3eoVNiZu3bTy.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Genau","native":"ゲナウ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/246055"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":566379,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":393042,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b393042-gJUh80660HzR.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Hermon","native":"へモン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/393042"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":536013,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A priest who is a part of the Hero's party. He later took care of [Fern](https://anilist.co/character/183965/Fern) until [Frieren](https://anilist.co/character/176754/Frieren) arrived.","gender":"Male","id":184310,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b184310-tiXvrq4FINXP.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Corrupt Priest"],"full":"Heiter","native":"ハイター"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/184310"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563408,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The president of the Norm Company in the Northern Plateau.","gender":"Male","id":331435,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331435-KtkRdUqphwVk.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Norm","native":"ノルム"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331435"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565585,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A mage that can use restraint and mental manipulation magic. Good at detecting mana and can use simple recovery magic.","gender":"Female","id":246054,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b246054-TKwFFWVGISUd.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Methode","native":"メトーデ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/246054"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":566380,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":393043,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b393043-rYRzXoZyBYDG.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Zorida","native":"ゾリーダ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/393043"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":548932,"node":{"age":"33-34","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Second-class mage and the leader of the eighth party during the first stage of the First Class Mage Exam. He is the captain of the Northern Magic Corps and is thus a very experienced mage. Specializes in magic that restrains the opponent when their body is in full-view.","gender":"Male","id":321716,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b321716-ORxrJOHaI4H4.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Wirbel","native":"ヴィアベル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/321716"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":566381,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":393045,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b393045-8BhpSTh9qeMU.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yun","native":"ユン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/393045"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556488,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The Hero of the South is a Hero who fought on the front lines against the demons for mankind before Himmel met Frieren. He was said to be mankind's strongest.","gender":"Male","id":331267,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b331267-hLeSvYXwuTDt.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Hero of the South","Mankind's Strongest"],"full":"Minami no Yuusha","native":"南の勇者"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/331267"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559039,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":387930,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Child"],"full":"Kodomo","native":"子供"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387930"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":560750,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":388977,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388977-N4J4JRpOO0Xd.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Koya no Shu","native":"小屋の主"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388977"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":562331,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":389793,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389793-l75n0uMYqzty.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Eihei","native":"衛兵"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389793"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":563411,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":390703,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Uketsuke","native":"受付"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390703"},"role":"BACKGROUND"}]},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eSousou no Frieren\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":182255,"meanScore":89,"popularity":146737,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":13,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"TV","rank":356,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":1,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":2,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":1,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":2,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/153518-7uRvV7SLqmHV.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e48650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx153518-IVXPDY5ph3kO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx153518-IVXPDY5ph3kO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx153518-IVXPDY5ph3kO.jpg"},"description":"When young adventurer Laios and his company are attacked and soundly thrashed by a dragon deep in a dungeon, the party loses all its money and provisions...and a member! They're eager to go back and save her, but there is just one problem: If they set out with no food or coin to speak of, they're sure to starve on the way! But Laios comes up with a brilliant idea: \"Let's eat the monsters!\" Slimes, basilisks, and even dragons...none are safe from the appetites of these dungeon-crawling gourmands! \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: A world premiere screening of Episode 1 was shown in the Studio TRIGGER panel at Anime Expo on July 1, 2023.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":153518,"idMal":52701,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/153518","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Delicious in Dungeon","native":"ダンジョン飯","romaji":"Dungeon Meshi","userPreferred":"Dungeon Meshi"},"trailer":{"id":"RtpYObV4c1Y","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RtpYObV4c1Y/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21827-ROucgYiiiSpR.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#3586e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21827-ubzq619ZA2E9.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21827-ubzq619ZA2E9.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21827-ubzq619ZA2E9.png"},"description":"A certain point in time, in the continent of Telesis. The great war which divided the continent into North and South has ended after four years, and the people are welcoming a new generation. Violet Evergarden, a young girl formerly known as “the weapon”, has left the battlefield to start a new life at CH Postal Service. There, she is deeply moved by the work of “Auto Memories Dolls”, who carry people's thoughts and convert them into words. Violet begins her journey as an Auto Memories Doll, and comes face to face with various people's emotions and differing shapes of love. There are words Violet heard on the battlefield, which she cannot forget. These words were given to her by someone she holds dear, more than anyone else. She does not yet know their meaning but she searches to find it.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":21827,"idMal":33352,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21827","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Violet Evergarden","native":"ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデン","romaji":"Violet Evergarden","userPreferred":"Violet Evergarden"},"trailer":{"id":"_grmduuECm4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_grmduuECm4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/161645-oqzTZYIvviWI.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1865d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx161645-QLbzHXiYRgV2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx161645-QLbzHXiYRgV2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx161645-QLbzHXiYRgV2.jpg"},"description":"Maomao lived a peaceful life with her apothecary father. Until one day, she’s sold as a lowly servant to the emperor’s palace. But she wasn’t meant for a compliant life among royalty. So when imperial heirs fall ill, she decides to step in and find a cure! This catches the eye of Jinshi, a handsome palace official who promotes her. Now, she’s making a name for herself solving medical mysteries!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":161645,"idMal":54492,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/161645","startDate":{"day":22,"month":10,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Apothecary Diaries","native":"薬屋のひとりごと","romaji":"Kusuriya no Hitorigoto","userPreferred":"Kusuriya no Hitorigoto"},"trailer":{"id":"oyHqh8ue4zw","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oyHqh8ue4zw/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112609-P969sQ0jIU6S.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#50a1f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx112609-hBCbnYlEHluz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx112609-hBCbnYlEHluz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx112609-hBCbnYlEHluz.jpg"},"description":"Inspired by her favorite book, Elaina ventures out to see the world she's read so much about. Like a leaf on the wind, she travels from one country to another, looking to sate her inquisitiveness and searching for new experiences. She's confronted by humanity in all its forms, whether strange, bizarre, or emotional. Exploration and curiosity drive her journey. Where to next, Elaina?\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":112609,"idMal":40571,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/112609","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Wandering Witch: The Journey of Elaina","native":"魔女の旅々","romaji":"Majo no Tabitabi","userPreferred":"Majo no Tabitabi"},"trailer":{"id":"Bfe08q9jer8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Bfe08q9jer8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114535-ASUprf4AsNwC.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx114535-y3NnjexcqKG1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx114535-y3NnjexcqKG1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx114535-y3NnjexcqKG1.jpg"},"description":"In the beginning, an \"orb\" is cast unto Earth. \"It\" can do two things: change into the form of the thing that stimulates \"it\"; and come back to life after death. \"It\" morphs from orb to rock, then to wolf, and finally to boy, but roams about like a newborn who knows nothing. As a boy, \"it\" becomes Fushi.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThrough encounters with human kindness, Fushi not only gains survival skills but grows as a \"person\". But his journey is darkened by the inexplicable and destructive enemy Nokker and cruel partings with the people he loves.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":20,"format":"TV","id":114535,"idMal":41025,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/114535","startDate":{"day":12,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"To Your Eternity","native":"不滅のあなたへ","romaji":"Fumetsu no Anata e","userPreferred":"Fumetsu no Anata e"},"trailer":{"id":"WHq46obaDR8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WHq46obaDR8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/176301-GkuTF1YTT6b2.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx176301-TIGmldLffQGX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx176301-TIGmldLffQGX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx176301-TIGmldLffQGX.jpg"},"description":"Using her wit and vast knowledge of medicines and poisons alike, Maomao played a pivotal role in solving a series of mysteries and conspiracies that plagued the imperial court. Having recently come to terms with the secrets of her parents, she returns to fulfill her normal duties on behalf of the emperor's highest-ranking consorts. Maomao also works alongside the eunuch Jinshi to better the consorts' many ladies-in-waiting, including helping them learn to read.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHowever, with the arrival of a merchant caravan comes a new wave of intrigue. A pattern of strange coincidences involving the visitors and their wares unsettles Maomao, driving her to investigate the puzzling circumstances behind the convoy. As dangers from both outside and within threaten the balance between the imperial concubines, Maomao continues to utilize her cunning and medical expertise to keep the women safe from harm.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":176301,"idMal":58514,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/176301","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Apothecary Diaries Season 2","native":"薬屋のひとりごと 第2期","romaji":"Kusuriya no Hitorigoto 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Kusuriya no Hitorigoto 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"3BYutu3Pf_0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3BYutu3Pf_0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n457-sWOJfqYC7s2I.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#d6bb78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx457-l6cTtNgI9Bi6.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx457-l6cTtNgI9Bi6.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx457-l6cTtNgI9Bi6.png"},"description":"Neither good nor evil, they are life in its purest form. Vulgar and strange, they have inspired fear in humans since the dawn of time and have, over the ages, come to be known as \"mushi.\" The stories of the Mushi and the people they affect are all linked together by a traveling Mushi-shi, or \"Mushi Master,\" who seeks rare Mushi sightings and uses his shaman-like knowledge of Mushi to help the affected people.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nWhat are the Mushi and what do they want?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","episodes":26,"format":"TV","id":457,"idMal":457,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/457","startDate":{"day":23,"month":10,"year":2005},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"MUSHI-SHI","native":"蟲師","romaji":"Mushishi","userPreferred":"Mushishi"},"trailer":{"id":"h371H0KIuPo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/h371H0KIuPo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/179966-hf71VrF1zhPM.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx179966-g0EU7rVe2Og7.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx179966-g0EU7rVe2Og7.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx179966-g0EU7rVe2Og7.jpg"},"description":"Monica Everett, the Silent Witch, is the world’s only practitioner of Voiceless Magic, a veritable heroine who single-handedly fended off the Black Dragon of legend. However, the young prodigy is actually…super-duper shy! Yup, turns out she only learned Voiceless Magic to avoid speaking in public. Ignorant of this, the Seven Sages have placed her on a top-secret mission to guard the Second Prince. Can Monica keep it together as she contends with both social interaction and the evils targeting the young royal?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Yen Press, edited)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":179966,"idMal":59459,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/179966","startDate":{"day":5,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Secrets of the Silent Witch","native":"サイレント・ウィッチ 沈黙の魔女の隠しごと","romaji":"Silent Witch: Chinmoku no Majo no Kakushigoto","userPreferred":"Silent Witch: Chinmoku no Majo no Kakushigoto"},"trailer":{"id":"0OBF29HoV4A","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0OBF29HoV4A/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/118586-R1c7mc72oPvS.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg"},"description":"The adventure is over but life goes on for an elf mage just beginning to learn what living is all about.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nElf mage Frieren and her courageous fellow adventurers have defeated the Demon King and brought peace to the land. With the great struggle over, they all go their separate ways to live a quiet life. But as an elf, Frieren, nearly immortal, will long outlive the rest of her former party. How will she come to terms with the mortality of her friends? How can she find fulfillment in her own life, and can she learn to understand what life means to the humans around her? Frieren begins a new journey to find the answer.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Winner of the Grand Prize at the 14th Manga Taisho Awards.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Placed 3rd at the 7th Annual Next Manga Award.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":118586,"idMal":126287,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118586","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Frieren at the Funeral","장송의 프리렌","Frieren: Oltre la Fine del Viaggio","คำอธิษฐานในวันที่จากลา Frieren","Frieren e a Jornada para o Além","Frieren – Nach dem Ende der Reise","葬送的芙莉蓮","Frieren After \"The End\"","Frieren: Remnants of the Departed","Frieren. U kresu drogi","Frieren","FRIEREN: Más allá del fin del viaje","Проводжальниця Фрірен","Frieren: Ved reisens ende"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End","native":"葬送のフリーレン","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren"},"trailer":{"id":"sIFkD5l8ZCU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sIFkD5l8ZCU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/154587-ivXNJ23SM1xB.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbf1a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg"},"description":"The adventure is over but life goes on for an elf mage just beginning to learn what living is all about. Elf mage Frieren and her courageous fellow adventurers have defeated the Demon King and brought peace to the land. But Frieren will long outlive the rest of her former party. How will she come to understand what life means to the people around her? Decades after their victory, the funeral of one her friends confronts Frieren with her own near immortality. Frieren sets out to fulfill the last wishes of her comrades and finds herself beginning a new adventure…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2024},"episodes":28,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":154587,"idMal":52991,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":91,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/154587","startDate":{"day":29,"month":9,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Frieren at the Funeral","장송의 프리렌","Frieren - Oltre la Fine del Viaggio","คำอธิษฐานในวันที่จากลา Frieren","Frieren e a Jornada para o Além","Frieren – Nach dem Ende der Reise","葬送的芙莉蓮","Frieren: Más allá del final del viaje","Frieren en el funeral","Sōsō no Furīren","Frieren. U kresu drogi","Frieren - Pháp sư tiễn táng","Фрирен, провожающая в последний путь","فريرن: ما وراء نهاية الرحلة","Frieren: Tras finalizar el viaje"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End","native":"葬送のフリーレン","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren"},"trailer":{"id":"qgQunxD0qCk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qgQunxD0qCk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6d678","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg"},"description":"A third batch of the \u003ci\u003e●● no Mahou\u003c/i\u003e shorts released alongside the airing of the TV anime's second season, starting with #18. Posted on the official YouTube account of TOHO animation, Frieren Twitter, and Frieren TikTok account.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cb\u003eIncludes:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n• Mita Mono wo Kousoku Suru Mahou (見た者を拘束する魔法), released Jan 19, 2026. \u003cbr\u003e\n• Doushin ni Kaeru Mahou (童心に還る魔法), released Feb 2, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e\n• Kokoro to Karada ga Irekawaru Mahou (心と体が入れ替わる魔法), released Feb 17, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e\n• Osentaku no Mahou  (お洗濯の魔法), released Mar 2, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e","duration":1,"endDate":{},"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":206425,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/206425","startDate":{"day":19,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season Mini Anime","Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End Season 2 Mini Anime","Sousou no Frieren: Marumaru no Mahou"],"title":{"native":"葬送のフリーレン ～●●の魔法～ 3クール","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren: ●● no Mahou Part 3","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren: ●● no Mahou Part 3"},"trailer":{"id":"WTUkzIG8ZeE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WTUkzIG8ZeE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182255","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":122202,"name":{"full":"Kanehito Yamada"}},"role":"Original Story"},{"node":{"id":170189,"name":{"full":"Tsukasa Abe"}},"role":"Original Character Design"},{"node":{"id":165996,"name":{"full":"Tomoya Kitagawa"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":153321,"name":{"full":"Daiki Harashina"}},"role":"Assistant Director"},{"node":{"id":119119,"name":{"full":"Tomohiro Suzuki"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":122660,"name":{"full":"Akiko Takase"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":134263,"name":{"full":"Keisuke Kojima"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":297833,"name":{"full":"Yuri Fujinaka"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":225507,"name":{"full":"Kazunori Ooshima"}},"role":"Original Work Assistance"},{"node":{"id":301998,"name":{"full":"Hironobu Yoshinaka"}},"role":"Original Work Assistance"},{"node":{"id":281660,"name":{"full":"Haruka Tajima"}},"role":"Original Work Assistance"},{"node":{"id":251859,"name":{"full":"Katsumasa Ogura"}},"role":"Original Work Assistance"},{"node":{"id":315812,"name":{"full":"Masato Ishizawa"}},"role":"Title Logo Design"},{"node":{"id":133708,"name":{"full":"Izumi Seguchi"}},"role":"Design Works"},{"node":{"id":138365,"name":{"full":"Hiroyuki Kobashi "}},"role":"Design Works"},{"node":{"id":153321,"name":{"full":"Daiki Harashina"}},"role":"Design Works"},{"node":{"id":154148,"name":{"full":"Runa Harano"}},"role":"Design Works"},{"node":{"id":131244,"name":{"full":"Shinji Sugiyama"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":127377,"name":{"full":"Seiko Yoshioka"}},"role":"Concept Art"},{"node":{"id":142139,"name":{"full":"Harue Oono"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":135989,"name":{"full":"Akane Fushihara"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":134282,"name":{"full":"Kashiko Kimura"}},"role":"Editing"},{"node":{"id":147828,"name":{"full":"Kana Imagaki"}},"role":"CG Director"},{"node":{"id":120066,"name":{"full":"Shouji Hata"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":128907,"name":{"full":"Noriko Izumo"}},"role":"Sound Effects"}]},"startDate":{"day":16,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":11,"name":"MADHOUSE"}]},"trailer":{"id":"RH-FcW94z00","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RH-FcW94z00/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:51:17.195009+03:00"},"182587":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":83,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":505459,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 158 cm (5'2\")\n\n[Ai Hoshino](https://anilist.co/character/172759/Ai-Hoshino)'s daughter, and the younger twin sister of [Aquamarine Hoshino](https://anilist.co/character/183885). \n~!She was previously a patient named Sarina under Goro's care. Due to her illness, she was wheelchair-bound. After discovering B-Komachi, she had always aspired to be an idol although her condition kept her from achieving her dream. Since being reincarnated as Ruby, she is now working towards her dream of being an idol like Ai. To do so she's currently working with Strawberry Productions to revive B-Komachi along with Arima Kana and Memcho.!~","gender":"Female","id":183884,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b183884-iyo3BmTuhJ0l.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ruby Hoshino","native":"星野ルビー"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/183884"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":505461,"node":{"age":"17","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 163 cm (5'4\")\n\nAkane Kurokawa is a rising star actress from the Lalalie Theatrical Company. Although a shy and quiet person, she is very serious when it comes to creating a good performance. She does a deep examination of each role she is given, allowing her to perfectly portray the character's personality and motivations. Akane is introduced to [Aqua](https://anilist.co/character/183885) as a fellow cast member on the set of the reality dating show *The Beginning of My Love With An Idol*.","gender":"Female","id":203384,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b203384-YuSppFDMw2wn.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["黒川茜"],"full":"Akane Kurokawa","native":"黒川あかね"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/203384"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":505462,"node":{"age":"16-","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 172 cm (5'7\")\n\n[Ai Hoshino](https://anilist.co/character/172759/Ai-Hoshino)'s son. He is the twin big brother of [Ruby Hoshino](https://anilist.co/character/183884/Ruby-Hoshino).\n~!He was previously a doctor named Goro, who became a fan of Ai through his patient named Sarina.!~ ~!After reincarnating as Aquamarine and witnessing Ai's murder, he is intent on plotting revenge to the person who schemed Ai's death.!~","gender":"Male","id":183885,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b183885-HOmw8CqcJdv3.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Aqua","Prodigy Baby"],"full":"Aquamarine Hoshino","native":"星野アクアマリン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/183885"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":505463,"node":{"age":"17-19","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 150 cm (4'11\")\n\nAn actress who was called a prodigy child. She has a rather stubborn personality yet an empathic side to her. She easily succumbs to pressure and while she does put up a front to others, she has very self-deprecating thoughts when it comes to her abilities. She's an honest and earnest person, who is very diligent and persistent even in the roughest of times. Also, she tends to place all responsibility on herself when it comes to others as she is the one who has the most experience in the show business world. She also hates bell peppers.\n  \n~!After the events of the Sweet Today Drama adaptation, she secretly develops a crush for Aquamarine.!~\n\n~!She longs for someone to look at her for who she is now and praise her efforts, someone to say that its okay for her to be here. And after the new B-Komachi's first concert, that person becomes Aquamarine after he waves her respected colored glow stick. Only reinforcing Kana's resolve to make Aquamarine fall for her.!~","gender":"Female","id":188783,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b188783-77orwP7vNuNg.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kana Arima","native":"有馬かな"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/188783"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":542700,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The director for the web variety show Dig Deep! One Chance.","gender":"Male","id":308812,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b308812-eosV3TGRTGFQ.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Tetsu Urushibara","native":"漆原鉄"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/308812"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562942,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A popular film director, currently the most influential in Japan. He has an honest desire to take care of the actors in his productions, but is also known as a playboy and target of tabloid reporters looking for industry scandal. ","gender":"Male","id":295838,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b295838-Kgopin5Csp6c.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Shima D","Director Shima"],"full":"Masanori Shima","native":"島政則"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/295838"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":505460,"node":{"age":"18","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 155 cm (5'1\")\n\nA girl who strived to become an idol at a young age, but due to her family situation, made sacrifices that ultimately ended with her becoming too old to become one. She is a YouTuber. \n\n~!Mem-cho's real age is 25, and she is later recruited as the third member of the re-formed B-Komachi idol group.!~","gender":"Female","id":205434,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b205434-AuBcR4M05f6s.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Mem"],"full":"MEM-cho","native":"MEMちょ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/205434"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542701,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Masaya Kaburagi is a TV and Web-TV producer. ","gender":"Male","id":245518,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b245518-9OvLmdKE5teR.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Masaya Kaburagi","native":"鏑木勝也"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/245518"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":562959,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":390291,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390291-XyTtNMZQS4s2.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mako Azami","native":"アザミマコ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390291"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":547491,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Ichigo Saitou is the director of the agency Ichigo Production. He is the one who scouted [Ai](https://anilist.co/character/172759/Ai-Hoshino) and made her a star. ","gender":"Male","id":245521,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b245521-Kc8y3UYQ4JXs.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ichigo Saitou","native":"斉藤壱護"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/245521"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556877,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She's a classmate and friend of Ruby Hoshino. Minami is a Gravure model who uses a fake accent.\n","gender":"Female","id":252073,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b252073-eLFb2PHy1erO.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Minami Kotobuki","native":"寿みなみ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/252073"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558760,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Cosplayer who uses the stage name Meiya. She was invited by Ruby for a cosplay segment on _Dig Deep! One Chance!_.","gender":"Female","id":295843,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b295843-FXpkXM1TQDGw.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Meiya","native":"メイヤ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/295843"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557331,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Frill Shiranui is a student in Ruby Hoshino's class. She is a multi-talented performer who can sing, dance, and act. At first, Ruby is in awe of her, yet they eventually become friends. \n\n ~!She is the younger sister of [Koromo Shiranui](https://anilist.co/character/212391/Koromo-Shiranui) from [Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensaitachi no Renai Zunousen](https://anilist.co/manga/86635/Kaguyasama-wa-Kokurasetai-Tensaitachi-no-Renai-Zunousen/).!~","gender":"Female","id":223871,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b223871-Yg32oIQlRkwH.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Frill Shiranui","native":"不知火フリル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/223871"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560058,"node":{"age":"22","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Author of \"Tokyo Blade\".","gender":"Female","id":237576,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b237576-BxJO6g6mfKlE.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Abiko Samejima","native":"鮫島アビ子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/237576"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":561290,"node":{"age":"56","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Leader of the Lala Lai Theatrical Company, and one of its founding members. He is the Director of the 2.5D Stage Play *Tokyo Blade*. \n","gender":"Male","id":245514,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b245514-k3JdzroTVwun.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Toshirou Kindaichi","native":"金田一敏郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/245514"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563968,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A weekly entertainment true story writer, a rather shameless person who has no problem with writing up scandalous stories about young actors provided that they are legal adults.","gender":"Male","id":308808,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b308808-l2hkEWjpdc81.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kazuhiko Itano","native":"板野一彦"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/308808"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":505464,"node":{"age":"15-","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"~!He is the father of Aqua and Ruby.!~\n\n~!He is later revealed to also be Taiki Himekawa's biological father, having been molested by Airi Himekawa when he was a child before allegedly having her murdered as well by telling her husband about the affair.!~","gender":"Male","id":299249,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b299249-r7PPoRmqqN1b.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["カミキヒカル"],"full":"Hikaru Kamiki","native":"神木ひかる"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/299249"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557332,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Miyako is married to the president of Ichigo Productions and is Ai's manager. She is a shallow woman who appears to have only married her husband due to the prospect of working with hot guys. She is also a babysitter to the twins.\n\n~!After Ai's death, she becomes the twin's adoptive parent. As the twins blossom into adolescence, she becomes more mature, both as a caretaker and as a manager. She is also the manager of the new B-Komachi.!~","gender":"Female","id":223870,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b223870-60FglagpVtHe.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Miyako Saitou","native":"斎藤ミヤコ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/223870"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":558487,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Cosplayer and VTuber under the name Komimi Suzune. [Shun](https://anilist.co/character/280874/Shun-Yoshizumi)'s sister.","gender":"Female","id":282748,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b282748-KwAOWGdq3DOC.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Komimi Suzune (鈴音コミミ)"],"full":"Mimi Yoshizumi","native":"吉住未実"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/282748"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":505465,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is a seemingly supernatural being apparently aware of everything that transpires within the story.","gender":"Female","id":308806,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b308806-Pfx0DfT8LKS5.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Crow Girl","Pest"],"full":"Karasu Shoujo","native":"カラス少女"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/308806"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":542699,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Former Assistant Director on the online variety show \"Dig Deep! One Chance!\" Currently works as [Ruby](https://anilist.co/character/183884/Ruby-Hoshino)'s manager.","gender":"Male","id":280874,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b280874-uDDV6wDm61Kn.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shun Yoshizumi","native":"吉住シュン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/280874"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557338,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Contestant on the web variety show Dig Deep! One Chance.","gender":"Male","id":386997,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386997-2cvP4BLLPXh0.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Comedian Mizuno"],"full":"Geinin Mizuno","native":"芸人・水野"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386997"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":558547,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":387703,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Cosplayer","native":"コスプレイヤー"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387703"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":560062,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":388620,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"SNS no Koe","native":"SNSの声"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388620"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":563972,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":391208,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Idol","native":"アイドル"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/391208"},"role":"BACKGROUND"}]},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story enters a new stage.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIt's been six months since \"POP IN 2\" was released. Thanks to MEM-Cho's hard work, B-Komachi is about to get their major break. Aqua is a multi-talented entertainer, and Akane's career as a talented actress is going smoothly. Meanwhile, Kana lost the cheerfulness she once had. To track down the truth behind Ai and Goro's deaths, Ruby keeps rising in the entertainment world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eUsing lies as a weapon.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":182587,"meanScore":84,"popularity":74640,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":116,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":4,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":5,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":4,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":5,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/437-3yMVTyN7gl2A.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#1a356b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx437-69NMlXKFeuse.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx437-69NMlXKFeuse.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx437-69NMlXKFeuse.jpg"},"description":"Rising pop star Mima has quit singing to pursue a career as an actress and model, but her fans aren’t ready to see her go... Encouraged by her managers, Mima takes on a recurring role on a popular TV show, when suddenly her handlers and collaborators begin turning up murdered. Harboring feelings of guilt and haunted by visions of her former self, Mima’s reality and fantasy meld into a frenzied paranoia. As her stalker closes in, in person and online, the threat he poses is more real than even Mima knows, in this iconic psychological thriller that has frequently been hailed as one of the most important animated films of all time.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Shout! Factory)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The film received an early premiere at the Fantasia Film Festival on August 5, 1997.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","id":437,"idMal":437,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/437","startDate":{"day":28,"month":2,"year":1998},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Perfect Blue","native":"PERFECT BLUE","romaji":"PERFECT BLUE","userPreferred":"PERFECT BLUE"},"trailer":{"id":"UXQraSkOOGs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UXQraSkOOGs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n101291-fqIUvQ6apEtD.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#356bff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101291-wfEdgPqtfU0l.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101291-wfEdgPqtfU0l.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101291-wfEdgPqtfU0l.jpg"},"description":"There's a rumor about a mysterious phenomenon called \"puberty syndrome.\" For example, Sakuta Azusagawa is a high school student who suddenly sees a bunny girl appear in front of him. The girl is actually a girl named Mai Sakurajima, who is Sakuta's upperclassman who is also a famous actress who has gone on hiatus from the entertainment industry. For some reason, the people around Mai cannot see her bunny-girl figure. Sakuta sets out to solve this mystery, and as he spends time with Mai, he learns her secret feelings. Other heroines who have \"puberty syndrome\" start to appear in front of Sakuta.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":101291,"idMal":37450,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101291","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Rascal Does Not Dream of Bunny Girl Senpai","native":"青春ブタ野郎はバニーガール先輩の夢を見ない","romaji":"Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume wo Minai","userPreferred":"Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume wo Minai"},"trailer":{"id":"o0TZj_d3Yfg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o0TZj_d3Yfg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101921-GgvvFhlNhzlF.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45086","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101921-ufrjLzhSz7L1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101921-ufrjLzhSz7L1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101921-ufrjLzhSz7L1.jpg"},"description":"Known for being both brilliant and powerful, Miyuki Shirogane and Kaguya Shinomiya lead the illustrious Shuchiin Academy as near equals. And everyone thinks they’d make a great couple. Pride and arrogance are in ample supply, so the only logical move is to trick the other into instigating a date! Who will come out on top in this psychological war where the first move is the only one that matters?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":101921,"idMal":37999,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101921","startDate":{"day":12,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Kaguya-sama: Love is War","native":"かぐや様は告らせたい～天才たちの恋愛頭脳戦～","romaji":"Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensaitachi no Renai Zunousen","userPreferred":"Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensaitachi no Renai Zunousen"},"trailer":{"id":"IwpJJiQkZzI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IwpJJiQkZzI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/130003-FEBlngeJSTEm.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx130003-HTDmeL4RGeJ4.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130003-HTDmeL4RGeJ4.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx130003-HTDmeL4RGeJ4.png"},"description":"Hitori Gotou, “Bocchi-chan,” is a girl who’s so introverted and shy around people that she’d always start her conversations with “Ah...”\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nDuring her middle school years, she started playing the guitar, wanting to join a band because she thought it could be an opportunity for even someone shy like her to also shine. But because she had no friends, she ended up practicing guitar for six hours every day all by herself. After becoming a skilled guitar player, she uploaded videos of herself playing the guitar to the internet under the name “Guitar Hero” and fantasized about performing at her school’s cultural festival concert. But not only could she not find any bandmates, before she knew it, she was in high school and still wasn’t able to make a single friend!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nShe was really close to becoming a shut-in, but one day, Nijika Ijichi, the drummer in Kessoku Band, reached out to her. And because of that, her everyday life started to change little by little...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":130003,"idMal":47917,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/130003","startDate":{"day":9,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"BOCCHI THE ROCK!","native":"ぼっち・ざ・ろっく！","romaji":"Bocchi the Rock!","userPreferred":"Bocchi the Rock!"},"trailer":{"id":"SyMMZF5zNW4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SyMMZF5zNW4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21234-7lfSSPoMmwr2.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21234-XmqW39aQ9o7O.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21234-XmqW39aQ9o7O.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21234-XmqW39aQ9o7O.jpg"},"description":"Satoru Fujinuma is a 29 year old manga artist struggling to make a name for himself following his debut. But, that was not the only thing in his life that Satoru was feeling frustrated about… He has a unique supernatural ability of being forced to prevent deaths and catastrophes by being sent back in time before the incident occurred, repeating time until the accident is prevented. One day, he gets involved in an accident that has him framed as a murderer. Desperate to save the victim, he sends himself back in time only to find himself as a grade-schooler one month before fellow classmate Kayo Hinazuki went missing. Satoru now embarks on a new quest: to save Kayo and solve the mystery behind her disappearance.\n","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":21234,"idMal":31043,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21234","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"ERASED","native":"僕だけがいない街","romaji":"Boku dake ga Inai Machi","userPreferred":"Boku dake ga Inai Machi"},"trailer":{"id":"TZzMOC-4k6M","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/TZzMOC-4k6M/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/159039-pS8nlIsLwzBr.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#fed650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx159039-88kPltmhTzqU.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx159039-88kPltmhTzqU.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx159039-88kPltmhTzqU.jpg"},"description":"Yuuhi Yugure and Yasumi Utatane, high school classmates and co-hosts of a weekly radio program, paint a picture-perfect friendship for their listeners. Yet, in reality, they couldn’t be more different. Their off-air dynamic is a whirlwind of chaos and insults. As their tumultuous relationship unfolds, they navigate the turbulent waters of friendship and rivalry in the cutthroat realm of showbiz. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":159039,"idMal":53912,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/159039","startDate":{"day":10,"month":4,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Many Sides of Voice Actor Radio","native":"声優ラジオのウラオモテ","romaji":"Seiyuu Radio no Uraomote","userPreferred":"Seiyuu Radio no Uraomote"},"trailer":{"id":"UKxaO-nqeNk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UKxaO-nqeNk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21049-PeKXMMYru3Xl.png","coverImage":{"color":"#aee4ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21049-4AHSLeiDE9eg.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21049-4AHSLeiDE9eg.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21049-4AHSLeiDE9eg.png"},"description":"The story follows Kaizaki Arata, a 27-year-old jobless man, who fails at every job interview he had after quitting his last company. His life changes after he met Yoake Ryou of the ReLife Research Institute, who offered him a drug that can change his appearance to 17-years-old and to become a subject in an experiment for one year. Thus, he begins his life as a high school student once more.\n","episodes":13,"format":"ONA","id":21049,"idMal":30015,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21049","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"ReLIFE","native":"ReLIFE","romaji":"ReLIFE","userPreferred":"ReLIFE"},"trailer":{"id":"fZCgXuxMAZY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/fZCgXuxMAZY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/4722-ZPCSfocx149r.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a143","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx4722-haxa25k1oSxU.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx4722-haxa25k1oSxU.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx4722-haxa25k1oSxU.png"},"description":"Kyouko followed her true love and childhood friend Shou to Tokyo so she could help him reach his dream of becoming an idol. She cleans, cooks, works three jobs and does nothing for herself because she loves him so much, but gets nothing in return. Still, she remains by his side. But then one day she goes unannounced to his agency with a delivery, and overhears him talking about her; he reveals to his manager that he only took her with him as a maid, and that he doesn't care for her at all. Upon hearing this, Kyouko doesn't just sit around and cry. She cuts and dyes her hair, changes her clothes and attitude and thus begins her journey to join showbiz and have her revenge against Shou.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Anime News Network)","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":4722,"idMal":4722,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/4722","startDate":{"day":6,"month":10,"year":2008},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Skip Beat!","native":"スキップ・ビート！","romaji":"Skip Beat!","userPreferred":"Skip Beat!"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/117195-VVYq1EEOwR0K.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e450a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png"},"description":"Gorou is a gynecologist and idol fan who’s in shock after his favorite star, Ai, announces an impromptu hiatus. Little does Gorou realize that he’s about to forge a bond with her that defies all common sense! Lies are an idol’s weapon! \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 14th and 15th Manga Taisho, the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize, the 67th Shogakukan Manga Award in the general category and the 46th Kodansha Manga Award.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Winner of the 7th Next Manga Award in the print category.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes two extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":14,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":117195,"idMal":126146,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117195","startDate":{"day":23,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Favorite Girl","My Idol's Child","[Mein*Star]","[เกิดใหม่เป็นลูกโอชิ]","Anak Idola","【OSHI NO KO】","【MOJA GWIAZDA】","【我推的孩子】","OSHI NO KO - DƯỚI ÁNH HÀO QUANG","Oshi no Ko: Minha Estrela Preferida","[Moje hvězda]","【OSHI NO KO】Mi Idol Favorita"],"title":{"english":"[Oshi no Ko]","native":"【推しの子】","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko]","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko]"},"trailer":{"id":"VTIB8snZ_lU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VTIB8snZ_lU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166531-vUu7iDwUkC67.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nAqua’s desire for revenge takes center stage as he navigates the dark underbelly of the entertainment world alongside his twin sister, Ruby. While Ruby follows in their slain mother’s footsteps to become an idol, Aqua joins a famous theater troupe in hopes of uncovering clues to the identity of his father — the man who arranged their mother’s untimely death, and the man who once starred in the same troupe Aqua hopes to infiltrate.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":10,"year":2024},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":166531,"idMal":55791,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2024,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166531","startDate":{"day":3,"month":7,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["我推的孩子"],"title":{"english":"Oshi no Ko Season 2","native":"【推しの子】第2期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 2nd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"QMuajQlx64c","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QMuajQlx64c/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207324-MsDp7ck3PIEl.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f10d0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg"},"description":"Music video directed by Emi Fukayama for the song \u003ci\u003eSerenade\u003c/i\u003e by natori. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The song featured in this music video also serves as the ending theme of the anime [Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season.","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":21,"month":1,"year":2026},"episodes":1,"format":"MUSIC","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":207324,"idMal":63349,"isAdult":false,"meanScor