{"node":{"id":335006,"name":{"full":"Suo Matsuhashi"}},"role":"Assistance"},{"node":{"id":387061,"name":{"full":"Marika Teraoka"}},"role":"Assistance"},{"node":{"id":148168,"name":{"full":"Kenji Sawada"}},"role":"Main Animator"},{"node":{"id":164761,"name":{"full":"Tetsuya Usami"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":299087,"name":{"full":"Kouta Mizumoto"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":156624,"name":{"full":"Akane Ashihara"}},"role":"Color Design"}]},"startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":95,"name":"Doga Kobo"}]},"trailer":{"id":"JGYY6Pui5Kc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JGYY6Pui5Kc/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:33:44.731868+03:00"},"184951":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":81,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":510281,"node":{"age":"16-17","dateOfBirth":{"day":30,"month":3},"description":"__Height:__ 158 cm (5'2\")\n\nAn energetic but self-conscious girl. She admires [Tani](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) for being the complete opposite of herself, but she can't interact with him normally and always ends up bothering him with pointless conversation. ","gender":"Female","id":281250,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b281250-3Ce6zhYCFWtN.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Miyu Suzuki","native":"鈴木みゆ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/281250"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":510284,"node":{"age":"17-18","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":11},"description":"__Height:__ 171 cm (5'7\")\n\nA quiet boy who clearly states his opinions. [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) always approaches him with a lighthearted vibe, but he always seems to reply curtly. ","gender":"Male","id":281251,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b281251-fpCKCGSQH6Rv.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yuusuke Tani","native":"谷悠介"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/281251"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":547065,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":10},"description":"__Height:__ 158 cm (5'2\")\n\nA girl from the same class as Nishi, with a dry, no-nonsense personality. She's logical and values efficiency in everything.She's close friends with Nishi and the only person Nishi communicates with normally.","gender":"Female","id":378435,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378435-NhrWQKUFcu9J.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rikako Honda","native":"本田梨花子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378435"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557681,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":387167,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387167-zMvMATsd0R8W.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yusuke's Grandmother"],"full":"Tani no Sobo","native":"谷の祖母"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387167"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":510282,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":22,"month":2},"description":"__Height:__ 147 cm (4'10\")\n\nA quiet and reserved girl from the class next to [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) who actually laughs at just about everything. She's extremely shy and bad at talking to classmates other than [Honda](https://anilist.co/character/378435/Rikako-Honda). One of her main worries is always being a beat behind in conversations.","gender":"Female","id":302624,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b302624-Uk2PVe27jAN6.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Natsumi Nishi","native":"西奈津美"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/302624"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557366,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":387018,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387018-kXXaYkKaQ4KJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Miyu's Mother"],"full":"Suzuki no Haha","native":"鈴木の母"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387018"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":510283,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":3,"month":6},"description":"__Height:__ 163 cm (5'4\")\n\nA mature-minded girl in [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani's](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) class. Though she comes off as jaded, she's never experienced a proper romantic relationship.","gender":"Female","id":302626,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b302626-CNCys5MLLoMk.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shino Azuma","native":"東紫乃"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/302626"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557367,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387019,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387019-v3Q0wE72LXAI.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Miyu's Brother"],"full":"Suzuki no Ani","native":"鈴木の兄"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387019"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":510285,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":10,"month":10},"description":"__Height:__ 180 cm (5'11\")\n\nA boy in [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani's](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) class with a cynical attitude. Lacking confidence, he often compares himself to others and ends up feeling insecure or down.","gender":"Male","id":302627,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b302627-6Udmewwwbani.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shuuji Taira","native":"平秀司"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/302627"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563574,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Miyu's classmate and ex-boyfriend from middle school.","gender":"Male","id":390850,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390850-Add26fg2Jp1J.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rihito Oka","native":"岡理人"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390850"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":565705,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":392474,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b392474-5aRLoWbyKiyL.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Miyu's Father"],"full":"Suzuki no Chichi","native":"鈴木の父"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/392474"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":510286,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":20,"month":4},"description":"__Height:__ 173 cm (5'8\")\n\nA cheerful, easygoing boy and classmate of [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani). He's the life of the party, open, honest, and quick to befriend anyone. He expresses his thoughts without holding back.","gender":"Male","id":302625,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b302625-oRbYsCHt58tt.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kentarou Yamada","native":"山田健太郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/302625"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559388,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":388227,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388227-4WrlbyeMk1qN.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Yuusuke's Mother"],"full":"Tani no Haha","native":"谷の母"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388227"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":541063,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":17,"month":6},"description":"__Height:__ 160 cm (5'3\")\n\nA quiet and cool-headed girl, also a classmate of [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani.](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) Calm and reliable, she tends to observe her friends' love lives with a rational, objective perspective.","gender":"Female","id":373190,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b373190-LhFzMz1ALZkx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Aoi Satou","native":"佐藤葵"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/373190"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559389,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Miyu's social studies teacher.","gender":"Male","id":388228,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388228-xEHvciy2Fx1E.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Masaru Gotou"],"full":"Gomapon","native":"ゴマポン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388228"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":541064,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{"day":7,"month":7},"description":"__Height:__ 155 cm (5'1\")\n\nA cheerful, upbeat classmate of [Suzuki](https://anilist.co/character/281250/Miyu-Suzuki) and [Tani.](https://anilist.co/character/281251/Yusuke-Tani) She's free-spirited and says exactly what's on her mind without hesitation.","gender":"Female","id":373191,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b373191-e6bXmVqmJIGA.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Manami Watanabe","native":"渡辺真奈美"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/373191"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":557372,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":387025,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387025-p0FvodEaU3cb.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Homeroom Teacher"],"full":"Tannin","native":"担任"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387025"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560898,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":389125,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Hahaoya","native":"母親"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389125"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":563578,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":390855,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Chuugaku no Tomodachi 3","native":"中学の友達3"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390855"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":565709,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":392478,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Jimoto no Joshi","native":"地元の女子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/392478"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":557682,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":387168,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b387168-hB43o8tSwwgI.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Reina","native":"れーな"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387168"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":562529,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":389940,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389940-9UJqrKJ9HJT6.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kouchou","native":"校長"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389940"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":564653,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"One of Miyu's classmates from middle school.","gender":"Male","id":391698,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b391698-XSIrtHn2G8ld.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mocchin","native":"モッチン"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/391698"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":557683,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":387169,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Gekijou Announce","native":"劇場アナウンス"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/387169"},"role":"BACKGROUND"},{"id":562530,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":389941,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Danshi","native":"男子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389941"},"role":"BACKGROUND"}]},"description":"Suzuki’s a high school girl in love, but the guy she’s fallen for is nothing like her! While she’s cheerful, outgoing, and always trying to fit in, her classmate Yusuke Tani is stoic, quiet, and doesn’t seem to care what people think of him. Will Suzuki be able to overcome her anxieties and ask him out, or will she discover that opposites really don’t attract?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":184951,"meanScore":81,"popularity":50805,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"TV","rank":245,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":6,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":8,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":6,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":8,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/141911-XqAZO540hFXw.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e4bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx141911-o6Jwav7hRPPM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx141911-o6Jwav7hRPPM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx141911-o6Jwav7hRPPM.jpg"},"description":"This country girl is ready for the big city! Well, at least she thought she was. Mitsumi’s dream is to attend a prestigious school and make the world a better place. But when she finally gets to Tokyo, it turns out she isn’t exactly prepared for city life. Luckily, she runs into Shima, a sweet and handsome classmate who becomes her first friend! Can she make it in Tokyo with Shima by her side?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":141911,"idMal":50416,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/141911","startDate":{"day":4,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Skip and Loafer","native":"スキップとローファー","romaji":"Skip to Loafer","userPreferred":"Skip to Loafer"},"trailer":{"id":"GcfUnbrsCJk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GcfUnbrsCJk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/132405-LnPQaqaksEpN.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx132405-qP7FQYGmNI3d.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx132405-qP7FQYGmNI3d.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx132405-qP7FQYGmNI3d.jpg"},"description":"High schooler Wakana Gojou cares about one thing: making Hina dolls. With nobody to share his obsession, he has trouble finding friends—or even holding conversation. But after the school’s most popular girl, Marin Kitagawa, reveals a secret of her own, he discovers a new purpose for his sewing skills. Together, they’ll make her cosplay dreams come true! \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":132405,"idMal":48736,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/132405","startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"My Dress-Up Darling","native":"その着せ替え人形は恋をする","romaji":"Sono Bisque Doll wa Koi wo Suru","userPreferred":"Sono Bisque Doll wa Koi wo Suru"},"trailer":{"id":"8oveGY6h6T8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8oveGY6h6T8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/124080-ARyLAHHgikRq.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx124080-oeviACzGv5Vx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx124080-oeviACzGv5Vx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx124080-oeviACzGv5Vx.jpg"},"description":"A secret life is the one thing they have in common. At school, Hori is a prim and perfect social butterfly, but the truth is she's a brash homebody. Meanwhile, under a gloomy facade, Miyamura hides a gentle heart, along with piercings and tattoos. In a chance meeting, they both reveal a side they've never shown. Could this blossom into something new?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":124080,"idMal":42897,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/124080","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Horimiya","native":"ホリミヤ","romaji":"Horimiya","userPreferred":"Horimiya"},"trailer":{"id":"tryurXgGqkI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/tryurXgGqkI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20668-hmoK9pH09pWT.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e47850","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20668-6UslJY5NDYNh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20668-6UslJY5NDYNh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20668-6UslJY5NDYNh.png"},"description":"You know how the story goes: girl crushes on guy, girl confesses feelings to guy, guy mistakes confession for a job application. Okay, maybe that's not how it usually goes, but that's what happens when Chiyo Sakura finally gets up the nerve to tell her classroom crush Nozaki how she feels. Since she doesn't know that he's secretly a manga artist who publishes under a female pen name, and he doesn't know that she doesn't know, he misunderstands and offers her a chance to work as his assistant instead of a date! But while it's not flowers and dancing, it is a chance to get closer to him, so Chiyo gamely accepts. And when Nozaki realizes how useful Chiyo can be in figuring out what girls find romantic, he'll be spending even more time with her \"researching\" while remaining completely clueless. Could Chiyo's romantic frustration possibly get any more drawn out of proportion?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":20668,"idMal":23289,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20668","startDate":{"day":7,"month":7,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Monthly Girls' Nozaki-kun","native":"月刊少女野崎くん","romaji":"Gekkan Shoujo Nozaki-kun","userPreferred":"Gekkan Shoujo Nozaki-kun"},"trailer":{"id":"-tHbKBCTDFQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-tHbKBCTDFQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/181444-SBhwJNPxjHrr.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#a1d6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg"},"description":"Chidori High is a boys’ school that takes in the dregs of society with the lowest grades. Next door stands Kikyo Girls’ High, where the wealthy, high-class families send their precious daughters. Chidori second-year Rintarou, who has a fierce face but a gentle heart, is helping at his family’s patisserie when he meets a girl named Kaoruko. The two hit it off right away…but this blissful peace is quickly disturbed when Rintarou discovers that Kaoruko is actually a student at Kikyo. Worse, she doesn’t seem to realize what a huge problem this really is! Will these two be able to forge a path for themselves, and sidestep the traps (metaphorical and literal) laid by their classmates?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":181444,"idMal":59845,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/181444","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Fragrant Flower Blooms With Dignity","native":"薫る花は凛と咲く","romaji":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku","userPreferred":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku"},"trailer":{"id":"wMDwbC-cAQg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wMDwbC-cAQg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n98291-cRLmqm7It2rZ.jpg","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx98291-LY6txxZTX8We.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx98291-LY6txxZTX8We.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx98291-LY6txxZTX8We.jpg"},"description":"To those of you out there who never could say \"I love you\"— This story is about ordinary highschoolers and how love makes them fired up, shaken, laugh, cry, and hurt. Whether things go well or not, this story of adolescence and romance will show you how they spend their precious youth. Every character is the main character here, and you're sure to find one you can sympathize with.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV_SHORT","id":98291,"idMal":34902,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/98291","startDate":{"day":4,"month":7,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Tsuredure Children","native":"徒然チルドレン","romaji":"Tsurezure Children","userPreferred":"Tsurezure Children"},"trailer":{"id":"g2LxeRRzD4w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/g2LxeRRzD4w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178005-X4Tr7p0sCQbx.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f15078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg"},"description":"Utage Kinoshita is a high school girl who works part-time as a housekeeper. She has devoted her life to her favorite idol, Tamon Fukuhara, from the group F/ACE. Then one day, Utage ends up being assigned to Tamon’s house! There she discovers that off-stage, he is nothing like his wild idol persona. A gloomy, introverted boy with no self-confidence, Utage still finds herself falling for him anyway.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":13,"format":"ONA","id":178005,"idMal":59047,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178005","startDate":{"day":1,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Tamon's B-Side","native":"多聞くん今どっち！？","romaji":"Tamon-kun Ima Docchi!?","userPreferred":"Tamon-kun Ima Docchi!?"},"trailer":{"id":"qFmSz2ZVxCA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qFmSz2ZVxCA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/141949-37BoBF129jLT.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#d6e45d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx141949-tViCIRHPZAyG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx141949-tViCIRHPZAyG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx141949-tViCIRHPZAyG.jpg"},"description":"Third-year high school student Jirou Yakuin hoped to partner with Shiori Sakurazaka of the same class in the mandatory \"Couple Practical\" course. In this practical, students must demonstrate that they have the necessary skillset to live with a partner of the opposite sex while presenting a certain level of harmony to the video surveillance that grades them.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nUnfortunately, random chance put his slightly subdued self into the practical with the person polar opposite to him, the gyaru Akari Watanabe. Akari on the other hand hoped to be paired with her crush Minami Tenjin.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nTheir hopes are doubly dashed when they find out that Shiori and Minami are assigned together. Thus, they reluctantly decide to cooperate to reach the top ten, which would give them the right to exchange partners if both couples agree. To that end, Jirou steals Akari's first kiss without realizing what he'd done, while giving a hurried good-bye kiss...","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":141949,"idMal":50425,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/141949","startDate":{"day":9,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"More than a Married Couple, but Not Lovers.","native":"夫婦以上、恋人未満。","romaji":"Fuufu Ijou, Koibito Miman.","userPreferred":"Fuufu Ijou, Koibito Miman."},"trailer":{"id":"2gHhxAksU9E","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2gHhxAksU9E/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/147997-GifZXKllbrw0.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15dbb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx147997-QSf3nuWPkYcE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx147997-QSf3nuWPkYcE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx147997-QSf3nuWPkYcE.jpg"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eWhen it comes to romance, opposites really do attract!\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMiyu Suzuki is a bright and bubbly high schooler who’s got a crush. There’s just one little problem—when it comes to personality, the guy she’s into is her polar opposite!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWhile she’s cheerful, outgoing, and always trying to fit in, her classmate Yusuke Tani is stoic and quiet, and he doesn’t seem to care what people think of him. Will Suzuki be able to overcome her anxieties and ask him out, or will she discover that opposites really don’t attract?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes three extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":25,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":147997,"idMal":147091,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/147997","startDate":{"day":2,"month":5,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["相反的你和我","Tú y yo somos polos opuestos","ลุ้นรักฉบับคู่ต่างขั้ว","Tentang Kita yang Bertolak Belakang"],"title":{"english":"You and I Are Polar Opposites","native":"正反対な君と僕","romaji":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku","userPreferred":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku"},"trailer":{"id":"feZ18ji7OjY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/feZ18ji7OjY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184951","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":203385,"name":{"full":"Koucha Agasawa"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":146101,"name":{"full":"Takakazu Nagatomo"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":128817,"name":{"full":"Teruko Utsumi"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":356764,"name":{"full":"Mako Miyako"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":135521,"name":{"full":"Naho Kozono"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":135521,"name":{"full":"Naho Kozono"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director"},{"node":{"id":141571,"name":{"full":"Sayuri Sakimoto"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director"},{"node":{"id":162389,"name":{"full":"Chieko Nakamura"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":119689,"name":{"full":"Tomoyuki Shiokawa"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":135534,"name":{"full":"Yuki Akimoto"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":128817,"name":{"full":"Teruko Utsumi"}},"role":"Animation Producer"},{"node":{"id":390137,"name":{"full":"Maike Siehl"}},"role":"ADR Script (German)"},{"node":{"id":145297,"name":{"full":"Stephanie Damare"}},"role":"ADR Director (German)"},{"node":{"id":389126,"name":{"full":"noa"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":105138,"name":{"full":"Eriko Kimura"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":387458,"name":{"full":"Juliana Martins"}},"role":"ADR Script (Brazilian Portuguese)"},{"node":{"id":164931,"name":{"full":"Kazuko Hayakawa"}},"role":"Chief Animation Director"},{"node":{"id":190844,"name":{"full":"tofubeats"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":179920,"name":{"full":"Rodolfo Novaes"}},"role":"ADR Director (Brazilian Portuguese)"},{"node":{"id":197594,"name":{"full":"André Rinaldi"}},"role":"ADR Director (Brazilian Portuguese)"},{"node":{"id":103970,"name":{"full":"Zachary Bolton"}},"role":"ADR Producer (English)"},{"node":{"id":96552,"name":{"full":"Andrew Tipps"}},"role":"ADR Mixer (English)"},{"node":{"id":282842,"name":{"full":"Jameson Outlaw"}},"role":"ADR Engineer (English)"},{"node":{"id":128531,"name":{"full":"Emily  Fajardo"}},"role":"ADR Director (English)"},{"node":{"id":138785,"name":{"full":"Macy Anne Johnson"}},"role":"ADR Script (English)"}]},"startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":6213,"name":"Lapin Track"}]},"trailer":{"id":"b5vpRUDkhT0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/b5vpRUDkhT0/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-02T03:43:20.645603+03:00"},"187901":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":61,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":523823,"node":{"id":342421,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{"day":19,"month":2},"name":{"full":"Kiyomi Urusugawa","native":"漆栖川希詠"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b342421-uvmcZEnn3LRe.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 160 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__ Parasocial Pistol\n\nA member of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B. A \"smotherer\", she spends her online time cyberstalking a bassist from a band she loves. Much like her love, her cyberkinesis manifests a gun that glues her to her target. She also loves eating sweet potato sticks and can't leave home without them.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/342421"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":523824,"node":{"id":342422,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":11},"name":{"full":"Kukuru Kasubata","native":"霞流括"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b342422-YyYc3r3T7CVS.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 180 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__ Banhammer of Civility\n\nA member of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B, and Souji's roommate. A former gang member, he tends to use foul language but immediately course-corrects to act like a proper honors student. \n\nA \"thumper\", he has a daily routine of posting comments online to \"correct the evil that overflows on the internet.\" His cyberkinesis, in turn, manifests as a massive hammer that keeps the peace of internet discourse.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/342422"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":523825,"node":{"id":298421,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","age":"15","dateOfBirth":{"day":3,"month":8},"name":{"alternative":["Aoringo (煽りんご)","Aori Enjou"],"full":"Souji Enishiro","native":"縁城蒼吏"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298421-VKXSMRPjQyih.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 173 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__  Onipien\n\nHe is one of the most well-known problematic streamers and is best known for his MyTuber username \"Aoringo.\" After the death of his sister, he is enrolled into Miden Academy to find the person responsible for her death. His cyberkenesis, owing to his past as a flamebaiter, calls forth eerie blue flames. Loves sweets, but often eats too much of them.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298421"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":539304,"node":{"id":342423,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":30,"month":4},"name":{"full":"Renri Hasumi","native":"羽住蓮理"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b342423-BeJHl2GS1V8G.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 175 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__ World Through a Shutter\n\nA member of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B, and Kukuru's childhood friend. In spite of his kind expression, he can also be a venomous little devil at times. Loves snappingphotos on his phone, and his cyberkinesis allows him to create \"windows\" wherever he's taken one. ","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/342423"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":539305,"node":{"id":342424,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":26,"month":5},"name":{"full":"Naruhiko Emoto","native":"柄本成彦"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b342424-P7v2CItuH117.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 183 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__ Nirvana Wall\n\nA member of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B. Contrary to his appearance, he doesn't like loud noises and is easily frightened. His cyberkinesis is more defense-oriented, creating walls of sound to protect himself and others when he listens to his MP3 player. Likes music, especially rock, and listens to them with his headphones gifted to him by his teacher.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/342424"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":539306,"node":{"id":342425,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":7,"month":7},"name":{"full":"Yoimaru Azaki","native":"痣木宵丸"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b342425-no2tOn5OM45M.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 188 cm\n\nTeacher of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B. Once called the genius youth of exorcists, he now works to teach the next generation of them. Digitally inept, he can only fight dead accounts by converting his spiritual energy to digital using a special fan - while incredibly powerful, it's only a fraction of his power in its prime. Zero immunity to women. ","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/342425"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":539571,"node":{"id":371625,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{"day":2,"month":1},"name":{"full":"Hiyori Haijima","native":"灰島ひより"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b371625-rZFdrNiVMxdk.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 146 cm\n__Cyberkinesis:__ Hardcore Gamer-Powered Doll\n\nA member of Miden Academy's Level 1 Class B, an esports player and expert in hand-to-hand combat. She's withdrawn and loath to communicate in person, but her cyberkinesis allows her to control dolls that she can control using her video game skills. Typically uses Denmi-chan, Miden Academy's mascot, in battle.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/371625"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":551408,"node":{"id":382255,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":10,"month":6},"name":{"full":"Minoru Wagari","native":"輪狩実"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382255-8QvYWgJUVhkw.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 179 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382255"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559695,"node":{"id":388363,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":14,"month":12},"name":{"full":"Jien Otoya","native":"茲苑堕也"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388363-HQ1W8w1F3URW.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 191 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388363"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563502,"node":{"id":390788,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Mimi Iizuka","native":"飯塚美味"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390788-bFsLZsLfJMJu.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390788"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551409,"node":{"id":382256,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{"day":2,"month":2},"name":{"full":"Eru Kusaba","native":"草場恵流"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382256-I2cM8CPICZ4A.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 158 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382256"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559696,"node":{"id":388368,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Kakiko Itabashi","native":"板橋柿子"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388368-FnYs9JydSx3t.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388368"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563503,"node":{"id":390789,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Kizuki Asatsuji","native":"朝辻綺月"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390789-iX8LDchZtNna.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390789"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551410,"node":{"id":382257,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":7},"name":{"full":"Ikko Oowada","native":"大和田一狐"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382257-rcNCYR173Afg.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 174 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382257"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559697,"node":{"id":388369,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Korekiyo Nanzou","native":"南蔵是清"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388369-Uc9P9BjyGRl6.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388369"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563504,"node":{"id":390790,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Sad Boy K","The Lonely K"],"full":"Sabishigariya no K","native":"寂しがり屋のK"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390790-ZZ1l4kgkcCiV.png"},"description":"The current biggest enemy of the Exorcist Association, and the monster that killed Souji's sister Akari. Through social media, he amplifies people's \"regrets\" and then kills them, creating ghosts. He controls a blue demonic fire like Souji, but what he was like in life is unknown.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390790"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551411,"node":{"id":382258,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":30,"month":3},"name":{"full":"Kiri Namekawa","native":"滑川霧"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382258-g99mjry4WWrZ.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 150 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382258"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559699,"node":{"id":388366,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{"day":24,"month":10},"name":{"full":"Konami Kanno","native":"菅野小波"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388366-dwhCLdj2FqkQ.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 167 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388366"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563505,"node":{"id":390791,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"GARAN","native":"GARAN"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390791-AkFag4rRA9G2.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390791"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551412,"node":{"id":382259,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":25,"month":12},"name":{"full":"Ban Ashina","native":"亜科伴"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382259-X8GLyEdK92op.png"},"description":"__Height:__ 186 cm","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382259"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563322,"node":{"id":390632,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Mina Kouchi","native":"高地美耶"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390632-gqQhAGs4mRcE.png"},"description":"__Cyberkinesis:__  Airbrush Effect\n\nMiden Academy's infirmary doctor.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390632"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559669,"node":{"id":388360,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Akari Enishiro","native":"緑城緋里"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388360-HBkz7KNITnuC.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388360"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563340,"node":{"id":390655,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Kenji Ekoza","native":"會古坐顕路"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390655-ylfgJZpwdcju.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390655"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559693,"node":{"id":388370,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Kyuuko Yabami","native":"矢喰究子"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388370-4jpH0uQjMsIj.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388370"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":563500,"node":{"id":390786,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Sabato Ochi","native":"越智哉人"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b390786-PPHa8JoO9LfG.png"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/390786"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction’s sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he’s nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he’s high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister’s medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn’t care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"id":187901,"meanScore":62,"popularity":16521,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":36,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":39,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":22,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/9919-S5idQm3GbZ80.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#aed6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx9919-nXS7JOZrWHfS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx9919-nXS7JOZrWHfS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx9919-nXS7JOZrWHfS.jpg"},"description":"This world consists of two dimensions joined as one, like a mirror. The first is the world in which the humans live, Assiah. The other is the world of demons, Gehenna. Ordinarily, travel between the two, and indeed any kind of contact between the two, is impossible. However the demons can pass over into this world by possessing anything that exist within it. Satan the god of demons, but there's one thing that he doesn't have, and that's a substance in the human world that is powerful enough to contain him!! For that purpose he created Rin, his son from a human woman, but will his son agree to his plans? Or will he become something else...? An exorcist?\n","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":9919,"idMal":9919,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/9919","startDate":{"day":17,"month":4,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Blue Exorcist","native":"青の祓魔師","romaji":"Ao no Exorcist","userPreferred":"Ao no Exorcist"},"trailer":{"id":"0HHNeeXrysA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0HHNeeXrysA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177474-ZIPsMWa6RO0i.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#ff5d1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177474-oHil1yLWldfl.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177474-oHil1yLWldfl.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177474-oHil1yLWldfl.jpg"},"description":"The bloodlines of “Oni” and “Momotarou” have been passed down among certain humans for generations.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nLong ago, the Oni, aware of their own ferocity, lived in seclusion. However, their peace was shattered by an invasion led by Momotarou.\nOver thousands of years, these two factions formed the “Momotarou Agency” and the “Oni Agency,” respectively, and have been locked in conflict ever since.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe protagonist, Shiki Ichinose, suddenly learns of his Oni lineage following an unexpected attack by Momotarou. This revelation sets Shiki on a path to discover the destiny that lies within his blood — a meeting with the Oni dwelling within him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n—A new generation of dark heroics begins here in this tale of demons!\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":177474,"idMal":58811,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177474","startDate":{"day":11,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"TOUGEN ANKI","native":"桃源暗鬼","romaji":"Tougen Anki","userPreferred":"Tougen Anki"},"trailer":{"id":"2AddvIbCrr8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2AddvIbCrr8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113415-jQBSkxWAAk83.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx113415-LHBAeoZDIsnF.jpg"},"description":"A boy fights... for \"the right death.\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nHardship, regret, shame: the negative feelings that humans feel become Curses that lurk in our everyday lives. The Curses run rampant throughout the world, capable of leading people to terrible misfortune and even death. What's more, the Curses can only be exorcised by another Curse.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nItadori Yuji is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a friend who has been attacked by Curses, he eats the finger of the Double-Faced Specter, taking the Curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with the Double-Faced Specter. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Gojou Satoru, Itadori is admitted to the Tokyo Metropolitan Technical High School of Sorcery, an organization that fights the Curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a Curse to exorcise a Curse, a life from which he could never turn back.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode received an early web premiere on September 19th, 2020. The regular TV broadcast started on October 3rd, 2020.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":113415,"idMal":40748,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113415","startDate":{"day":3,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN","native":"呪術廻戦","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen"},"trailer":{"id":"pkKu9hLT-t8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pkKu9hLT-t8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/269-08ar2HJOUAuL.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx269-d2GmRkJbMopq.png"},"description":"Ichigo Kurosaki is a rather normal high school student apart from the fact he has the ability to see ghosts. This ability never impacted his life in a major way until the day he encounters the Shinigami Kuchiki Rukia, who saves him and his family's lives from a Hollow, a corrupt spirit that devours human souls. \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWounded during the fight against the Hollow, Rukia chooses the only option available to defeat the monster and passes her Shinigami powers to Ichigo. Now forced to act as a substitute until Rukia recovers, Ichigo hunts down the Hollows that plague his town. \n\n\n","episodes":366,"format":"TV","id":269,"idMal":269,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/269","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2004},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Bleach","native":"BLEACH","romaji":"BLEACH","userPreferred":"BLEACH"},"trailer":{"id":"0c4IoCA5fY0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0c4IoCA5fY0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/11633-LRJK2MSqP1Ya.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#d6c91a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx11633-vIjtabJq64Xt.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx11633-vIjtabJq64Xt.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx11633-vIjtabJq64Xt.jpg"},"description":"Staz is the vampire boss of a section of the demon world, but he has little interest in human blood. He's more infatuated with Japanese culture. When he learns that Yanagi Fuyumi, a Japanese teenage girl, accidentally wanders into the demon city, he jumps to the occasion. However, while Staz deals with an intruder on his turf, the oblivious Fuyumi is killed by a monster and becomes a wandering ghost. The disappointed Staz vows to her that he will find a way to bring Fuyumi back to life.\n","episodes":10,"format":"TV","id":11633,"idMal":11633,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/11633","startDate":{"day":8,"month":7,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Blood Lad","native":"ブラッドラッド","romaji":"Blood Lad","userPreferred":"Blood Lad"},"trailer":{"id":"bBBp1tw_vEI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bBBp1tw_vEI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/163270-fcjrqp3iKWdb.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#288643","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163270-wboZJp0ybwVK.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163270-wboZJp0ybwVK.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx163270-wboZJp0ybwVK.jpg"},"description":"Where the average scores are the lowest, but the fights are the strongest. Furin High School is renowned as a super school of delinquents. Haruka Sakura, a first-year student, came from outside the city to fight to the top. However, Furin High School has become a group that protects the town called the “Chime of the Wind Breaker” – Bofurin. The heroic legend of high school delinquent Sakura begins here!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":163270,"idMal":54900,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/163270","startDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"WIND BREAKER","native":"WIND BREAKER","romaji":"WIND BREAKER","userPreferred":"WIND BREAKER"},"trailer":{"id":"62r_G9bEPlU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/62r_G9bEPlU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/171018-SpwPNAduszXl.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e47850","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx171018-60q1B6GK2Ghb.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx171018-60q1B6GK2Ghb.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx171018-60q1B6GK2Ghb.jpg"},"description":"This is a story about Momo, a high school girl who comes from a family of spirit mediums, and her classmate Okarun, an occult fanatic. After Momo rescues Okarun from being bullied, they begin talking. However, an argument ensues between them since Momo believes in ghosts but denies aliens exist, and Okarun believes in aliens but denies ghosts exist.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTo prove to each other what they believe in is real, Momo goes to an abandoned hospital where a UFO has been spotted and Okarun goes to a tunnel rumored to be haunted. To their surprise, they each encounter overwhelming paranormal activities that transcend comprehension. Amid these predicaments, Momo awakens her hidden power and Okarun gains the power of a curse to overcome these new dangers! Their fateful love begins as well!?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story of the occult battle and adolescence starts!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll) \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eNotes: \u003cbr\u003e\n- Worldwide premiere of Episode 1 before the Japanese television premiere occurred at Anime Expo July 6, 2024. \u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 1-3 titled as \u003cb\u003eDAN DA DAN: FIRST ENCOUNTER\u003c/b\u003e was pre-screened in advance in theaters on August 31, 2024 in Asia, September 7, 2024 in Europe and September 13, 2024 in North America. The regular TV broadcast began October 4, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":171018,"idMal":57334,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/171018","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"DAN DA DAN","native":"ダンダダン","romaji":"Dandadan","userPreferred":"Dandadan"},"trailer":{"id":"vnRmIBoyfBM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/vnRmIBoyfBM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/174653-Rq9ikE3MDb4x.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx174653-OsnK4BuENjUT.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx174653-OsnK4BuENjUT.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx174653-OsnK4BuENjUT.jpg"},"description":"Scrawny high school student Hobin Yu is probably the last guy you’d expect to star in a NewTube channel that revolves around fighting. But after following some advice from a mysterious NewTube channel, Hobin is soon knocking out guys stronger than him and raking in more money than he could have ever dreamed of. Can Hobin keep this up, or will he eventually meet his match?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":174653,"idMal":58080,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/174653","startDate":{"day":11,"month":4,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Viral Hit","native":"喧嘩独学","romaji":"Kenka Dokugaku","userPreferred":"Kenka Dokugaku"},"trailer":{"id":"zKFWWXhcZrQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zKFWWXhcZrQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":160460,"idMal":155118,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/160460","status":"RELEASING","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","synonyms":["デドアカ","DEAD ACCOUNT 死亡帳號","데드 어카운트"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":72,"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction's sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he's nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he's high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister's medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn't care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K Manga, edited)","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"title":{"english":"Dead Account","native":"デッドアカウント","romaji":"Dead Account","userPreferred":"Dead Account"},"coverImage":{"color":"#1abbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx160460-x45Jr2637Frf.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx160460-x45Jr2637Frf.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx160460-x45Jr2637Frf.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":18,"month":1,"year":2023},"endDate":{}},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187901","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":107131,"name":{"full":"Shizumu Watanabe"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":209761,"name":{"full":"Hiroya Saitou"}},"role":"Director "},{"node":{"id":110939,"name":{"full":"Mitsutaka Hirota"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":118971,"name":{"full":"Saho Yamane"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":235726,"name":{"full":"Seika Fujii"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":196452,"name":{"full":"Haruka Serizawa"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":233023,"name":{"full":"Yuusuke Ueno"}},"role":"Editing"},{"node":{"id":138285,"name":{"full":"Ryousuke Naya"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":115885,"name":{"full":"Keiji Inai"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":366900,"name":{"full":"Miyu Kaneko"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED)"},{"node":{"id":382262,"name":{"full":"Haru Igarashi"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":207743,"name":{"full":"James Baker"}},"role":"ADR Mixer (English)"},{"node":{"id":95313,"name":{"full":"Caitlin Glass"}},"role":"ADR Director (English)"},{"node":{"id":148687,"name":{"full":"Samantha Herek"}},"role":"ADR Producer (English)"},{"node":{"id":129028,"name":{"full":"Howard Wang"}},"role":"ADR Script (English)"},{"node":{"id":269724,"name":{"full":"Noah Whitehead"}},"role":"ADR Engineer (English)"},{"node":{"id":208636,"name":{"full":"Domonique French"}},"role":"ADR Script (English)"}]},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":118,"name":"SynergySP"}]},"trailer":{"id":"ynnk0CIyu10","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ynnk0CIyu10/hqdefault.jpg"}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T05:59:21.790136+03:00"},"187942":{"value":{"Media":{"averageScore":69,"characters":{"edges":[{"id":523910,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Iko is a member of Fuurin high school's broadcasting club. She dreams of becoming a Vtuber.","gender":"Female","id":339096,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b339096-kAM2CwKPxg4h.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Iko Kirino","native":"霧乃イコ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/339096"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":523911,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Shinobu is a member of Fuurin high school's broadcasting club. She dreams of becoming an announcer","gender":"Female","id":339095,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b339095-dUyxQfd5nyOu.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shinobu Uzuki","native":"雨月しのぶ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/339095"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":523912,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Rikka is the president of Fuurin high school's broadcasting club. She dreams of becoming a singer.","gender":"Female","id":339098,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b339098-HM8ujhptLjAR.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rikka Inohana","native":"井ノ花六花"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/339098"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":523914,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Nene is a member of Fuurin high school's broadcasting club. She dreams of becoming a voice actress.","gender":"Female","id":339099,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b339099-WAPop7ezUO3P.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Nene Himekawa","native":"日芽川寧々"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/339099"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":525158,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Arisu is a transfer student at Fuurin high school. He enters the broadcasting club because he's looking for the host of a radio show he used to listen to years ago, who he believes to be one of the club members.","gender":"Male","id":339097,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b339097-plfluCmjRz0T.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Gofer Boy","Bucky"],"full":"Arisu Yamabuki","native":"山吹有栖"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/339097"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":543079,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Advisor to the broadcasting club who yearns to be called \"Lemon-chan.\" She tries not to rock the boat or stand out but still helps the club.","gender":"Female","id":375232,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b375232-LtjUq9L8o7VJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Lemon Andou","native":"安藤檸檬"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/375232"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":555176,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is a student at Furin High School, and Rikka's former band memeber. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Tune in to the Midnight Heart Wiki)","gender":"Female","id":385344,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b385344-2Fvjl1IsCHMs.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Aiko","native":"アイコ"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/385344"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":555177,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Momotose Ao is a famous VTuber and side character in Tune In to the Midnight Heart. As part of the VTuber group Blue Box, she has over 3 million subscribers and does streaming as well as live shows. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Tune in to the Midnight Heart Wiki)","gender":"Female","id":385342,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b385342-M98N5a1IhqZB.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ao Momotose","native":"百歳あお"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/385342"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"When Arisu Yamabuki was all alone in bed at night, he was able to find solace in the voice of a radio host who went by “Apollo.” However, one day, she simply stopped broadcasting without any explanation. Years then passed, and Arisu is now a second-year high-schooler. He makes it his mission to search for Apollo, as there is something he wants to tell her. He doesn’t know what she looks like, or even what her real name is, but he manages to get some leads on her in his school’s broadcasting club. That’s where he meets four girls who all dream to get a job where they can make full use of their voices! Just who is Apollo, and how will those four’s dreams pan out?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K Manga)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2026},"genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":187942,"meanScore":70,"popularity":27549,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":21,"type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":24,"type":"POPULAR","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"TV","rank":21,"season":"WINTER","type":"RATED","year":2026},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":14,"season":"WINTER","type":"POPULAR","year":2026}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/103572-qRtBguYOOR2j.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4436b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx103572-cchriAdH95cQ.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx103572-cchriAdH95cQ.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx103572-cchriAdH95cQ.png"},"description":"Uesugi Fuutarou, a high school second-year from a poor family, receives a highly appealing offer to work part-time as a tutor... but his students turn out to be girls from his own class! What's more, they're quintuplets... and all five are beautiful, but happen to be problem students who have borderline grades and hate studying! Looks like his first assignment will be to win all the sisters' trust?! Every day is a wild party in this rom-com centering around the quintuplet sisters of the Nakano household!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":103572,"idMal":38101,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/103572","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Quintessential Quintuplets","native":"五等分の花嫁","romaji":"Go-toubun no Hanayome","userPreferred":"Go-toubun no Hanayome"},"trailer":{"id":"pCwfEB6PbFk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pCwfEB6PbFk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/164172-ceuofxXerReI.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e47850","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx164172-GY2aqItIuqtR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx164172-GY2aqItIuqtR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx164172-GY2aqItIuqtR.jpg"},"description":"Uryuu Kamihate is a high school student striving to enter Kyoto University’s medical school. After being raised at an orphanage, Uryuu is taken in by the chief priest at Amagami Shrine, where he begins to live as a freeloader—and to cohabit with Yae, Yuna, and Asahi, the three beautiful shrine maiden sisters! What’s more, the condition he must meet in order to live at the shrine for free is to marry into the family and inherit the shrine! How will Uryuu overcome his marriage meetings with the three sisters as well as the many challenges that Amagami Shrine faces? So begins a miraculous rom-com about living under the same roof with three shrine maidens!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":164172,"idMal":55071,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/164172","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Tying the Knot with an Amagami Sister","native":"甘神さんちの縁結び","romaji":"Amagami-san Chi no Enmusubi","userPreferred":"Amagami-san Chi no Enmusubi"},"trailer":{"id":"pwb10_z0zvw","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pwb10_z0zvw/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/103900-I3gUCm5xlsyX.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#c9f1f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx103900-E3rqgpq4X0Py.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx103900-E3rqgpq4X0Py.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx103900-E3rqgpq4X0Py.jpg"},"description":"His late father always said that a useless man should strive to be useful, so to that end, third-year high school student Nariyuki Yuiga dedicated himself to becoming a high-achieving student in his school, despite his history of poor grades. In order to give his destitute family a better life, his ultimate goal is to obtain the special VIP nomination, a prestigious scholarship covering all future university tuition fees. Although Nariyuki could feasibly be a shoe-in for the nomination, he is constantly overshadowed by classmates Rizu Ogata and Fumino Furuhashi in mathematics and literature, respectively.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTo his delight, Nariyuki receives the nomination, but there’s a catch: he has to tutor his two star classmates, who are each hopelessly mediocre at the other’s subject of expertise! To make matters worse, the subjects they are horrible at are the same subjects they want to pursue for their future. As the time to submit university applications draws nearer, Nariyuki must find an effective tutoring method for the girls before it’s too late.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Website)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":103900,"idMal":38186,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/103900","startDate":{"day":7,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"We Never Learn: BOKUBEN","native":"ぼくたちは勉強ができない","romaji":"Bokutachi wa Benkyou ga Dekinai","userPreferred":"Bokutachi wa Benkyou ga Dekinai"},"trailer":{"id":"CXQdqp6JFxI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CXQdqp6JFxI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/18897-h3TRFmkGYLkd.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx18897-G2Fx2ZACsXBU.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx18897-G2Fx2ZACsXBU.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx18897-G2Fx2ZACsXBU.jpg"},"description":"As a child, Raku Ichijo made a secret promise with his childhood sweetheart, keeping a pendant as a memento while his love took the key. He dreams of one day meeting his past love, but years later, reality smashes his hopes when Chitoge Kirisaki accidentally knees him in the face...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThough Raku's a normal high schooler, his family heads the notorious yakuza gang the Shuei-Gumi faction! And he's dragged into family affairs when he's forced into a relationship with Chitoge, the daughter of a rival gang's boss!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDespite their constant spats, the two somehow fool everyone with their false relationship. Raku then discovers that Chitoge has a mysterious key from her past, which she can't remember... Plus, two other girls appear with keys as well—Kosaki Onodera and Marika Tachibana!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nCaught in the midst of this love maelstrom, even more complications arise for Raku when his class decides on Romeo and Juliet as the class's play for the school festival. Can the two false lovebirds pull off the impossible and make the play a success?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)","episodes":20,"format":"TV","id":18897,"idMal":18897,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/18897","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Nisekoi","native":"ニセコイ","romaji":"Nisekoi","userPreferred":"Nisekoi"},"trailer":{"id":"PuB1VpKbWtE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/PuB1VpKbWtE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/154412-xecstCsfPLIe.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx154412-bEMQkJWOStDR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx154412-bEMQkJWOStDR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx154412-bEMQkJWOStDR.jpg"},"description":"After inheriting his late grandmother’s failing café, Hayato sees it as a bother and plans to sell it for a quick buck. Until he discovers five beautiful girls staying there! When they beg him to keep the café open, Hayato reluctantly gives in. Can he manage the seaside shop while learning to live with these unruly women?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":154412,"idMal":52973,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/154412","startDate":{"day":8,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Café Terrace and Its Goddesses","native":"女神のカフェテラス","romaji":"Megami no Café Terrace","userPreferred":"Megami no Café Terrace"},"trailer":{"id":"SyoNRBW3g7g","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SyoNRBW3g7g/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/180082-EoMpR2lHsD73.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#43aeff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx180082-IZAlf06G2VVm.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx180082-IZAlf06G2VVm.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx180082-IZAlf06G2VVm.png"},"description":"Being popular isn’t easy. It’s hard to beat Saku Chitose. The most popular kid in his high school? Check. An ironclad reputation that can weather even vicious online attacks? Check. A group of friends as attractive on the outside as they are inside? Check. But when a teacher asks for his help bringing back a student who has been shut away in his room for months, Saku’s perfect world will never be the same. What is this, some kind of normie harem story...?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode has an extended runtime of ~34 minutes.\u003c/i\u003e","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":180082,"idMal":59517,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/180082","startDate":{"day":7,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Chitose Is in the Ramune Bottle","native":"千歳くんはラムネ瓶のなか","romaji":"Chitose-kun wa Ramune Bin no Naka","userPreferred":"Chitose-kun wa Ramune Bin no Naka"},"trailer":{"id":"wC7FYPFHLeQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wC7FYPFHLeQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/13367-DtBXQ4MPjgZF.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f18650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx13367-mjPgNBIcatlt.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx13367-mjPgNBIcatlt.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx13367-mjPgNBIcatlt.png"},"description":"Is insanity hereditary? Shougo Mikadono's beginning to think so, because the terms of his late father's will seem crazy and following them may drive Shougo bonkers as well. Oh, it sounds simple at first: before Shougo can claim his VERY large inheritance, he just has to start attending a certain new school and find a nice girl to marry. It's a little unromantic, but perfectly do-able, right? After all, all the girls seem quite friendly, so all Shougo has to do is find one he has something in common with. EXCEPT, and here's the kicker, it turns out that Shougo has WAY too much in common with one of them, because she's actually his long lost sister! And he has no idea which one she is! Will Shougo meet and court his Miss Right without committing something very morally wrong? Can he find his future bride without slipping into the wrong set of genes? And if his little sister does reveal herself, just how much will be revealed and under what circumstances? \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks) ","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":13367,"idMal":13367,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":60,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/13367","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"NAKAIMO - My Little Sister Is Among Them!","native":"この中に1人, 妹がいる！","romaji":"Kono Naka ni Hitori, Imouto ga Iru!","userPreferred":"Kono Naka ni Hitori, Imouto ga Iru!"},"trailer":{"id":"VECze5u2K6w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VECze5u2K6w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178022-bxiuw2sgcTsS.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178022-gB3zAfazGBJ6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178022-gB3zAfazGBJ6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178022-gB3zAfazGBJ6.jpg"},"description":"On the picturesque island of Tonakijima with a population of only 600, Hana’s favorite pastime is reading literature to the island’s children. Her narration skills are second to none, and Mizuki, the president of the school’s broadcasting club immediately recognizes Hana’s ability to engage with others and draw them into her recitations. Invited by Mizuki to join the club, Hana embarks on a journey to discover her true love of reading — and maybe even change the course of her life along the way.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: HIDIVE)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":178022,"idMal":59055,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178022","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Flower and Asura","native":"花は咲く、修羅の如く","romaji":"Hana wa Saku, Shura no Gotoku","userPreferred":"Hana wa Saku, Shura no Gotoku"},"trailer":{"id":"Hbu5KOGlihs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Hbu5KOGlihs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/169272-2LF1bU4MnwQc.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9e4f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg"},"description":"When Arisu Yamabuki was all alone in bed at night, he was able to find solace in the voice of a radio host who went by “Apollo.” However, one day, she simply stopped broadcasting without any explanation. Years then passed, and Arisu is now a second-year high-schooler. He makes it his mission to search for Apollo, as there is something he wants to tell her. He doesn’t know what she looks like, or even what her real name is, but he manages to get some leads on her in his school’s broadcasting club. That’s where he meets four girls who all dream to get a job where they can make full use of their voices! Just who is Apollo, and how will those four’s dreams pan out?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K MANGA)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":169272,"idMal":162964,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/169272","startDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sintonía Del Corazón a Medianoche","午夜的傾心旋律","Mayochu"],"title":{"english":"Tune In to the Midnight Heart","native":"真夜中ハートチューン","romaji":"Mayonaka Heart Tune","userPreferred":"Mayonaka Heart Tune"},"trailer":{"id":"AX2juUGZ9zI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AX2juUGZ9zI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187942","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":122225,"name":{"full":"Masakuni Igarashi"}},"role":"Original Creator"},{"node":{"id":217932,"name":{"full":"Masayuki Takahashi"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":121844,"name":{"full":"Yukie Sugawara"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":106064,"name":{"full":"Tomoyuki Shitaya"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":142430,"name":{"full":"Minori Homura"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":143234,"name":{"full":"Yurika Someya"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":269677,"name":{"full":"Mikio"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":300261,"name":{"full":"Akihiro Kikuchi"}},"role":"Sub Character Design"},{"node":{"id":120031,"name":{"full":"Masakazu Miyake"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":165539,"name":{"full":"Yukiko Uegaki"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":128853,"name":{"full":"Azusa Sasaki"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":348364,"name":{"full":"Souta Hiroshima"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":186970,"name":{"full":"Akio Hayashi"}},"role":"Assistant Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":211987,"name":{"full":"Tsutomu Nomoto"}},"role":"CG Director"},{"node":{"id":147481,"name":{"full":"Yuuichi Morita"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":154774,"name":{"full":"Kuniyuki Takahashi"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":370149,"name":{"full":"Ami Hayashi"}},"role":"CG Layout"},{"node":{"id":146478,"name":{"full":"Ayako Tan"}},"role":"Offline Editing"},{"node":{"id":174835,"name":{"full":"Suisei Hoshimachi"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":311360,"name":{"full":"Takashi Iwami"}},"role":"Theme Song Lyrics (OP)"},{"node":{"id":311360,"name":{"full":"Takashi Iwami"}},"role":"Theme Song Arrangement (OP)"},{"node":{"id":311360,"name":{"full":"Takashi Iwami"}},"role":"Theme Song Composition (OP)"},{"node":{"id":381828,"name":{"full":"Soala"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED)"},{"node":{"id":38