PORTING"},{"id":187835,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":147069,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b147069-zWXRGX0OInp6.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Torino Kazami","native":"風巳とりの"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/147069"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":187843,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":147081,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b147081-QhK63xIXkfYv.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"E9","native":"E9"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/147081"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":500457,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"id":343155,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ritter A","native":"リッターA"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/343155"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"description":"After adorable “mermaid” Mamori is transferred to one of five artificial islands, she’s cornered, attacked and eventually saved by another beautiful transfer named Mirei. Unfortunately, even after the girl intervenes, Mamori’s attackers refuse to let up. Just when they think all hope is lost, Mirei and Mamori share a passionate kiss that turns the little “mermaid” into a powerful sword.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: FUNimation)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":12,"year":2015},"genres":["Action","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance","Sci-Fi"],"id":21116,"meanScore":55,"popularity":35944,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":72,"type":"POPULAR","year":2015},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"TV","rank":19,"season":"FALL","type":"POPULAR","year":2015}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/162780-rZ0KpsfCg2IA.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx162780-brAdNEROhZdG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx162780-brAdNEROhZdG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx162780-brAdNEROhZdG.jpg"},"description":"Hiiragi Utena is a major fangirl of the magical girls protecting her city, so when she has the chance to become one herself, she leaps at the chance to join their technicolor ranks… but when she transforms, she learns she isn’t fated to be a daring do-gooder, but rather a villain on the side of evil! At first she tries to quit her new gig as the leader of the local baddies, but she quickly realizes she enjoys it and is a total natural at tormenting the magical girls she loves so much. With both a bang and a whimper, Hiragi’s journey as a magical-girl-tormenting sadist has begun!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","episodes":13,"format":"TV","id":162780,"idMal":54722,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/162780","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Gushing Over Magical Girls","native":"魔法少女にあこがれて","romaji":"Mahou Shoujo ni Akogarete","userPreferred":"Mahou Shoujo ni Akogarete"},"trailer":{"id":"hOgF0D8Pcjs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hOgF0D8Pcjs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n20806-rXk0tGTLIehi.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20806-TFTl8bavYzvc.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20806-TFTl8bavYzvc.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20806-TFTl8bavYzvc.jpg"},"description":"Betrayed, stripped of her birthright, and declared less than human. Everything that Princess Angelise Ikaruga Misurugi of the Misurugi Empire thought she knew about her world was a lie. Now, for the crime of not being able to use magic, she’s been sentenced to certain death as a slave-soldier. The girl now known as Ange is no longer an innocent Princess: she’s learning how to kill draconic invaders, defending the same traitors who stole her life. However, they made a fatal mistake: they gave her access to an incredible weapon.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)","episodes":25,"format":"TV","id":20806,"idMal":25731,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20806","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Cross Ange: Rondo of Angel and Dragon","native":"クロスアンジュ 天使と竜の輪舞","romaji":"Cross Ange: Tenshi to Ryuu no Rondo","userPreferred":"Cross Ange: Tenshi to Ryuu no Rondo"},"trailer":{"id":"_aQF5kye0kg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_aQF5kye0kg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20705-BD0QCm8eyzr5.png","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20705-X2uRDZWD6xGn.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20705-X2uRDZWD6xGn.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20705-X2uRDZWD6xGn.jpg"},"description":"In the story, the prideful archangel Lucifer disobeys God and is cast into the lowest level of hell as a fallen angel. On her way to hell, Lucifer happens to meet a high school girl on Earth named Maria, who helps her. In hell, Lucifer meets Leviathan, and Leviathan explains to Lucifer about The Seven Deadly Sins, the seven demon king rulers of hell. After The Seven Deadly Sins seal Lucifer's powers, Lucifer goes on a journey with Maria and Leviathan to defeat them.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Official Website)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":20705,"idMal":33834,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":52,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20705","startDate":{"day":15,"month":4,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Seven Mortal Sins","native":"sin 七つの大罪","romaji":"sin: Nanatsu no Taizai","userPreferred":"sin: Nanatsu no Taizai"},"trailer":{"id":"eqiRF7ovKM4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eqiRF7ovKM4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/6500.jpg","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx6500-RQxUgnApAqqn.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx6500-RQxUgnApAqqn.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx6500-RQxUgnApAqqn.png"},"description":"When Mafuyu Oribe and her adopted sister Tomo rescue a strange wounded man, they have no idea what they're getting involved with or what the consequences will be. Alexander Nikolaevith Hell is an Iron Qwaser, one of many opposing factions of super-warriors who can each draw upon the power of an element and wield it as an almost unstoppable array of weapons. And unfortunately for Mafuyu, Alexander's faction is there to gather the mystical relics known collectively as the High Circuit, which puts her friends, family and school at ground zero in a battle for the fate of all mankind! But there's an even more disturbing twist, as Qwasers require a special liquid diet to manifest their powers, one provided by the women who serve as a Qwaser's partner. And THAT means that the nursing Mafuyu's already given Alexander isn't the only kind of nursing he needs! \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks) ","episodes":24,"format":"TV","id":6500,"idMal":6500,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":55,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/6500","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2010},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"The Qwaser of Stigmata","native":"聖痕のクェイサー","romaji":"Seikon no Qwaser","userPreferred":"Seikon no Qwaser"},"trailer":{"id":"mr_Sus560xM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mr_Sus560xM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"coverImage":{"color":"#d6281a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx4719-je2iLM7t0jsd.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx4719-je2iLM7t0jsd.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx4719-je2iLM7t0jsd.jpg"},"description":"In a land where a queen is chosen every few years solely by winning a tournament, there can be no short supply of formidable opponents. For one woman warrior however, an early defeat clearly shows her that she is lacking in experience though she may be bountiful in body.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFortunately, while defeat could spell one's doom, her life is saved by a powerful stranger. But unfortunately for this savior, less-than-pure motives and shrewd family members mean her reward is a prison cell. Her release is prompt when the unseasoned warrior she saved, tired of her current lifestyle of nobility, sets off to prove herself.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Media Blasters)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":4719,"idMal":4719,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":56,"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/4719","startDate":{"day":2,"month":4,"year":2009},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Queen's Blade: The Exiled Virgin","native":"クイーンズブレイド 流浪の戦士","romaji":"Queen's Blade: Rurou no Senshi","userPreferred":"Queen's Blade: Rurou no Senshi"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/192867-r3UitttEQv8C.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg"},"description":"Office Lady Tsuda Akane, age 28, seems like she’s got it all together. Beautiful, brainy, and an indispensable office worker for a robotics manufacturer, Akane’s admired at work…because her colleagues can’t see her at home. Privately, Akane’s a hot mess with an apartment that looks more like a landfill than a living space. Good thing she drunkenly ordered a new android named Nadeshiko to help her clean up! Well, maybe not good, because the beautiful lady android that arrives is a horny hottie. Akane’s about to get more service than she expected!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","episodes":8,"format":"TV_SHORT","id":192867,"idMal":61694,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/192867","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Does it Count if You Lose Your Innocence to an Android?","native":"アンドロイドは経験人数に入りますか？？","romaji":"Android wa Keiken Ninzuu ni Hairimasu ka??","userPreferred":"Android wa Keiken Ninzuu ni Hairimasu ka??"},"trailer":{"id":"SQAHZWo7x28","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SQAHZWo7x28/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/9936-TxE1ElPknoOw.png","coverImage":{"color":"#e4505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/9936.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/9936.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/9936.jpg"},"description":"Based on the manga series by Hiromitsu Takeda, this romantic comedy is about Takeru Ohyama, a typical perverted teenage boy. His new school doesn't require entrance exams, and it just turned co-ed! Unfortunately, his dreams of a happy high school life are dashed when he finds out the school is much more than it seems. All of the students wield a special item\u0026mdash;a Maken\u0026mdash;to unleash their magical abilities in duels! Can Takeru find a Maken that works for him? Even while trying to fit in at a new school and dealing with all kinds of girl problems?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: FUNimation)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":9936,"idMal":9936,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/9936","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Maken-Ki! Battling Venus","native":"マケン姫っ！","romaji":"Maken-Ki!","userPreferred":"Maken-Ki!"},"trailer":{"id":"pBlx0N9eLNY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pBlx0N9eLNY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/110810-O9fJXhXPWU50.jpg","coverImage":{"color":"#50c9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx110810-dJEpyDWfzbfX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx110810-dJEpyDWfzbfX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx110810-dJEpyDWfzbfX.jpg"},"description":"Rin Namiki's greatest ambition is to follow in her late mother's footsteps and compete in Kandagawa Jet Racing, where teams of girls on jet skis race while firing high-powered water guns to slow their competitors' jets (and blow off their clothing!). But since there's no jet racing in Rin's remote fishing village, that means moving, all by herself, to a girls' school in faraway Tokyo!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nMeanwhile, Misa Aoi dreamed of becoming a great player, but those ambitions floundered until Rin transferred to her school, displaying astonishing skill for a newcomer. Is it fate? Now they \"only\" have to resurrect their school's Jet Riding Club, endure brutal training, and face some seriously skilled rivals… but even the toughest tasks are easier when you're doing something you love with someone who's quickly becoming far more than just a friend!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)","episodes":12,"format":"TV","id":110810,"idMal":40196,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":53,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/110810","startDate":{"day":8,"month":10,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Kandagawa Jet Girls","native":"神田川JET GIRLS","romaji":"Kandagawa JET GIRLS","userPreferred":"Kandagawa JET GIRLS"},"trailer":{"id":"hbsIFTlxMFI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hbsIFTlxMFI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg"},"description":"A series of specials included in the 'Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid' DVD/BD volumes.","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":5,"year":2016},"episodes":6,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Ecchi","Fantasy"],"id":21413,"idMal":31736,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21413","startDate":{"day":18,"month":12,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Specials","native":"ヴァルキリードライヴ マーメイド ミニOVA","romaji":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Mini OVA","userPreferred":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Mini OVA"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx97005-xNX791FXcaNc.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx97005-xNX791FXcaNc.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx97005-xNX791FXcaNc.jpg"},"description":"Tokonome Mamori is transferred to \"Mermaid\"—an artificial quarantine island for people with superpowers. When Mamori is attacked, a newly transferred girl named Mirei saves her. The enemy doesn't stop, however, and the two are soon cornered. Just when they think all hope is lost, Mirei kisses Mamori, and Mamori turns into a sword. Mirei then wields the sword and launches a counterattack against their enemies.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","endDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Ecchi","Fantasy"],"id":97005,"idMal":97328,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":66,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/97005","startDate":{"day":26,"month":10,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["VALKYRIE DRIVE -MERMAID-"],"title":{"native":"ヴァルキリードライヴ マーメイド","romaji":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid","userPreferred":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"ADAPTATION"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21116","staff":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":107537,"name":{"full":"Hiraku Kaneko"}},"role":"Director"},{"node":{"id":97471,"name":{"full":"Yousuke Kuroda"}},"role":"Series Composition"},{"node":{"id":107537,"name":{"full":"Hiraku Kaneko"}},"role":"Character Design"},{"node":{"id":102193,"name":{"full":"Hiroki Matsumoto"}},"role":"Art Director"},{"node":{"id":120019,"name":{"full":"Hiroaki Tsutsumi"}},"role":"Music"},{"node":{"id":103030,"name":{"full":"Hitomi Harada"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (OP)"},{"node":{"id":95885,"name":{"full":"Yuka Iguchi"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED)"},{"node":{"id":119401,"name":{"full":"Mikako Izawa"}},"role":"Theme Song Performance (ED)"},{"node":{"id":118925,"name":{"full":"Hideki Furukawa"}},"role":"Key Animation (OP)"},{"node":{"id":121364,"name":{"full":"Akiko Kikuchi"}},"role":"Background Art (eps 1-4)"},{"node":{"id":102193,"name":{"full":"Hiroki Matsumoto"}},"role":"Background Art (eps 1-5, 7-12)"},{"node":{"id":159989,"name":{"full":"Takurou Hatakeyama"}},"role":"Producer"},{"node":{"id":148176,"name":{"full":"Kazuo Oonuki"}},"role":"Producer"},{"node":{"id":142246,"name":{"full":"Noritomo Isogai"}},"role":"Producer"},{"node":{"id":142292,"name":{"full":"Shou Tanaka"}},"role":"Producer"},{"node":{"id":214929,"name":{"full":"Kazuyoshi Ozawa"}},"role":"Production Generalization"},{"node":{"id":146766,"name":{"full":"Gou Wakabayashi"}},"role":"Music Producer"},{"node":{"id":130465,"name":{"full":"Hisashi Akimoto"}},"role":"CG Director"},{"node":{"id":129400,"name":{"full":"Takeshi Seyama"}},"role":"Editing"},{"node":{"id":102193,"name":{"full":"Hiroki Matsumoto"}},"role":"Art Design"},{"node":{"id":103074,"name":{"full":"Jin Aketagawa"}},"role":"Sound Director"},{"node":{"id":148360,"name":{"full":"Takeo Gotou"}},"role":"Director of Photography"},{"node":{"id":217001,"name":{"full":"Hideo Kamiya"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":219403,"name":{"full":"Mayumi Nagashima"}},"role":"Color Design"},{"node":{"id":170201,"name":{"full":"Hiyori Denforword Akishino"}},"role":"Prop Design"}]},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":10,"year":2015},"studios":{"nodes":[{"id":38,"name":"Arms"}]}}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:34:00.788085+03:00"}}
